  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You burst from the shadows with terrifying speed. You can Stride up to your Speed towards an enemy. If you end this movement within melee reach of the enemy, you can make a melee Strike. If this attack hits, the target is Off-Guard until the start of your next turn.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actStalkersPounce", "name": "Stalker’s Pounce", "traits": "Shistavanen", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You burst from the shadows with terrifying speed. You can Stride up to your Speed towards an enemy. If you end this movement within melee reach of the enemy, you can make a melee Strike. If this attack hits, the target is Off-Guard until the start of your next turn.", "requirements": "You are Hidden or Undetected by your target. "}]}}',	' You burst from the shadows with terrifying speed.',	'0',	5,	'Shistavanen',	NULL),
('aftLopingStride',	'ancShistavanen',	'Loping Stride',	'Your digitigrade legs are built for running down fleeing targets. Your Speed increases by 5 feet. When you take the Step action, you can move 10 feet instead of 5 feet, provided you are not in difficult terrain.',	'{"speed": [{"amount": 5, "target": "all"}]}',	'Your digitigrade legs are built for running down fleeing targets.',	'0',	5,	'Shistavanen',	NULL),
('aftPredatorsPatience',	'ancShistavanen',	'Predator’s Patience',	'You can stand perfectly still for hours waiting for prey. You can use the Hide action even if you do not have cover or concealment, provided you remain completely motionless. You cannot use this benefit to Sneak, and you lose the benefit if you Step.',	NULL,	'You can stand perfectly still for hours waiting for prey.',	'0',	1,	'Shistavanen',	NULL),
('aftReactionaryReflexes',	'ancShistavanen',	'Reactionary Reflexes',	'Your species is known for twitch-reflexes, making you excellent pilots and duelist. You gain a +2 status bonus to initiative.',	'{"perception": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Reactionary Reflexes", "value": "+2 status bonus to initiative.", "target": "all"}]}}',	'Your species is known for twitch-reflexes.',	'0',	1,	'Shistavanen',	NULL),
('aftUnstoppableJuggernaut',	'ancWookiee',	'Unstoppable Juggernaut',	'Pain is just information that you choose to ignore. You gain resistance 5 to all Physical damage (Bludgeoning, Piercing, Slashing). When you are Slowed or Stunned, you reduce the value of the condition by 1 (effectively ignoring Slowed 1 or Stunned 1).',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Bludgeoning", "amount": "5", "source": "Unstoppable Juggernaut (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Piercing", "amount": "5", "source": "Unstoppable Juggernaut (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Slashing", "amount": "5", "source": "Unstoppable Juggernaut (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Pain is just information that you choose to ignore.',	'0',	17,	'Wookiee',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftTenaciousVitality", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftSolitarySurvivor',	'ancShistavanen',	'Solitary Survivor',	'Shistavanens are culturally isolationist and often work alone. If you end your turn with no allies adjacent to you, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC until the start of your next turn.',	NULL,	'Shistavanens are culturally isolationist and often work alone.',	'0',	1,	'Shistavanen',	NULL),
('aftArboreal Stride',	'ancEwok',	'Arboreal Stride',	'You move through the trees as easily as humans walk on ground. You gain a Climb Speed of 20 feet. You can hang from a branch by your feet or tail to leave your hands free for combat, though you cannot move while doing so.',	'{"speed": [{"climb": 20}]}',	'You move through the trees as easily as humans walk on ground.',	'0',	5,	'Ewok',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftTreeDweller", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftParanoidAlertness',	'ancBothan',	'Paranoid Alertness',	'Bothans are naturally distrustful, always expecting a knife in the back. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Perception checks to determine Initiative. Additionally, you cannot be Off-Guard (Flat-Footed) to creatures of your level or lower that are hidden or undetected by you at the start of combat.',	NULL,	'Bothans are naturally distrustful, always expecting a knife in the back.',	'0',	1,	'Bothan',	NULL),
('aftInformedTarget',	'ancBothan',	'Informed Target',	'You know exactly where to hit because you studied the anatomy charts. You can use Recall Knowledge as a free action at the start of your turn against a creature you have not yet identified. If you succeed, your first Strike against that creature this turn deals +1 Precision damage. This increases to +2 at level 5, +3 at level 9, etc.',	NULL,	'You know exactly where to hit because you studied the anatomy charts.',	'0',	1,	'Bothan',	NULL),
('aftPrimevalAwareness',	'ancShistavanen',	'Primeval Awareness',	'Your evolutionary traits have reached their absolute peak; there is no hiding from you. You gain Tremorsense (Imprecise) out to 60 feet, allowing you to feel vibrations in the ground.

Furthermore, you can perceive creatures within 30 feet as if you had True Sight (ignoring illusions, invisibility, blur/displacement, and darkness). This is not magical sight, but a hyper-acute synthesis of smell, hearing, and air pressure sensitivity that creates a perfect mental image of your surroundings.',	'{"sense": [{"Tremorsense": "60 feet"}, {"True Sight": "30 feet"}]}',	'Your evolutionary traits have reached their absolute peak; there is no hiding from you.',	'0',	17,	'Shistavanen',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftBloodScent", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftMasterOfTheLanes',	'ancShistavanen',	'Master of the Lanes',	'You rely on animal instinct rather than computer targeting, reacting to threats before the sensors even register them. You are one with your vessel.

- When you pilot a vehicle or starship, its Maneuverability improves by one step (e.g., Average becomes Good, Good becomes Perfect).
- You can perform defensive maneuvers instinctually. At the start of each round of vehicle combat, you automatically gain the benefits of the Evade action (or your system''s equivalent "Defensive Piloting" action that grants an AC bonus) without spending an action.
- Once per hour, if you fail a Piloting check to perform a stunt or navigate a hazard, you can reroll the check with a +4 circumstance bonus. You must use the second result.',	NULL,	'You rely on animal instinct rather than computer targeting.',	'0',	17,	'Shistavanen',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftInstinctiveAstrogation", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftFaceInTheCrowd',	'ancBothan',	'Face in the Crowd',	'You know how to position yourself so that there is always someone else between you and a threat. You can use the Hide and Sneak actions even if you are being observed, provided you are within 10 feet of at least two other creatures of your size or larger (these can be allies, enemies, or neutral bystanders). While you are within reach of another creature of your size or larger, you gain Standard Cover (+2 to AC, Reflex saves, and Stealth checks) from attacks originating from creatures not adjacent to you, rather than the usual Lesser Cover provided by intervening creatures.',	NULL,	'You know how to position yourself so that there is always someone else between you and a threat.',	'0',	5,	'Bothan',	NULL),
('aftWaveringFur',	'ancBothan',	'Wavering Fur',	'You can communicate complex concepts solely through the rippling of your fur. You gain Sign Language as a bonus feat. However, unlike standard sign language, your communication is subtle enough that creatures without the Bothan trait or specific training in reading Bothan body language cannot detect that you are communicating at all. You can convey secret messages to allies in plain sight while holding a normal conversation with an enemy.',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaSignLanguage", "type": "skill"}]}}',	'You can communicate complex concepts solely through the rippling of your fur.',	'0',	1,	'Bothan, Visual',	NULL),
('aftSpynetInitiate',	'ancBothan',	'Spynet Initiate',	'You have a low-level contact in the legendary Bothan Spynet. You become trained in Diplomacy and Underworld Lore. Additionally, you can use the Gather Information activity in half the normal time (typically 1 hour instead of 2), and you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to the check.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklDiplomacy", "rank": "Trained"}, {"id": "sklLoreUnderworld", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You have a low-level contact in the legendary Bothan Spynet.',	'0',	1,	'Bothan',	NULL),
('aftPoliticalAnimal',	'ancBothan',	'Political Animal',	'To you, every conversation is a duel. You can use Society or Politics Lore instead of Perception to Sense Motive. If you succeed at a Sense Motive check to detect a lie, you also learn why the target is lying (e.g., to protect someone, for greed, or out of fear).',	NULL,	'To you, every conversation is a duel.',	'0',	1,	'Bothan',	NULL),
('aftThroatRipper',	'ancShistavanen',	'Throat-Ripper',	'You aim for vital arteries. Your Claw attack gains the Deadly d6 trait. On a Critical Hit, in addition to the deadly damage, the target takes 1d4 persistent Bleed damage.',	'{"weapon": [{"id": "natWolfmansClaws", "bulk": null, "name": "Wolfman''s Claws", "type": "Melee", "group": "Brawling", "hands": "1", "traits": "Agile, Deadly d6, Finesse", "category": "Unarmed", "damagedie": "d4", "damagetype": "S", "description": "You have honed your natural weapons for combat. You gain a Claw unarmed attack that deals 1d4 Slashing damage. Your claws are in the Brawling group and have the Agile and Finesse traits.<br><br>You aim for vital arteries. Your Claw attack gains the Deadly d6 trait. On a Critical Hit, in addition to the deadly damage, the target takes 1d4 persistent Bleed damage."}]}',	'You aim for vital arteries.',	'0',	5,	'Shistavanen',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftShistavanenClaws", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftCoordinatedAmbush',	'ancChubbit',	'Coordinated Ambush',	'You seamlessly signal your squadmates the moment you detect a threat. When you roll Stealth or Perception for Initiative, you can grant one ally who can see or hear you a +2 circumstance bonus to their Initiative roll.',	NULL,	'You seamlessly signal your squadmates the moment you detect a threat.',	'0',	9,	'Chubbit',	NULL),
('aftPsychologicalWarfare',	'ancBothan',	'Psychological Warfare',	'You don''t just hurt the body; you break the spirit by revealing you know their darkest secrets. When you succeed at a Demoralize check, the target takes Mental Damage equal to your level. If you Critically Succeed, the target is also Stunned 1 as they reel from the revelation of their private information.',	NULL,	'You don''t just hurt the body; you break the spirit by revealing you know their darkest secrets.',	'0',	9,	'Bothan, Emotion, Mental',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSowDiscord", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftSpynetSafehouse',	'ancBothan',	'Spynet Safehouse',	'You can find a safe place to rest almost anywhere in the galaxy. In any settlement of Village size or larger, you can automatically locate a hidden safehouse. This provides a secure location for you and your team to take a Long Rest without fear of interruption or discovery, effectively reducing the danger level of resting in hostile territory to zero (unless the settlement is actively being purged).',	NULL,	'You can find a safe place to rest almost anywhere in the galaxy.',	'0',	5,	'Bothan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSpynetInitiate", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftMasterOfDisguise',	'ancBothan',	'Master of Disguise',	'You can adopt a new persona with terrifying speed. You can create a convincing disguise (Impersonate) as a 1-minute activity (instead of 10+ minutes). If you have studied a specific individual for at least 1 hour, you can mimic their voice and mannerisms perfectly, granting you a +4 circumstance bonus to Deception checks to pass as them.',	NULL,	'You can adopt a new persona with terrifying speed.',	'0',	13,	'Bothan',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklDeception", "rank": "Expert"}]}]'),
('aftLogicalStoicism',	'ancCerean',	'Logical Stoicism',	'You have been trained to suppress volatile emotions in favor of pure logic. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Will saves against Emotion and Fear effects. If you roll a Success on a saving throw against a Fear effect, you get a Critical Success instead.',	NULL,	'You have been trained to suppress volatile emotions in favor of pure logic.',	'0',	1,	'Cerean',	NULL),
('aftAridusPhantom',	'ancChubbit',	'Aridus Phantom',	'You are a ghost in the wilds, impossible to pin down. While you are in natural terrain (such as desert, forest, or mountains), you are permanently concealed. This concealment cannot be used to Hide, but it does force the standard DC 11 flat check for enemies to target you with attacks.',	NULL,	'You are a ghost in the wilds, impossible to pin down.',	'0',	17,	'Chubbit',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSpeckledCamouflage", "type": "ancestry"}], "skill": [{"id": "sklStealth", "rank": "Master"}]}]'),
('aftOpportunisticBetrayal',	'ancBothan',	'Opportunistic Betrayal',	'You take advantage of the chaos. You can make a melee Strike against the triggering enemy as a Reaction. This Strike counts as a Sneak Attack (dealing extra precision damage if you have that class feature, or adding 1d6 precision damage if you do not).

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Opportunistic Betrayal</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 9</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Bothan</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>An enemy within your melee reach is hit by an attack from one of its own allies (due to Confusion, a Critical Failure, or an area of effect).</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You take advantage of the chaos. You can make a melee Strike against the triggering enemy. This enemy is Off-Guard against this Strike.  If you do not have any sources of precision damage against Off-Guard opponents, you deal an extra 1d6 precision damage instead.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actOpportunisticBetrayal", "name": "Opportunistic Betrayal", "traits": "Bothan", "trigger": "An enemy within your melee reach is hit by an attack from one of its own allies (due to Confusion, a Critical Failure, or an area of effect).", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You take advantage of the chaos. You can make a melee Strike against the triggering enemy. This enemy is Off-Guard against this Strike.  If you do not have any sources of precision damage against Off-Guard opponents, you deal an extra 1d6 precision damage instead."}]}}',	'You take advantage of the chaos.',	'0',	9,	'Bothan',	NULL),
('aftTwoHearts',	'ancCerean',	'Two Hearts',	'Your dual cardiovascular system provides incredible stamina. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Fortitude saving throws. Additionally, whenever you would gain the Fatigued condition, you can attempt a DC 15 Flat Check. On a success, you do not become Fatigued.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"fortitude": {"bonus": [{"type": "circumstance", "amount": "1", "source": "Two Hearts (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}]}',	'Your dual cardiovascular system provides incredible stamina.',	'0',	1,	'Cerean',	NULL),
('aftCalculatedTrajectory',	'ancCerean',	'Calculated Trajectory',	'You instinctively calculate parabolas and wind resistance. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to attack rolls with Grenades and Thrown weapons. Additionally, you reduce the penalty for attacking into the second range increment of a thrown weapon by 2.',	'{"attack": {"group": [{"grenade": {"bonus": [{"type": "circumstance", "amount": "1", "source": "Calculated Trajectory (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}]}}',	'You instinctively calculate parabolas and wind resistance.',	'0',	1,	'Cerean',	NULL),
('aftIndomitableVigor',	'ancGamorrean',	'Indomitable Vigor',	'Your metabolism is an aggressive furnace that burns through toxins and trauma, and your muscles are too dense to atrophy. You are immune to the Sickened condition, whenever you would gain the Enfeebled or Clumsy condition, reduce the value of that condition by 1.',	NULL,	'Your metabolism is an aggressive furnace that burns through toxins and trauma, and your muscles are too dense to atrophy.',	'0',	13,	'Gamorrean',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftThickHide", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftLogicalDiscourse',	'ancCerean',	'Logical Discourse',	'You can dismantle an opponent’s worldview with a few sentences. You can use Society or Diplomacy to Demoralize an enemy. When you do so, the effect is not based on fear, but on crushing doubt. If you Critically Succeed, the target is Stupefied 1 for 1 minute in addition to being Frightened/Doubtful.',	NULL,	'You can dismantle an opponent’s worldview with a few sentences.',	'0',	9,	'Cerean, Auditory, Linguistic, Mental',	NULL),
('aftMentalPartitioning',	'ancCerean',	'Mental Partitioning',	'You can quarantine a compromised part of your mind while the other lobe remains active. If you would be affected by a Mental effect that imposes the Confused, Controlled, or Stupefied condition, you can attempt a new Will save at the start of each of your turns to end the effect immediately, even if the effect does not normally allow a new save.',	NULL,	'You can quarantine a compromised part of your mind while the other lobe remains active.',	'0',	5,	'Cerean',	NULL),
('aftCanopyAwareness',	'ancEwok',	'Canopy Awareness',	'You are accustomed to threats coming from any direction at any time. You can trigger your Reactions even if you are Surprised or Off-Guard. Additionally, you are no longer Off-Guard to hidden, undetected, or flanking creatures of your level or lower.',	NULL,	'You are accustomed to threats coming from any direction at any time.',	'0',	13,	'Ewok',	NULL),
('aftDualFocus',	'ancCerean',	'Dual Focus',	'You can maintain attention on two complex tasks at once. If you use the Sustain action (to sustain a power, a tech ability, or an active item), you can Sustain two different effects with that single action.',	NULL,	'You can maintain attention on two complex tasks at once.',	'0',	5,	'Cerean',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftBinaryProcessing", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftMultiArmedCoordination',	'ancCodruJi',	'Multi-Armed Coordination',	'You are adept at using your lower set of arms for support tasks. You can use a single Interact action to draw, sheathe, or pick up two different items, provided you have the free hands to do so. Additionally, you do not drop held items when you become Unconscious.',	NULL,	'You are adept at using your lower set of arms for support tasks.',	'0',	1,	'Codru-Ji',	NULL),
('aftBinaryRedundancy',	'ancCerean',	'Binary Redundancy',	'Even if one brain is shut down, the other takes over. You are immune to the Stunned condition unless the duration is "Permanent." If a mental effect would Stun you, you are Slowed 1 instead.',	NULL,	'Even if one brain is shut down, the other takes over.',	'0',	9,	'Cerean',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftMentalPartitioning", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftStandingSlumber',	'ancCodruJi',	'Standing Slumber',	'Your species sleeps standing up and can transition to wakefulness instantly. You do not take penalties to Perception checks while sleeping, and you do not gain the Prone condition when you fall asleep or become unconscious. Standing up from Prone is a free action for you.',	NULL,	'Your species sleeps standing up and can transition to wakefulness instantly.',	'0',	1,	'Codru-Ji',	NULL),
('aftUnstoppableMomentum',	'ancGamorrean',	'Unstoppable Momentum',	'When you use Boar''s Charge, you ignore Difficult Terrain. Additionally, if you hit with the Strike at the end of the charge, you can attempt to Shove the target as a free action.',	NULL,	'When you use Boar''s Charge, you ignore Difficult Terrain.',	'0',	9,	'Gamorrean',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftBoarsCharge", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftElectropoleGuard',	'ancGungan',	'Electropole Guard',	'You know how to hold the line. When wielding a Spear or Staff (or Electropole), you gain the Reactive Strike (Attack of Opportunity) reaction. If you already have Reactive Strike from your class, you gain a second reaction per round that can only be used for Reactive Strikes with these weapons.',	NULL,	'You know how to hold the line.',	'0',	9,	'Gungan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftGunganWeaponFamiliarity", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftRapidAssessment',	'ancCerean',	'Rapid Assessment',	'Your brain processes visual data faster than standard biology allows. You can use the Seek action as a Free Action at the start of your turn. You can only use this to scan for creatures in your line of sight, not to search for hidden doors or traps.',	NULL,	'Your brain processes visual data faster than standard biology allows.',	'0',	5,	'Cerean',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftIntuitiveGeometry", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftProfessionalAbductor',	'ancCodruJi',	'Professional Abductor',	'Kidnapping is a complex social game in your culture, and you know the holds well. You gain the Titan Wrestler skill feat (allowing you to Grapple creatures larger than you). Additionally, if you succeed at an Athletics check to Grapple a creature, you can choose to move that creature 5 feet into an adjacent open space as part of the action.',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaTitanWrestler", "type": "skill"}]}}',	'Kidnapping is a complex social game in your culture, and you know the holds well.',	'0',	1,	'Codru-Ji',	NULL),
('aftGrapplersAdvantage',	'ancCodruJi',	'Grappler’s Advantage',	'You have two hands for holding and two hands for hitting. When you have a creature Grabbed or Restrained, you can make melee Strikes against that creature without taking the standard Multiple Attack Penalty (MAP) for the Grapple action you just performed. (Usually, Grapple counts as an Attack for MAP; this feat allows your first Strike against the grabbed target to ignore that specific MAP increase).',	NULL,	'You have two hands for holding and two hands for hitting.',	'0',	5,	'Codru-Ji',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftProfessionalAbductor", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftTuskedVisage',	'ancGamorrean',	'Tusked Visage',	'Your tusks are not just for display. You gain a Tusk unarmed attack that deals 1d6 Piercing damage. Your tusks are in the Brawling group and have the Unarmed trait. Unlike most unarmed attacks, your tusks do not have the Finesse trait (you must use Strength).',	'{"weapon": [{"id": "natGamorreanTusks", "bulk": null, "name": "Gamorrean Tusks", "type": "Melee", "group": "Brawling", "hands": "1", "category": "Unarmed", "damagedie": "d6", "damagetype": "P", "description": "Your tusks are not just for display. You gain a Tusk unarmed attack that deals 1d6 Piercing damage. Your tusks are in the Brawling group and have the Unarmed trait. Unlike most unarmed attacks, your tusks do not have the Finesse trait (you must use Strength)."}]}',	'Your tusks are not just for display.',	'0',	1,	'Gamorrean',	NULL),
('aftWyrwulfAgility',	'ancCodruJi',	'Wyrwulf Agility',	'You retain some of the hexapedal scrambling speed of your larval stage. You gain a Climb Speed of 15 feet. You do not need to use your hands to climb surfaces with a DC of 20 or lower; you can simply scramble up them, leaving your hands free for combat.',	'{"speed": [{"climb": 15}]}',	'You retain some of the hexapedal scrambling speed of your larval stage.',	'0',	5,	'Codru-Ji',	NULL),
('aftShieldPhalanx',	'ancGungan',	'Shield Phalanx',	'You can project your shield to cover your allies. When you Raise a Shield, you can grant Standard Cover (+2 AC) to all adjacent allies until the start of your next turn. You cannot move while maintaining this phalanx.',	NULL,	'You can project your shield to cover your allies.',	'0',	13,	'Gungan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftEnergyShieldExpert", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftElectromagneticResilience',	'ancChubbit',	'Electromagnetic Resilience',	'Your nervous system has completely hardened against the frequency overloads that once crippled your people. Your resistance to sonic damage increases to equal your full level. Additionally, you gain resistance to electricity damage equal to half your level.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Sonic", "amount": "{level}", "source": "Electromagnetic Resilience (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Electricity", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Electromagnetic Resilience (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your nervous system has completely hardened against the frequency overloads that once crippled your people.',	'0',	13,	'Chubbit',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftIronTowerSurvivor", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftLivingShield',	'ancGamorrean',	'Living Shield',	'You are wide enough to block a hallway. If you are adjacent to an ally of your size or smaller, that ally gains Standard Cover (+2 AC) against attacks that pass through your space. You do not provide cover to enemies against allies adjacent to you.',	NULL,	'You are wide enough to block a hallway.',	'0',	5,	'Gamorrean',	NULL),
('aftFourArmedReload',	'ancCodruJi',	'Four-Armed Reload',	'You use your lower hands to grab power cells while your upper hands keep the aim steady. You can Interact to reload a weapon as a Free Action once per round. This counts towards the limit of 1 free action per trigger/round.',	NULL,	'You use your lower hands to grab power cells while your upper hands keep the aim steady.',	'0',	5,	'Codru, Manipulate',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftMultiArmedCoordination", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftThreateningPosture',	'ancCodruJi',	'Threatening Posture',	'You know how to flare your four arms to look larger and more menacing. You become Trained in Intimidation. If you are already trained, you gain a skill of your choice. When you Demoralize a creature while wielding two or more weapons, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to the check.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklIntimidation", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You know how to flare your four arms to look larger and more menacing.',	'0',	1,	'Codru-Ji, Emotion, Mental',	NULL),
('aftHostageShield',	'ancCodruJi',	'Hostage Shield',	'You are an expert at keeping "valuable assets" between you and the enemy. You gain Standard Cover (+2 AC) while you are grappling a creature of your size or larger. If an attack misses you but would have hit you without this cover, the attack hits the creature you are grappling instead.',	NULL,	'You are an expert at keeping "valuable assets" between you and the enemy.',	'0',	9,	'Codru-Ji',	NULL),
('aftMasterOfTheComplexForm',	'ancCodruJi',	'Master of the Complex Form',	'Your coordination is flawless; your mind controls each limb with independent perfection. You are permanently Quickened. You can use the extra action to Interact, Step, or Reload. You cannot be Flanked by creatures of your level or lower, as your peripheral limbs defend your rear.',	NULL,	'Your coordination is flawless; your mind controls each limb with independent perfection.',	'0',	17,	'Codru-Ji',	NULL),
('aftWallScuttler',	'ancRodian',	'Wall-Scuttler',	'You can run up walls as easily as floors. You gain a Climb Speed equal to your land Speed. You can climb even on smooth surfaces (like glass or metal) without penalty, provided you have at least two hands free (or one hand and two feet).',	'{"speed": [{"climb": "{speed}"}]}',	'You can run up walls as easily as floors.',	'0',	5,	'Rodian',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSuctionCups", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftSavageGore',	'ancGamorrean',	'Savage Gore',	'You know how to twist your head to rip flesh. On a Critical Hit with your Tusk attack, the target takes 1d6 persistent Bleed damage.',	NULL,	'You know how to twist your head to rip flesh.',	'0',	5,	'Gamorrean',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftTuskedVisage", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftUncannySkirmisher',	'ancChubbit',	'Uncanny Skirmisher',	'Your reflexes are nearly supernatural. When you use your Guerrilla Retreat reaction, you can Step twice instead of once, or you can Stride up to half your Speed.',	NULL,	'Your reflexes are nearly supernatural.',	'0',	13,	'Chubbit',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftGuerillaRetreat", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftInternalGyroscope',	'ancSullustan',	'Internal Gyroscope',	'Your inner ear is a biological compass that never fails. You always know which way is North and can instantly gauge the depth you are underground. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Survival checks to Navigate. Additionally, you are immune to the Clumsy condition (often caused by zero-G or flight maneuvers).',	'{"skill": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Internal Gyroscope", "value": "+2 circumstance bonus to Navigate.", "target": "sklSurvival"}]}}',	'Your inner ear is a biological compass that never fails.',	'0',	1,	'Sullustan',	NULL),
('aftRyykBladeWhirlwind',	'ancWookiee',	'Ryyk Blade Whirlwind',	'You spin your blades in a deadly defensive perimeter.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Ryyk Blade Whirlwind</h3>
