  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You Strike every enemy within your Reach. Each attack is rolled separately but counts as one attack for your Multiple Attack Penalty (the penalty increases only after all attacks are resolved).
  </div>
