    You can use the Crafting skill to Repair yourself as a 2-action activity without needing a repair kit. The DC for the Crafting check and the healing delivered are the same as if using the Medicine skill to Treat Wounds, but this action does not count as any other form of healing for the purpose of ability immunity timers.
  </div>
