  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actShakeItOff", "name": "Shake It Off", "traits": "Gamorrean, Manipulate", "trigger": "You are suffering from the Frightened, Sickened, or Stupefied condition.", "frequency": "Once per minute.", "action_cost": "[free-action]", "description": "You grunt, slap your face, and force your body to focus. You reduce the value of the triggering condition by 1. (e.g., Frightened 2 becomes Frightened 1)."}]}}',	'You grunt, slap your face, and force your body to focus.',	'0',	5,	'Gamorrean, Manipulate',	NULL),
('aftAnzellanOptics',	'ancAnzellan',	'Anzellan Optics',	'Whether through biological mutation or cybernetic lenses, your eyes are microscopes. You gain Darkvision. Additionally, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Perception checks to find hidden objects, traps, or small details (like a micro-switch on a datapad).',	'{"perception": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Anzellan Optics", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to find hidden objects, traps, or small details.", "target": "all"}]}}',	'Whether through biological mutation or cybernetic lenses, your eyes are microscopes.',	'0',	1,	'Anzellan',	NULL),
('aftHordeBreaker',	'ancGamorrean',	'Horde Breaker',	'You swing wildly through the enemy ranks

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Horde Breaker</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
