  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You swing wildly through the enemy ranks. Make a melee Strike against a foe. If it hits, you can make another Strike against a different foe adjacent to the first. Continue making Strikes until you miss or run out of adjacent targets. You cannot attack the same creature twice, and your multiple attack penalty increases normally after the entire activity is resolved (not during the swings).
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actHorde Breaker", "name": "Horde Breaker", "traits": "Gamorrean", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You swing wildly through the enemy ranks. Make a melee Strike against a foe. If it hits, you can make another Strike against a different foe adjacent to the first. Continue making Strikes until you miss or run out of adjacent targets. You cannot attack the same creature twice, and your multiple attack penalty increases normally after the entire activity is resolved (not during the swings).", "requirements": "You are wielding a weapon with the Sweep or Backswing trait."}]}}',	'You swing wildly through the enemy ranks',	'0',	13,	'Gamorrean',	NULL),
('aftBloodScent',	'ancShistavanen',	'Blood Scent',	'The smell of iron in the air drives you forward. Your Scent range increases to 60 feet. Furthermore, if a living creature within your Scent range is not at maximum Hit Points (it has taken damage or is bleeding), your sense of smell toward that specific creature becomes Precise (allowing you to target them as if you could see them, ignoring the Hidden or Invisible condition).',	NULL,	'The smell of iron in the air drives you forward.',	'0',	5,	'Shistavanen',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftWolfenSenses", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftCardiovascularOverdrive',	'ancCerean',	'Cardiovascular Overdrive',	'Your secondary heart pumps a massive surge of adrenaline and oxygen to purge toxins. You immediately remove the Enfeebled, Fatigued, and Slowed conditions. You gain Temporary Hit Points equal to your Level.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
