('aftScompLink',	'ancDroid',	'Scomp Link',	'You have a retractable data probe that allows you to interface directly with computers. You are considered to always be wielding a slicer''s toolkit for the purpose of making Computers checks to Slice. At level 3, you gain a +1 item bonus to these checks.',	'{"3": {"skill": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Scomp Link", "value": "+1 item bonus to Slice.", "target": "sklComputers"}]}}}',	'You have a retractable data probe that allows you to interface directly with computers.',	'0',	1,	'Droid',	NULL),
