    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Gungan</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Electricity</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You score a Critical Hit with a weapon that deals Electricity damage.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    The impact releases a massive surge of bio-electric feedback. The creature you hit must succeed at a Fortitude save against your Class DC or become Stunned 1 (or Stunned 2 on a Critical Failure) as their nervous system or circuitry seizes up. Lightning arcs from the primary target to up to three other enemies within 20 feet. These enemies take Electricity damage equal to your Level. They can attempt a Reflex save against your Class DC for half damage.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actShockingConduction", "name": "Shocking Conduction", "traits": "Gungan, Electricity", "trigger": "You score a Critical Hit with a weapon that deals Electricity damage.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "The impact releases a massive surge of bio-electric feedback. The creature you hit must succeed at a Fortitude save against your Class DC or become Stunned 1 (or Stunned 2 on a Critical Failure) as their nervous system or circuitry seizes up. Lightning arcs from the primary target to up to three other enemies within 20 feet. These enemies take Electricity damage equal to your Level. They can attempt a Reflex save against your Class DC for half damage."}]}}',	'You know how to modulate the power output of electropoles and energy weapons to cause cascading system failures.',	'0',	13,	'Gungan, Electricity',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftGunganWeaponFamiliarity", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftAcousticDampening',	'ancIthorian',	'Acoustic Dampening',	'Your throat structure is designed to handle immense sonic pressure. You gain resistance to Sonic damage equal to half your level (minimum 1).',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Sonic", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Acoustic Dampening (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your throat structure is designed to handle immense sonic pressure.',	'0',	1,	'Ithorian',	NULL),
('aftAquaticSuperiority',	'ancGungan',	'Aquatic Superiority',	'You move through air as if it were water. You gain a Fly Speed equal to your Speed (representing powerful leaps and rebounds off surfaces), but you fall if you don''t end your turn standing on a surface that can support you. You are immune to the Grabbed and Restrained conditions, as your skin produces a hyper-slick mucus on command.',	NULL,	'You move through air as if it were water.',	'0',	17,	'Gungan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftHydroDynamic", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftArcWelderDefense',	'ancDroid',	'Arc Welder Defense',	'You can repurpose your integrated maintenance tools—such as fusion cutters or shock prods—into close-quarters weapons.

You gain a Shock Probe unarmed attack. It deals 1d6 electricity damage and has the Finesse and Agile traits. Because this is a tool repurposed for combat, you do not take a penalty for making a lethal attack with it, but it creates a loud electrical discharge when used, preventing you from remaining hidden while attacking.',	'{"weapon": [{"id": "natArcWelder", "bulk": null, "name": "Shock Probe", "type": "Melee", "group": "Brawling", "hands": "1", "traits": "Agile, Finesse", "category": "Unarmed", "damagedie": "d6", "damagetype": "Electricity", "description": "You gain a Shock Probe unarmed attack. It deals 1d6 electricity damage and has the Finesse and Agile traits. Because this is a tool repurposed for combat, you do not take a penalty for making a lethal attack with it, but it creates a loud electrical discharge when used, preventing you from remaining hidden while attacking."}]}',	'You can repurpose your integrated maintenance tools—such as fusion cutters or shock prods—into close-quarters weapons.',	'0',	1,	'Droid',	'[{"heritage": "herDroidClass2"}]'),
('aftNuisanceDistraction',	'ancAnzellan',	'Nuisance Distraction',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Nuisance Distraction</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 5</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Anzellan</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You are occupying an enemy''s space. </span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You climb over the target’s armor or sensors, obscuring their vision and distracting them. The target must succeed at a Reflex save against your Class DC.<br><br><strong>Failure</strong> Target is Dazzled until the start of your next turn.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As Failure, but the target is also Blinded for the same duration.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actNuisance Distraction", "name": "Nuisance Distraction", "traits": "Anzellan", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You climb over the target’s armor or sensors, obscuring their vision and distracting them. The target must succeed at a Reflex save against your Class DC.<br><br><strong>Failure</strong> Target is Dazzled until the start of your next turn.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As Failure, but the target is also Blinded for the same duration.", "requirements": "You are occupying an enemy''s space. "}]}}',	'You climb over the target’s armor or sensors, obscuring their vision.',	'0',	5,	'Anzellan',	NULL),
('aftReverberatingSpeech',	'ancIthorian',	'Reverberating Speech',	'You speak with a harmonic resonance that commands attention. When you attempt to Diplomacy (Make an Impression) or Intimidation (Coerce) a group of two or more creatures, you do not take the standard penalty for targeting multiple creatures. You can target a number of creatures equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum 2) simultaneously without penalty.',	NULL,	'You speak with a harmonic resonance that commands attention.',	'0',	5,	'Ithorian, Auditory, Linguistic',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftStereoProjection", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftPanoramicAwareness',	'ancIthorian',	'Panoramic Awareness',	'You have mastered the processing of two distinct visual fields. You can no longer be Flanked by creatures of your level or lower.',	NULL,	'You have mastered the processing of two distinct visual fields.',	'0',	13,	'Ithorian',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftWideAngleVision", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftConcussiveForce',	'ancIthorian',	'Concussive Force',	'Your scream hits with the force of a physical blow. When a creature fails its Fortitude save against your Ithorian Bellow, it is pushed back 10 feet. If it Critically Fails, it is pushed back 20 feet and knocked Prone.',	NULL,	'Your scream hits with the force of a physical blow.',	'0',	13,	'Ithorian, Healing',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftIthorianBellow", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftRestorativePollen',	'ancIthorian',	'Restorative Pollen',	'You shake loose potent, bio-luminescent spores from your skin or gear that accelerate regrowth.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Release Spores</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 13</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Ithorian</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Sonic</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You release a cloud in a 15-foot emanation. You and all living allies in the area regain Hit Points equal to 4d8 + your Constitution modifier. Additionally, any ally in the area suffering from a Poison effect can immediately attempt a new saving throw against it with a +2 circumstance bonus.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actReleaseSpores", "name": "Release Spores", "traits": "Ithorian, Sonic", "frequency": "Once per day.", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You release a cloud in a 15-foot emanation. You and all living allies in the area regain Hit Points equal to 4d8 + your Constitution modifier. Additionally, any ally in the area suffering from a Poison effect can immediately attempt a new saving throw against it with a +2 circumstance bonus."}]}}',	'You shake loose potent, bio-luminescent spores from your skin or gear that accelerate regrowth.',	'0',	13,	'Ithorian, Healing',	NULL),
('aftResonantHarmonics',	'ancIthorian',	'Resonant Harmonics',	'You can find the structural frequency of solid matter. When you use Ithorian Bellow against Constructs or objects, the damage ignores an amount of Hardness equal to your Level. Additionally, if you use an ability with the Sonic trait that targets a single creature or object, you gain a +2 status bonus to damage.',	NULL,	'You can find the structural frequency of solid matter.',	'0',	9,	'Ithorian, Sonic',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftIthorianBellow", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftUltimateStoicism',	'ancKelDor',	'Ultimate Stoicism',	'You are a pillar of absolute order. You are immune to the Frightened, Stupefied, and Confused conditions. Even if a mental effect would bypass immunity, you treat your saving throw result as one degree of success better.',	NULL,	'You are a pillar of absolute order.',	'0',	17,	'Kel Dor',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftMentalFortress", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftBotanicalAlchemist',	'ancIthorian',	'Botanical Alchemist',	'You know how to synthesize healing balms from local flora. You can use Nature instead of Medicine to Treat Wounds. When you use fresh plants or herbs gathered from the immediate environment (requiring 10 minutes of foraging) to Treat Wounds, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to the check and heal an additional 1d8 Hit Points on a success.',	NULL,	'You know how to synthesize healing balms from local flora.',	'0',	5,	'Ithorian',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklNature", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftPistonPunch',	'ancDroid',	'Piston Punch',	'You can over-pressurize your hydraulic lines to deliver a devastating blow. You gain a Piston Slam unarmed attack. It deals 1d6 Bludgeoning damage and has the Shove trait (allowing you to Shove enemies even if your hands are full).<br><br>On a critical hit with this attack, the target is pushed back 5 feet (as if you had successfully Shoved them).',	'{"weapon": [{"id": "natPistonSlam", "bulk": null, "name": "Piston Slam", "type": "Melee", "group": "Brawling", "hands": "1", "traits": "Shove", "category": "Unarmed", "damagedie": "d6", "damagetype": "B", "description": "You can over-pressurize your hydraulic lines to deliver a devastating blow. You gain a Piston Slam unarmed attack. It deals 1d6 Bludgeoning damage and has the Shove trait (allowing you to Shove enemies even if your hands are full).<br><br>On a critical hit with this attack, the target is pushed back 5 feet (as if you had successfully Shoved them)."}]}',	'You can over-pressurize your hydraulic lines to deliver a devastating blow.',	'0',	1,	'Droid',	'[{"heritage": "herDroidClass5"}]'),
('aftAmbushSalesman',	'ancJawa',	'Ambush Salesman',	'You are used to popping out of nowhere. If you roll Deception or Stealth for Initiative, you can Interact to draw a weapon as a free action immediately before the first round of combat begins.',	NULL,	'You are used to popping out of nowhere.',	'0',	5,	'Jawa',	'[{"skill": [{"id": ["sklDeception", "sklStealth"], "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftJunkTinker',	'ancJawa',	'Junk Tinker',	'You can fix anything with duct tape and a kick. You are trained in Crafting and gain the Jury-Rig skill feat. Additionally, you do not take the standard -2 penalty when using Shoddy items or items you have Jury-Rigged.',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaJuryRig", "type": "skill"}]}, "skill": {"skill": [{"id": "sklCrafting", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You can fix anything with duct tape and a kick.',	'0',	1,	'Jawa',	NULL),
('aftGangUp',	'ancJawa',	'Gang Up',	'Jawas are never alone. You can flank an enemy if it’s within reach of both of you and an ally—you and your ally don’t have to be on opposite sides. This benefits your allies as well as you, but only if they’re flanking with you, not each other. The other requirements for flanking must still be met.',	NULL,	'Jawas are never alone.',	'0',	5,	'Jawa',	NULL),
('aftSandcrawlerStride',	'ancJawa',	'Sandcrawler Stride',	'You are accustomed to moving through shifting dunes and cluttered cargo holds. You ignore Difficult Terrain caused by rubble, sand, junk, or scrap metal. You can move at full speed while Crawling.',	NULL,	'You are accustomed to moving through shifting dunes and cluttered cargo holds.',	'0',	5,	'Jawa',	NULL),
('aftPackScrounger',	'ancJawa',	'Pack Scrounger',	'You have an uncanny knack for finding value in trash. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Perception checks to Search. If you succeed at a Search check to find loot or salvage, you automatically find 10% more value (in raw materials or credits) than a non-Jawa would, representing small components others overlook.',	'{"perception": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Pack Scrounger", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Search.", "target": "all"}]}}',	'You have an uncanny knack for finding value in trash.',	'0',	1,	'Jawa',	NULL),
('aftUtini',	'ancJawa',	'"Utini!"',	'You shout the cry of the hunt!

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">"Utini!"</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 1</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Jawa</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Auditory</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Emotion</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>An enemy within 30 feet drops an item, falls Prone, or is reduced to 0 HP.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You shout the cry of the hunt! You and all allies within 30 feet gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Attack Rolls against that specific enemy (or the enemy closest to the downed opponent) until the start of your next turn.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actUtini", "name": "\"Utini!\"", "traits": "Jawa, Auditory, Emotion", "trigger": "An enemy within 30 feet drops an item, falls Prone, or is reduced to 0 HP.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You shout the cry of the hunt! You and all allies within 30 feet gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Attack Rolls against that specific enemy (or the enemy closest to the downed opponent) until the start of your next turn."}]}}',	'You shout the cry of the hunt!',	'0',	1,	'Jawa, Auditory, Emotion',	NULL),
('aftDiplomaticImmunity',	'ancIthorian',	'Diplomatic Immunity',	'Your presence is so commanding and peaceful that violence against you becomes mentally painful. Creatures attempting to attack the target must attempt a Will save against your Class DC each time.  If a creature succeeds at the save and attacks you, or if you take a hostile action, the effect is suppressed for 1d4 rounds before automatically reactivating.',	NULL,	'Your presence is so commanding and peaceful that violence against you becomes mentally painful.',	'0',	17,	'Ithorian, Mental, Visual',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftGentleGiant", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftIonSpecialist',	'ancJawa',	'Ion Specialist',	'You know exactly where to shoot a droid to fry its circuits without damaging the chassis. When you critically hit a creature with the Construct or Tech trait using an Ion or Electricity weapon, the target is Slowed 1 for 1 round (in addition to normal critical effects).',	NULL,	'You know exactly where to shoot a droid to fry its circuits without damaging the chassis.',	'0',	5,	'Jawa',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftJawaWeaponFamiliarity", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftAtmosphericFilter',	'ancKelDor',	'Atmospheric Filter',	'Your breath mask is a masterpiece of filtration technology. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to saving throws against inhaled poisons, gases, and airborne diseases. You can survive in a vacuum for 1 hour (using the air recycled in your mask) before you begin to suffocate.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Atmospheric Filter", "value": "+2 circumstance bonus against inhaled poisons, gases, and airborne diseases.", "target": "all"}]}]}',	'Your breath mask is a masterpiece of filtration technology.',	'0',	1,	'Kel Dor',	NULL),
('aftOffWorldBuyers',	'ancJawa',	'Off-World Buyers',	'You have a contact for everything. You can spend 1 hour communicating with the Jawa trade network. You can procure any common item of Level equal to or lower than your Level as if you were in a settlement of unlimited size. You must pay full price (plus a 10% "delivery fee"), but the item arrives within 24 hours via courier or drop-pod.',	NULL,	'You have a contact for everything.',	'0',	13,	'Jawa',	NULL),
('aftGoggleAugmentedVision',	'ancKelDor',	'Goggle-Augmented Vision',	'Your protective lenses are custom-ground for superior optics. You gain Darkvision. Additionally, you are immune to being Dazzled by bright light or flash-bang effects, as your goggles auto-dim instantly.',	'{"sense": [{"Darkvision": "60 feet"}], "defense": {"immunity": [{"type": "Dazzled", "source": "Goggle-Augmented Vision (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your protective lenses are custom-ground for superior optics.',	'0',	1,	'Kel Dor',	NULL),
('aftBaranDoSensitive',	'ancKelDor',	'Baran Do Sensitive',	'You possess the latent sensory abilities of the Baran Do Sages, allowing you to hear the "breath" of the universe. You become Trained in The Force skill. You can use The Force in place of Perception to Sense Motive and to Seek Force-sensitive creatures or other Force effects.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklTheForce", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You possess the latent sensory abilities of the Baran Do Sages, allowing you to hear the "breath" of the universe.',	'0',	1,	'Kel Dor',	NULL),
('aftStoicMagistrate',	'ancKelDor',	'Stoic Magistrate',	'Kel Dor culture prizes justice and emotional control. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Will saves against Emotion and Fear effects. If you roll a Success on a saving throw against an Emotion effect, you get a Critical Success instead.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Stoic Magistrate", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus against Emotion and Fear effects.", "target": "will"}]}]}',	'Kel Dor culture prizes justice and emotional control.',	'0',	1,	'Kel Dor, Mental',	NULL),
('aftLimitedTelepathy',	'ancKelDor',	'Limited Telepathy',	'You can communicate mentally with creatures within 30 feet. You can send simple messages and images. This communication is one-way (unless the target also has telepathy), but it transcends language barriers for simple concepts (like "Danger," "Go," or "Help").',	NULL,	'You can communicate mentally with creatures within 30 feet.',	'0',	5,	'Kel Dor, Mental, Linguistic',	NULL),
('aftShootFirst',	'ancRodian',	'Shoot First',	'Rodians are culturally aggressive and paranoid. When you roll Initiative, you can immediately Interact to Draw a Weapon as a free action. If you roll a Natural 20 on Initiative, you can also make a single ranged Strike as a free action before the first round begins.  The target is Off-Guard against this Strike.',	NULL,	'Rodians are culturally aggressive and paranoid.',	'0',	1,	'Rodian',	NULL),
('aftTheGreatMarket',	'ancJawa',	'The Great Market',	'You are the economy. You can sell items to black market contacts near-instantly from almost anywhere in the galaxy (subject to GM discretion) for their full resale value. Once per day, you can produce a consumable item (Grenade, Chem, Ammunition) of Level 15 or lower from your pockets as if you had bought it earlier. You do not pay for this item; you "found" it.',	NULL,	'You are the economy.',	'0',	17,	'Jawa',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftOffWorldBuyers", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftWaterDiscipline',	'ancTusken',	'Water Discipline',	'Your body is optimized for extreme dehydration. You require only one-quarter the daily water of a standard medium creature. You gain resistance to fire damage equal to half your level, representing your body''s conditioned resistance to extreme heat and burns.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Fire", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Water Discipline (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your body is optimized for extreme dehydration.',	'0',	9,	'Tusken Raider',	NULL),
('aftRubberySkeleton',	'ancSquib',	'Rubbery Skeleton',	'Your bones are surprisingly flexible. You gain the Quick Squeeze skill feat. Additionally, you treat Squeezing as difficult terrain rather than the usual slow movement, allowing you to move at half your Speed through tight spaces.',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaQuickSqueeze", "type": "skill"}]}}',	'Your bones are surprisingly flexible.',	'0',	5,	'Squib',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklAcrobatics", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftDesertGhost',	'ancJawa',	'Desert Ghost',	'You vanish into the shimmer of the heat. In any environment with Dim Light or Bright Light (but not Darkness), you can Hide even if observed, provided you are within 10 feet of Difficult Terrain (rocks, dunes, junk). You are effectively using the glare and camouflage to disappear.',	NULL,	'You vanish into the shimmer of the heat.',	'0',	13,	'Jawa',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftHeatHazeSurvivor", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftShortCircuit',	'ancJawa',	'Short Circuit',	'Your ion shots chain between targets. When you hit a target with an Ion or Electricity weapon, you can deal splash damage equal to your weapon''s minimum damage (e.g., 1 for a d6, 2 for a d8) to all adjacent creatures with the Construct or Tech trait.',	NULL,	'Your ion shots chain between targets.',	'0',	13,	'Jawa',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftIonSpecialist", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftPrecognitiveReflexes',	'ancKelDor',	'Precognitive Reflexes',	'You react to attacks before they are launched. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Initiative rolls. Additionally, you cannot be Surprised or caught Off-Guard during the first round of combat, as you foresaw the ambush.',	NULL,	'You react to attacks before they are launched.',	'0',	13,	'Kel Dor, Mental',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSagesWarning", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftLifeSense',	'ancKelDor',	'Life Sense',	'Your connection to the currents of life is profound. You gain Imprecise Life Sense out to 30 feet. You can detect the presence of living creatures within range even if they are Hidden or Invisible, though you cannot target them precisely without seeing them.',	'{"sense": [{"Life Sense": "Imprecise (30ft)"}]}',	'Your connection to the currents of life is profound.',	'0',	9,	'Kel Dor, Force Power, Mental',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftBaranDoSensitive", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftVacuumHardened',	'ancKelDor',	'Vacuum Hardened',	'Your hide is tough enough to withstand the void. You gain resistance to Cold damage equal to half your level. You do not take damage from the vacuum of space (decompression), though you still need your mask to breathe.',	'{"defense": {"immunity": [{"type": "Vacuum", "source": "Vacuum Hardened (Ancestry Feat)"}], "resistance": [{"type": "Cold", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Vacuum Hardened (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your hide is tough enough to withstand the void.',	'0',	5,	'Kel Dor',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftDorinsResilience", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftViciousConstriction',	'ancSavrip',	'Vicious Constriction',	'Once you get your massive arms around a target, the fight is effectively over. Whenever you successfully Grapple a creature, you automatically deal bludgeoning damage to that creature equal to your Strength modifier plus two dice of your unarmed attack damage. On a critical success, the target takes double this damage and is restrained.',	NULL,	'Once you get your massive arms around a target, the fight is effectively over.',	'0',	13,	'Mantellian Savrip',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklAthletics", "rank": "Expert"}]}]'),
('aftSharedSenses',	'ancKelDor',	'Shared Senses',	'You can link your mind with willing allies. You can maintain a telepathic bond with up to 4 allies within 1 mile. You can communicate clearly as if speaking. Furthermore, if you possess Darkvision, Life Sense, or See Invisibility, you can spend an Action to share those senses with your bonded allies for 1 minute.',	NULL,	'You can link your mind with willing allies.',	'0',	13,	'Kel Dor, Mental',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftLimitedTelepathy", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftElectricJudgment',	'ancKelDor',	'Electric Judgment',	'<p>You channel the &quot;Emerald Lightning&quot; of the Baran Do—a technique used to incapacitate rather than kill.</p>
<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Discharge</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 5</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Kel Dor</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Attack</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Electricity</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Range</strong>
      <span>30 feet</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Target</strong>
      <span>1 creature</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Make a ranged attack roll using The Force. This attack deals2d6 + your Level nonlethal Electricity damage.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> Double the damage, and the target is Clumsy 1 for 1 round as their muscles seize.<br><br><strong>Heightened (+4)</strong> The damage increases by 1d6 at Level 9, 13, and 17.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powDischarge", "name": "Discharge", "level": 5, "range": "30 feet", "target": "1 creature", "traits": "Kel Dor, Attack, Force Power, Electricity", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "Make a ranged attack roll using The Force. This attack deals2d6 + your Level nonlethal Electricity damage.\n\n**Critical Success** Double the damage, and the target is Clumsy 1 for 1 round as their muscles seize.\n\n**Heightened (+4)** The damage increases by 1d6 at Level 9, 13, and 17."}]}}',	'You channel the "Emerald Lightning" of the Baran Do—a technique used to incapacitate rather than kill.',	'0',	5,	'Kel Dor, Attack, Force Power, Electricity',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklTheForce", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftSquatStability',	'ancOrtolan',	'Squat Stability',	'You are built like a blue fire hydrant. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Fortitude or Reflex DC against attempts to Shove, Trip, or Overrun you.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Squat Stability", "value": "+2 circumstance bonus to DC against Shove, Trip, or Overrun.", "target": "all"}]}]}',	'You are built like a blue fire hydrant.',	'0',	1,	'Ortolan',	NULL),
('aftJizzWailerProdigy',	'ancOrtolan',	'Jizz-Wailer Prodigy',	'You were born with rhythm in your soul. You become Trained in Performance and Art Lore. If you are already trained, you gain a skill of your choice. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Performance checks when playing an instrument.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklPerformance", "rank": "Trained"}, {"id": "sklLoreArt", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You were born with rhythm in your soul.',	'0',	1,	'Ortolan',	NULL),
('aftFingerSensors',	'ancOrtolan',	'Finger-Sensors',	'Ortolans have sensitive organ-clusters in their fingertips. You don’t need to succeed at a flat check to target concealed creatures. You’re not off-guard to creatures that are hidden from you (unless you’re off-guard to them for reasons other than the hidden condition), and you need only a successful DC 5 flat check to target a hidden creature.

Additionally, you can perform Perception checks to "Search" a 5-foot square by touching it with your hands, even if you are blinded or in total darkness, with no penalty.',	NULL,	'Ortolans have sensitive organ-clusters in their fingertips.',	'0',	1,	'Ortolan',	NULL),
('aftBouncingBlueBall',	'ancOrtolan',	'Bouncing Blue Ball',	'You can tuck your limbs in and let gravity do the work. You can Tumble Through the space of an enemy larger than you without making an Acrobatics check. Additionally, when you Fall, you treat the fall distance as half for the purpose of calculating damage, as you bounce upon impact.',	NULL,	'You can tuck your limbs in and let gravity do the work.',	'0',	5,	'Ortolan, Move',	NULL),
('aftFeignedSimplicity',	'ancSavrip',	'Feigned Simplicity',	'You are used to the galaxy assuming you are nothing but a dumb beast, and you know exactly how to use that prejudice to your advantage. You become trained in Deception (or another skill if you are already trained). You can use Deception to roll for Initiative if you are pretending to be an unthinking animal before combat begins. If you do, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your first attack roll against a creature that hasn''t acted yet.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklDeception", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You are used to the galaxy assuming you are nothing but a dumb beast, and you know exactly how to use that prejudice to your advantage.',	'0',	1,	'Mantellian Savrip',	NULL),
('aftTrandoshanWeaponFamiliarity',	'ancTrandoshan',	'Trandoshan Weapon Familiarity',	'You have trained extensively with the brutal, specialized armory of your people to ensure no prey escapes. You have familiarity with weapons with the Trandoshan trait including the hunting sword. For the purpose of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons.

At 5th level, whenever you get a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.',	'{"attack": [{"weapon_familiarity": ["Trandoshan"]}]}',	'You have trained extensively with the brutal, specialized armory of your people to ensure no prey escapes.',	'0',	1,	'Trandoshan',	NULL),
('aftStrategicGirth',	'ancOrtolan',	'Strategic Girth',	'You are effectively a portable barricade. You provide Standard Cover (+2 AC) to any ally of your size or smaller who is standing directly behind you. Additionally, you can Shove enemies using your body weight (Athletics) without needing a free hand.',	NULL,	'You are effectively a portable barricade.',	'0',	9,	'Ortolan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSquatStability", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftTacticalSnacking',	'ancOrtolan',	'Tactical Snacking',	'You keep snacks in your pockets, pouches, and even cheek pouches.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Tactical Snacking</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 1</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Ortolan</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Manipulate</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per 10 minutes.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You consume a small, nutrient-dense food item. You gain Temporary Hit Points equal to 1 + your Level. These temporary hit points last for 1 minute.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actTacticalSnacking", "name": "Tactical Snacking", "traits": "Ortolan, Manipulate", "frequency": "Once per 10 minutes.", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You consume a small, nutrient-dense food item. You gain Temporary Hit Points equal to 1 + your Level. These temporary hit points last for 1 minute."}]}}',	'You keep snacks in your pockets, pouches, and even cheek pouches.',	'0',	1,	'Ortolan, Manipulate',	NULL),
('aftPowerLunch',	'ancOrtolan',	'Power Lunch',	'You eat with terrifying efficiency. You can use Tactical Snacking as a Free Action immediately after you roll Initiative. Additionally, when you drink a Potion or use a consumable healing item, you regain an additional 2 HP per damage die of the item (due to your superior metabolism).',	NULL,	'You eat with terrifying efficiency.',	'0',	5,	'Ortolan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftTacticalSnacking", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftAccompanist',	'ancOrtolan',	'Accompanist',	'You play best when supporting others. When you use the Aid action to help an ally''s Attack Roll or Skill Check, and you use Performance to do so (playing a rallying tune). A Critical Failure on the Aid check is treated as a regular Failure (no penalty), and a Success grants a +2 bonus (instead of +1).',	NULL,	'You play best when supporting others.',	'0',	5,	'Ortolan, Auditory',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklPerformance", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftMentalFortress',	'ancKelDor',	'Mental Fortress',	'Your mind is an ordered archive that rejects intrusion. You are immune to Detect Thoughts and similar mind-reading effects unless you allow them. If a creature attempts to read your mind and fails, they take Mental damage equal to your Level.',	NULL,	'Your mind is an ordered archive that rejects intrusion.',	'0',	9,	'Kel Dor, Mental',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftStoicMagistrate", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftSuctionCups',	'ancRodian',	'Suction Cups',	'Your fingers and toes end in suction cups. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks to Climb. Additionally, you have an incredible grip on your gear; you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Reflex DC against attempts to Disarm you.',	'{"skill": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Suction Cups", "value": "+2 circumstance bonus to Climb.", "target": "sklAthletics"}]}, "saving_throw": [{"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Suction Cups", "value": "+2 circumstance bonus to DC against Disarm.", "target": "reflex"}]}]}',	'Your fingers and toes end in suction cups.',	'0',	1,	'Rodian',	NULL),
('aftCompoundEyes',	'ancRodian',	'Compound Eyes',	'Your large, faceted eyes are evolved to spot movement in the twilight of Rodia. You gain Darkvision. Additionally, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Perception checks to Seek creatures that have moved since your last turn.',	'{"perception": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Compound Eyes", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Seek creatures that have moved since your last turn.", "target": "all"}]}}',	'Your large, faceted eyes are evolved to spot movement in the twilight of Rodia.',	'0',	1,	'Rodian',	NULL),
('aftPheromoneTracker',	'ancRodian',	'Pheromone Tracker',	'You can taste the pheromones targets leave behind. You gain Scent (Imprecise) with a range of 30 feet. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Survival checks to Track a creature that is Fatigued, Enfeebled, or below half HP.',	'{"sense": [{"Scent": "Imprecise (30ft)"}]}',	'You can taste the pheromones targets leave behind. ',	'0',	5,	'Rodian',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklSurvival", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftDeadlySniper',	'ancTusken',	'Deadly Sniper',	'You know exactly where to place a slug to ensure your target bleeds out on the dunes. Whenever you critically hit an off-guard creature with a cycler rifle, sniper weapon, or other single-shot projectile weapon, the target takes persistent bleed damage equal to 1d6 per weapon damage die, plus your Wisdom modifier.',	NULL,	'You know exactly where to place a slug to ensure your target bleeds out on the dunes.',	'0',	17,	'Tusken Raider',	'[{"attack": [{"weapon": [{"id": "wepCyclerRifle", "rank": "Master"}]}]}, {"attack": [{"group": [{"sniper": {"rank": "Master"}}]}]}]'),
('aftUrbanHunter',	'ancRodian',	'Urban Hunter',	'While some hunt in the jungle, you hunt in the ferrocrete canyons of city-planets. You become Trained in Stealth and Underworld Lore. You do not take the penalty for Moving while performing the Track activity if you are in an Urban environment.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklStealth", "rank": "Trained"}, {"id": "sklLoreUnderworld", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'While some hunt in the jungle, you hunt in the ferrocrete canyons of city-planets.',	'0',	1,	'Rodian',	NULL),
('aftThermalOptics',	'ancRodian',	'Thermal Optics',	'Your eyes can shift into the infrared spectrum. You can use an Action to focus your vision. For 1 minute, you ignore the Concealed condition from smoke, fog, or darkness for creatures that emit heat. This does not let you see through solid walls or ignore the Hidden condition, only Concealment.',	NULL,	'Your eyes can shift into the infrared spectrum. ',	'0',	5,	'Rodian',	NULL),
('aftFoodComa',	'ancOrtolan',	'Food Coma',	'You can sleep it off.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Nap</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">None</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 13</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Ortolan</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Healing</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You fall asleep for 10 minutes. At the end of the nap, you regain Hit Points equal to 50% of your maximum HP and remove the Fatigued and Enfeebled conditions. You must be undisturbed for the entire duration.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actNap", "name": "Nap", "traits": "Ortolan, Healing", "frequency": "Once per day.", "action_cost": null, "description": "You fall asleep for 10 minutes. At the end of the nap, you regain Hit Points equal to 50% of your maximum HP and remove the Fatigued and Enfeebled conditions. You must be undisturbed for the entire duration."}]}}',	'You can sleep it off.',	'0',	13,	'Ortolan, Healing',	NULL),
('aftAmbushHunter',	'ancTusken',	'Ambush Hunter',	'You excel at striking from concealment before your prey even knows they are being hunted. If you roll Stealth for initiative, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your initiative roll. If you act before a target in the first round of combat, that target is off-guard against your first melee or ranged Strike.',	'{"skill": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Ambush Hunter", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to your initiative.", "target": "sklStealth"}]}}',	'You excel at striking from concealment before your prey even knows they are being hunted.',	'0',	5,	'Tusken Raider',	NULL),
('aftThermalVisionMastery',	'ancRodian',	'Thermal Vision Mastery',	'Your infrared sight is always active. You gain Thermal Vision as a precise sense out to 60 feet. You automatically succeed at attempts to Seek creatures that are Hidden or Undetected only by darkness or invisibility (if they emit heat). Cold-blooded creatures or droids running cold are invisible to this specific sense.',	'{"sense": [{"Thermal Vision": "Precise (60ft)"}]}',	'Your infrared sight is always active.',	'0',	13,	'Rodian',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftThermalOptics", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftAmphibiousStalker',	'ancRodian',	'Amphibious Stalker',	'Rodia is a swamp planet, and you haven''t forgotten your roots. You gain a Swim Speed of 25 feet and can hold your breath for 1 hour. You can use the Stealth action while swimming even if you do not have cover, provided you are submerged.',	'{"speed": [{"swim": 25}]}',	'Rodia is a swamp planet, and you haven''t forgotten your roots.',	'0',	9,	'Rodian',	NULL),
('aftOversizedReach',	'ancSavrip',	'Oversized Reach',	'Your arms are so long that your knuckles practically drag on the floor. You can Interact with objects, open doors, or manipulate computer terminals up to 10 feet away. This does not increase your reach for melee Strikes.',	NULL,	'Your arms are so long that your knuckles practically drag on the floor.',	'0',	1,	'Mantellian Savrip',	NULL),
('aftSnipersPerch',	'ancRodian',	'Sniper''s Perch',	'You hang upside down or cling to vertical surfaces to get the perfect shot. If you are Climbing or clinging to a wall/ceiling, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Attack Rolls with ranged weapons against targets who are on lower elevation than you. Additionally, you are not Off-Guard while Climbing.',	NULL,	'You hang upside down or cling to vertical surfaces to get the perfect shot.',	'0',	13,	'Rodian',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftWallScuttler", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftMonCalamariWeaponFamiliarity',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Mon Calamari Weapon Familiarity',	'You are trained in the traditional weapons of the Mon Calamari Knights and the planetary defense forces. You have familiarity with weapons with the Mon Calamari trait including the spear-blaster. For the purpose of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons.

At 5th level, whenever you get a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.',	'{"attack": [{"weapon_familiarity": ["Mon Calamari"]}]}',	'You are trained in the traditional weapons of the Mon Calamari Knights and the planetary defense forces.',	'0',	1,	'Mon Calamari',	NULL),
('aftCorneredRat',	'ancRodian',	'Cornered Rat',	'Panic makes you dangerous. You are Quickened for 1 minute. You can only use the extra action to Stride, Step, or Seek.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Cornered Rat</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 9</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Rodian</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Emotion</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You are reduced to fewer than half your maximum Hit Points.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Panic makes you dangerous. You are Quickened for 1 minute. You can only use the extra action to Stride, Step, or Seek.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actCorneredRat", "name": "Cornered Rat", "traits": "Rodian, Emotion", "trigger": "You are reduced to fewer than half your maximum Hit Points.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "Panic makes you dangerous. You are Quickened for 1 minute. You can only use the extra action to Stride, Step, or Seek."}]}}',	'Panic makes you dangerous.',	'0',	9,	'Rodian, Emotion',	NULL),
('aftPerfectCamouflage',	'ancRodian',	'Perfect Camouflage',	'Your skin pigment shifts to match your surroundings perfectly. You can use the Hide action even while Observed. As long as you remain stationary, you are Invisible. If you move, you remain Hidden until the end of your turn.',	NULL,	'Your skin pigment shifts to match your surroundings perfectly.',	'0',	17,	'Rodian',	'[{"feat": [{"id": ["aftAmphibiousStalker", "aftUrbanHunter"], "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftDramaticEntrance',	'ancRodian',	'Dramatic Entrance',	'Rodian culture is theatrical; you love a good speech before the violence. When you roll Initiative, you can attempt to Demoralize one enemy as a free action. If you succeed, that enemy focuses its attention on you (imposing a -2 penalty to their attacks against anyone else) for 1 round.',	NULL,	'Rodian culture is theatrical; you love a good speech before the violence.',	'0',	5,	'Rodian, Emotion, Mental',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklIntimidation", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftTechnologicalMiracle',	'ancSquib',	'Technological Miracle',	'Once per day, you can perform a rapid repair or modification that defies logic. You can use a 3-action activity to touch a broken or destroyed technological object of up to 10 Bulk. The object is instantly restored to full Hit Points and functionality. Alternatively, you can touch a functioning device to allow it to function without a power source or ammunition for 1 hour.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Technological Miracle</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[three-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 17</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Squib</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You can perform a rapid repair or modification that defies logic. You touch a broken or destroyed technological object of up to 10 Bulk. The object is instantly restored to full Hit Points and functionality. Alternatively, you can touch a functioning device to allow it to function without a power source or ammunition for 1 hour.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actTechnologicalMiracle", "name": "Technological Miracle", "traits": "Squib", "frequency": "Once per day.", "action_cost": "[three-actions]", "description": "You can perform a rapid repair or modification that defies logic. You touch a broken or destroyed technological object of up to 10 Bulk. The object is instantly restored to full Hit Points and functionality. Alternatively, you can touch a functioning device to allow it to function without a power source or ammunition for 1 hour."}]}}',	'You can perform a rapid repair or modification that defies logic.',	'0',	17,	'Squib',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklCrafting", "rank": "Legendary"}]}]'),
('aftSeismicTremors',	'ancSullustan',	'Seismic Tremors',	'You can feel footsteps through the floor. You gain imprecise Tremorsense out to 30 feet. You can detect creatures touching the ground within this range, even if they are Invisible or behind walls.',	'{"sense": [{"Tremorsense": "Imprecise (30ft)"}]}',	'You can feel footsteps through the floor.',	'0',	5,	'Sullustan',	NULL),
('aftGeometryOfWar',	'ancSullustan',	'Geometry of War',	'You see the vectors of death before they happen. Your ranged attacks ignore all Cover (even Total Cover, provided the target is not fully enclosed in a sealed box). You are never Off-Guard (Flat-Footed) to ranged attacks, and you have a +4 circumstance bonus to AC against attacks made from beyond 30 feet, as you step out of the trajectory effortlessly.',	NULL,	'You see the vectors of death before they happen.',	'0',	17,	'Sullustan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftRicochetShot", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftRicochetShot',	'ancSullustan',	'Ricochet Shot',	'You know the geometry of the room so well you can bounce shots off walls. When you make a Ranged Strike with a firearm, you can ignore the Concealed condition. Additionally, you can target a creature that has Total Cover if there is a solid surface (wall/ceiling) nearby to bounce the shot off of. The target is treated as having Standard Cover (+2 AC) instead of Total Cover.',	'{"feat": [{"id": "aftSullustanWeaponFamiliarity", "type": "ancestry"}]}',	'You know the geometry of the room so well you can bounce shots off walls.',	'0',	9,	'Sullustan',	NULL),
('aftSubterraneanSovereign',	'ancSullustan',	'Subterranean Sovereign',	'You are one with the stone. You gain a burrow speed equal to your base land speed. You can burrow through solid stone (leaving a tunnel behind you) or loose earth. While burrowing, you have Tremorsense (Precise) out to 60 feet.',	'{"speed": [{"burrow": "{speed}"}]}',	'You are one with the stone.',	'0',	17,	'Sullustan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSeismicTremors", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftDarkDweller',	'ancSullustan',	'Dark-Dweller',	'You are most comfortable in the dark. When you are in an area of dim light or darkness, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC and Reflex saves.',	'{"ac": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Dark-Dweller", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus in dim light or darkness.", "target": "ac"}]}, "saving_throw": [{"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Dark-Dweller", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus in dim light or darkness.", "target": "reflex"}]}]}',	'You are most comfortable in the dark.',	'0',	5,	'Sullustan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftTunnelRat", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftCognitiveOverclock',	'ancCerean',	'Cognitive Overclock',	'Your binary brain operates at peak efficiency, effectively giving you two turns worth of mental processing every round. You are permanently Quickened 1. You can use the extra action only to Recall Knowledge, Seek, Sustain, or Analyze (for Analytical Defense).',	NULL,	'Your binary brain operates at peak efficiency, effectively giving you two turns worth of mental processing every round.',	'0',	17,	'Cerean, Mental',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftBinaryProcessing", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftConduitContortionist',	'ancSullustan',	'Conduit Contortionist',	'Your skeletal structure is partially cartilaginous, allowing you to dislocate joints at will to fit into maintenance shafts and exhaust ports that would block others. You can move through tight spaces as if you were two sizes smaller than you actually are (e.g., a Medium creature squeezing through a space meant for a Tiny creature). You treat these tight squeezes as difficult terrain rather than needing to use the Squeeze activity.',	NULL,	'Your skeletal structure is partially cartilaginous, allowing you to dislocate joints at will to fit into maintenance shafts and exhaust ports that would block others.',	'0',	13,	'Sullustan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftTunnelRat", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftToxicImmunity',	'ancSullustan',	'Toxic Immunity',	'Your lungs have adapted to filter out the worst of the galaxy''s atmosphere. You are immune to Inhaled Poisons and cannot be Sickened by gas or stench-based effects.',	NULL,	'Your lungs have adapted to filter out the worst of the galaxy''s atmosphere.',	'0',	9,	'Sullustan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftVolcanicAdaptation", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftEcholocationMastery',	'ancSullustan',	'Echolocation Mastery',	'Your senses paint a perfect 3D picture of the world. You gain Echolocation as a precise sense out to 30 feet. You can see creatures within this range clearly even in magical darkness or if you are blinded.',	'{"sense": [{"Echolocation": "Precise (30ft)"}]}',	'Your senses paint a perfect 3D picture of the world.',	'0',	13,	'Sullustan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": ["aftSonarSensitiveEars", "aftSeismicTremors"], "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftCoPilotsReflexes',	'ancSullustan',	'Co-Pilot''s Reflexes',	'You are the ultimate "guy in the chair." When you use the Aid action to assist an ally’s Piloting or Attack roll, you can do so as a Reaction instead of preparing an Action. If you roll a Critical Failure on the Aid check, you treat it as a normal Failure.',	NULL,	'You are the ultimate "guy in the chair."',	'0',	5,	'Sullustan',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklPiloting", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftAnalyticRepair',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Analytic Repair',	'You can bypass diagnostic protocols to apply emergency fixes to hardware in the heat of battle, much like a medic treats a soldier. You gain the Combat Repair skill feat, and your bonus HP repaired increases by +15 per DC increase instead of the normal +10 (so +15 at Expert, +30 at Master, +45 at Legendary).',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaCombatRepair", "type": "skill"}]}}',	'You can bypass diagnostic protocols to apply emergency fixes to hardware in the heat of battle, much like a medic treats a soldier.',	'0',	5,	'Mon Calamari',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftShipwrightHeritage", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftUnflappableCalculator',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Unflappable Calculator',	'Stress does not affect your math. You can Disable a Device or Pick a Lock in combat without taking the standard penalty for being threatened or distracted. If you roll a Critical Failure on a check to Disable a Device, it counts as a regular Failure (you don''t trigger it accidentally).',	NULL,	'Stress does not affect your math.',	'0',	9,	'Mon Calamari',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftShipwrightsHeritage", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftShipwrightHeritage',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Shipwright Heritage',	'You grew up maintaining the floating cities or star cruisers of your people. You become Trained in Crafting and Shipwright Lore. If you are already trained, you gain a skill of your choice. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Crafting checks to Repair items or vehicles.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklCrafting", "rank": "Trained"}, {"id": "sklLoreShipwright", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You grew up maintaining the floating cities or star cruisers of your people.',	'0',	1,	'Mon Calamari',	NULL),
('aftTacticalVoice',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Tactical Voice',	'Your voice carries distinctively over the din of battle. When you use the Point Out action to indicate the location of a hidden creature, the range at which allies can hear/understand you increases to 100 feet, and you do not need to share a language if you use basic hand signals alongside the shout.',	NULL,	'Your voice carries distinctively over the din of battle.',	'0',	1,	'Mon Calamari, Auditory',	NULL),
('aftSavripJaws',	'ancSavrip',	'Savrip Jaws',	'Your wide, reptilian maw is filled with sharp, formidable teeth. You gain a jaws unarmed attack that deals 1d6 piercing damage. Your jaws are and unarmed attack in the brawling weapon group.',	'{"weapon": [{"id": "natSavripJaws", "bulk": null, "name": "Savrip Jaws", "type": "Melee", "group": "Brawling", "hands": "1", "traits": null, "category": "Unarmed", "damagedie": "d6", "damagetype": "P", "description": "Your wide, reptilian maw is filled with sharp, formidable teeth. You gain a jaws unarmed attack that deals 1d6 piercing damage. Your jaws are and unarmed attack in the brawling weapon group."}]}',	'Your wide, reptilian maw is filled with sharp, formidable teeth.',	'0',	1,	'Mantellian Savrip',	NULL),
('aftBioLuminescentCommunication',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Bio-Luminescent Communication',	'You can flash patterns on your skin to communicate silently. You can communicate with other Mon Calamari or Quarren within 100 feet silently. Furthermore, you can cast emit dim light from your skin. In darkness, allies within 10 feet of you gain a +1 morale bonus to Will saves against Fear.',	NULL,	'You can flash patterns on your skin to communicate silently.',	'0',	9,	'Mon Calamari, Visual',	NULL),
('aftDeepSeaPhysiology',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Deep-Sea Physiology',	'You are built for the high-pressure depths of Dac. You gain resistance to Cold damage equal to half your level (minimum 1). You can see clearly underwater (ignoring the usual visual penalties for murky water) out to 60 feet.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Cold", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Deep-Sea Physiology (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'You are built for the high-pressure depths of Dac.',	'0',	1,	'Mon Calamari',	NULL),
('aftCurrentDancer',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Current Dancer',	'You move with the flow of battle, just as you move with the ocean currents. You gain a Swim Speed of 25 feet. Additionally, while you are in water or zero-gravity, you can Step 10 feet instead of 5 feet.',	'{"speed": [{"swim": 25}]}',	'You move with the flow of battle, just as you move with the ocean currents.',	'0',	1,	'Mon Calamari',	NULL),
('aftPanoramicDefense',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Panoramic Defense',	'It is difficult to catch you unaware. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your Reflex DC against attempts to Feint or Create a Diversion against you. You are not Off-Guard to creatures due to being Flanked, unless the flanking creatures are higher level than you.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Panoramic Defense", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to DC against Feint or Create a Diversion.", "target": "reflex"}]}]}',	'It is difficult to catch you unaware.',	'0',	5,	'Mon Calamari',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftIndependentEyes", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftRylothianGrace',	'ancTwilek',	'Rylothian Grace',	'Your center of gravity is perfectly offset by your lekku, allowing for acrobatic feats that defy standard humanoid physics. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Acrobatics checks to Balance. If you roll a Success on a Balance check, you get a Critical Success instead. You are not Off-Guard (Flat-Footed) while Balancing.',	'{"skill": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Rylothian Grace", "value": "+2 circumstance bonus to Balance.", "target": "sklAcrobatics"}]}}',	'Your center of gravity is perfectly offset by your lekku, allowing for acrobatic feats that defy standard humanoid physics.',	'0',	1,	'Twi''lek',	NULL),
('aftLekkuCypher',	'ancTwilek',	'Lekku Cypher',	'You are fluent in the silent, subtle language of head-tail twitching used by your people to communicate under the noses of guards and slavers. You can communicate silently with other creatures who know Twi''leki (Lekku) Sign Language. You can convey complex tactical information silently to allies within 30 feet, provided they can see you. If you are restrained or bound, you can still communicate fully as long as your head is free.',	NULL,	'You are fluent in the silent, subtle language of head-tail twitching used by your people to communicate under the noses of guards and slavers.',	'0',	1,	'Twi''lek, Linguistic, Visual',	NULL),
('aftOmniscientSight',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Omniscient Sight',	'Your independent eyes process visual data faster than a computer. You are immune to being Off-Guard for any reason (including Feints, Hidden attackers, or Paralyzed conditions—your eyes see it coming even if your body can''t move). You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against any attack that originates from within 20 feet of you.',	NULL,	'Your independent eyes process visual data faster than a computer.',	'0',	17,	'Mon Calamari',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftPanoramicDefense", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftFleetTactics',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Fleet Tactics',	'Your designate ability improves. When you use Designate Target, all allies who hit the target deal the extra precision damage until the start of your next turn, not just the first ally.',	NULL,	'Your designate ability improves.',	'0',	13,	'Mon Calamari',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSquadCommander", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftArtfulEscape',	'ancTwilek',	'Artful Escape',	'You have trained your body to twist out of grips that would hold a rigid skeleton fast, turning a retreat into a tactical advantage. When you roll a Success on a check to Escape using Acrobatics, you get a Critical Success instead. Additionally, if you use the 5-foot Stride to leave the reach of the creature that was grabbing you, that creature is Off-Guard to your next attack before the end of your next turn.',	NULL,	'You have trained your body to twist out of grips that would hold a rigid skeleton fast, turning a retreat into a tactical advantage.',	'0',	1,	'Twi''lek',	NULL),
('aftParlorDancersGuile',	'ancTwilek',	'Parlor Dancer''s Guile',	'You know how to use your physical presence and the hypnotic movement of your lekku to lower an enemy''s guard. You are trained in Performance and gain the Fascinating Performance skill feat. Additionally, when you Feint, you can use Performance instead of Deception.',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaFascinatingPerformance", "type": "skill"}]}, "skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklPerformance", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You know how to use your physical presence and the hypnotic movement of your lekku to lower an enemy''s guard.',	'0',	1,	'Twi''lek',	NULL),
('aftVoidSwimmer',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Void-Swimmer',	'You treat the vacuum of space like water. You gain a Fly Speed equal to your Speed, but only in zero-gravity environments. Additionally, you can hold your breath for 1 hour, allowing you to survive hull breaches with ease.',	NULL,	'You treat the vacuum of space like water.',	'0',	13,	'Mon Calamari',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftCurrentDancer", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftSensoryFingers',	'ancOrtolan',	'Sensory Fingers',	'Your fingertips can feel vibrations through the floor. You gain Tremorsense (Imprecise) with a range of 30 feet. You can pinpoint the location of creatures touching the ground within this range, though they are still considered Hidden from you unless you can see them.',	'{"sense": [{"Tremorsense": "Imprecise (30ft)"}]}',	'Your fingertips can feel vibrations through the floor.',	'0',	9,	'Ortolan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftFingerSensors", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftLongArmedSweeper',	'ancSavrip',	'Long-Armed Sweeper',	'Your incredibly long, muscular arms allow you to manage crowds with ease. You gain a claw unarmed attack that deals 1d4 slashing damage. Your claws are in the brawling weapon group and possess the agile and sweep traits.',	'{"weapon": [{"id": "natSavripClaws", "bulk": null, "name": "Savrip Claws", "type": "Melee", "group": "Brawling", "hands": "1", "traits": "Agile, Sweep", "category": "Unarmed", "damagedie": "d4", "damagetype": "S", "description": "Your incredibly long, muscular arms allow you to manage crowds with ease. You gain a claw unarmed attack that deals 1d4 slashing damage. Your claws are in the brawling weapon group and possess the agile and sweep traits."}]}',	'Your incredibly long, muscular arms allow you to manage crowds with ease.',	'0',	1,	'Mantellian Savrip',	NULL),
('aftPercussiveMaintenance',	'ancUgnaught',	'Percussive Maintenance',	'You know exactly where to hit a machine to jolt a loose servo back into place or realign a Gyro—a technique that works once, but requires actual repairs if tried again.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Percussive Maintenance</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Ugnaught</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Manipulate</span>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You strike a Construct creature, Droid, or vehicle with any Bludgeoning weapon (including an improvised weapon or fist).<br><br>If the target is a willing Ally: Attempt a Crafting check against the target''s Level DC. On a success, the target regains 2d8 Hit Points. The healing increases to 4d8 at Level 9, 6d8 at Level 13, and 8d8 at Level 17. Regardless of the result, the target is temporarily immune to your Percussive Maintenance for 24 hours.<br><br>If the target is an Enemy: Make a Melee Strike. If you hit, you deal your normal damage plus 1d6 additional damage (this extra damage ignores Hardness).
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actPercussiveMaintenance", "name": "Percussive Maintenance", "traits": "Ugnaught, Manipulate", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You strike a Construct creature, Droid, or vehicle with any Bludgeoning weapon (including an improvised weapon or fist).\n\nIf the target is a willing Ally: Attempt a Crafting check against the target''s Level DC. On a success, the target regains 2d8 Hit Points. The healing increases to 4d8 at Level 9, 6d8 at Level 13, and 8d8 at Level 17. Regardless of the result, the target is temporarily immune to your Percussive Maintenance for 24 hours.\n\nIf the target is an Enemy: Make a Melee Strike. If you hit, you deal your normal damage plus 1d6 additional damage (this extra damage ignores Hardness)."}]}}',	'You know exactly where to hit a machine to jolt a loose servo back into place or realign a Gyro—a technique that works once, but requires actual repairs if tried again.',	'0',	5,	'Ugnaught, Manipulate',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklCrafting", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftSavripLore',	'ancSavrip',	'Savrip Lore',	'You have learned to navigate the complex underworld that frequently tries to exploit your kind. You become trained in Athletics and Thievery. If you would automatically become trained in one of those skills, you instead become trained in a skill of your choice. You also become trained in Underworld Lore.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklAcrobatics", "rank": "Trained"}, {"id": "sklThievery", "rank": "Trained"}, {"id": "sklLoreUnderworld", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You have learned to navigate the complex underworld that frequently tries to exploit your kind.',	'0',	1,	'Mantellian Savrip',	NULL),
('aftServantsShadow',	'ancTwilek',	'Servant''s Shadow',	'You are a master of social camouflage, able to fade into the background of a scene by appearing harmless or unimportant. In social or urban environments, you can use Deception instead of Stealth to Hide and Sneak. Additionally, you can Hide while Observed provided you are within 15 feet of at least two other creatures (allies, enemies, or bystanders), as you blend into the "crowd" rather than relying on physical cover.',	NULL,	'You are a master of social camouflage, able to fade into the background of a scene by appearing harmless or unimportant.',	'0',	5,	'Twi''lek',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklDeception", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftLekkuTremors',	'ancTwilek',	'Lekku Tremors',	'Your head-tails are sensitive to the slightest change in air pressure or vibration, a trait evolved to sense storms in the Badlands. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Perception checks. Additionally, you gain imprecise Tremorsense out to 15 feet, allowing you to sense invisible creatures touching the ground near you.',	'{"perception": {"bonus": [{"type": "circumstance", "amount": "1", "source": "Lekku Tremors (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your head-tails are sensitive to the slightest change in air pressure or vibration, a trait evolved to sense storms in the Badlands.',	'0',	5,	'Twi''lek',	NULL),
('aftLegendaryNomad',	'ancTusken',	'Legendary Nomad',	'You are an unparalleled master of the wastes, capable of reading the shifting dunes to find shelter where none seemingly exists. You and up to five allies traveling with you can survive indefinitely in hostile environments without taking damage from severe heat, severe cold, or regional sandstorms. Additionally, whenever you roll a Survival check, if your rolled result on the d20 is less than 10, you treat it as a 10.',	NULL,	'You are an unparalleled master of the wastes, capable of reading the shifting dunes to find shelter where none seemingly exists.',	'0',	17,	'Tusken Raider',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklSurvival", "rank": "Master"}]}]'),
('aftClanBoundResolve',	'ancTwilek',	'Clan-Bound Resolve',	'The history of your people is one of survival against occupation; your mind is a fortress. If you roll a Success on a Will save against a Mental or Emotion effect, you get a Critical Success instead.',	NULL,	'The history of your people is one of survival against occupation; your mind is a fortress.',	'0',	13,	'Twi''lek',	NULL),
('aftMemoryOfTheKalikori',	'ancTwilek',	'Memory of the Kalikori',	'Your lekku connect you to the genetic memory of your clan totem (Kalikori), granting you the skills of your ancestors for a brief moment.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Memory of the Kalikori</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[free-action]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 17</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Twi''lek</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Mental</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You are about to attempt a Skill Check in which you are less than Legendary.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You are treated as Legendary in that skill for this specific check. You gain a +2 status bonus to the roll.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actMemoryOfTheKalikori", "name": "Memory of the Kalikori", "traits": "Twi''lek, Mental", "trigger": "You are about to attempt a Skill Check in which you are less than Legendary.", "frequency": "Once per day.", "action_cost": "[free-action]", "description": "You are treated as Legendary in that skill for this specific check. You gain a +2 status bonus to the roll."}]}}',	'Your lekku connect you to the genetic memory of your clan totem (Kalikori), granting you the skills of your ancestors for a brief moment.',	'0',	17,	'Twi''lek, Mental',	NULL),
('aftIndustrialResilience',	'ancUgnaught',	'Industrial Resilience',	'Generations of working in the toxic fumes of Tibanna gas platforms and droid foundries have hardened your lungs. You gain resistance to Poison damage equal to half your level (minimum 1). You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Saving Throws against Inhaled Poisons, gases, and airborne diseases.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Poison", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Industrial Resilience (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Generations of working in the toxic fumes of Tibanna gas platforms and droid foundries have hardened your lungs.',	'0',	1,	'Ugnaught',	NULL),
('aftIndenturedStamina',	'ancUgnaught',	'Indentured Stamina',	'You are used to 20-hour shifts and heavy lifting. You are trained in Athletics and gain the Hefty Hauler skill feat. Additionally, you ignore the penalty to AC and saving throws from the Fatigued condition, though you still cannot use Exploration activities.',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaHeftyHauler", "type": "skill"}]}, "skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklAthletics", "rank": "Trained"}]}}',	'You are used to 20-hour shifts and heavy lifting.',	'0',	1,	'Ugnaught',	NULL),
('aftToolWielder',	'ancUgnaught',	'Tool Wielder',	'To an Ugnaught, a heavy wrench is just a mace that tightens bolts. You do not take the -2 penalty for using Improvised Weapons, provided the object is a tool of some kind (hammer, wrench, pry bar, welder). Additionally, when you attack with a tool, it gains the Shove weapon trait.',	NULL,	'To an Ugnaught, a heavy wrench is just a mace that tightens bolts.',	'0',	1,	'Ugnaught',	NULL),
('aftSaboteursInsight',	'ancChubbit',	'Saboteur’s Insight',	'You have a generational hatred of massive industrial machinery and know exactly which wires to cut. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Thievery checks to Disable a Device and Crafting checks to Sabotage. If you roll a critical failure on a check to disable an electronic trap or technological hazard, you get a failure instead.',	'{"skill": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Saboteur’s Insight", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Sabotage.", "target": "sklCrafting"}, {"name": "Saboteur’s Insight", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Disable a Device.", "target": "sklThievery"}]}}',	'You have a generational hatred of massive industrial machinery and know exactly which wires to cut.',	'0',	9,	'Chubbit',	'[{"skill": [{"id": ["sklCrafting", "sklThievery"], "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftDroidDisassembler',	'ancUgnaught',	'Droid Disassembler',	'You know how to take them apart faster than they were put together. When you hit a creature with the Construct or Tech trait, you ignore Hardness equal to your Level. If you score a Critical Hit against a Construct, it is Slowed 1 for 1 round as a servo comes loose.',	NULL,	'You know how to take them apart faster than they were put together.',	'0',	5,	'Ugnaught',	NULL),
('aftGantryWalker',	'ancUgnaught',	'Gantry Walker',	'You are accustomed to fighting on suspended platforms and narrow catwalks without railings. You gain the Combat Climber skill feat. Additionally, you are not Off-Guard when you are Balancing or Climbing, and you can move at your full Speed while Balancing.',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaCombatClimber", "type": "skill"}]}}',	'You are accustomed to fighting on suspended platforms and narrow catwalks without railings.',	'0',	5,	'Ugnaught',	NULL),
('aftParalyticVenom',	'ancSavrip',	'Paralytic Venom',	'Your biology produces a mild paralytic toxin that you can secrete into your bite. Whenever you score a critical hit with your jaws unarmed attack, the target must succeed at a Fortitude save against your Class DC or become clumsy 1 for 1 round.',	NULL,	'Your biology produces a mild paralytic toxin that you can secrete into your bite.',	'0',	5,	'Mantellian Savrip, Poison',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftSavripJaws", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftScrapIntuition',	'ancUgnaught',	'Scrap Intuition',	'You can assess the value of "junk" instantly. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Crafting checks. When you Scavenge or Salvage materials, you gain 10% more raw materials (in credit value) than a standard success, representing usable components others would discard.',	'{"skill": {"bonus": [{"id": "sklCrafting", "type": "circumstance", "amount": "1", "source": "Scrap Intuition (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'You can assess the value of "junk" instantly.',	'0',	1,	'Ugnaught',	NULL),
('aftDanceOfTheSevenWinds',	'ancTwilek',	'Dance of the Seven Winds',	'You enter a trance of pure kinetic flow, moving constantly even when standing still.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Dance of the Seven Winds</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 17</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Twi''lek</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Stance</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You are unarmored or wearing Light Armor.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You gain the following benefits:<br><br>- You gain a +1 status bonus to AC.<br>- You are immune to the Grabbed, Restrained, and Prone conditions.<br>- If you move at least 10 feet during your turn, you gain Concealment until the start of your next turn.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDanceOfTheSevenWinds", "name": "Dance of the Seven Winds", "traits": "Twi''lek, Stance", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You gain the following benefits:\n\n- You gain a +1 status bonus to AC.\n- You are immune to the Grabbed, Restrained, and Prone conditions.\n- If you move at least 10 feet during your turn, you gain Concealment until the start of your next turn.", "requirements": "You are unarmored or wearing Light Armor."}]}}',	'You enter a trance of pure kinetic flow, moving constantly even when standing still.',	'0',	17,	'Twi''lek, Stance',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftRylothianGrace", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftGruffNegotiator',	'ancUgnaught',	'Gruff Negotiator',	'Ugnaughts speak plainly and expect fair value for their labor. You can use Intimidation instead of Diplomacy to Make an Impression or Request something, provided the interaction involves a business transaction, contract, or trade. (You aren''t scaring them; you are just being aggressively professional).',	NULL,	'Ugnaughts speak plainly and expect fair value for their labor.',	'0',	1,	'Ugnaught',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklIntimidation", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftKineticCalibration',	'ancSavrip',	'Kinetic Calibration',	'You take great joy in fixing complex machinery while making it look like you''re just smashing it. You can use your Athletics modifier instead of your Crafting modifier when attempting to Repair an item. When you do so, the action gains the auditory trait, as you physically pound the console or engine block into precise alignment.',	NULL,	'You take great joy in fixing complex machinery while making it look like you''re just smashing it.',	'0',	5,	'Mantellian Savrip',	'[{"attribute": [{"int": 1}]}]'),
('aftLethalNeurotoxin',	'ancSavrip',	'Lethal Neurotoxin',	'Your biological toxin matures into a highly potent, fast-acting strain. Whenever a creature fails its Fortitude save against your Paralytic Venom or Venomous Spit, it is also slowed 1 for 1 round. On a critical failure, it is stunned 1.',	NULL,	'Your biological toxin matures into a highly potent, fast-acting strain.',	'0',	17,	'Mantellian Savrip, Poison',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftParalyticVenom", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftCanopyClimber',	'ancWookiee',	'Canopy Climber',	'Your retractable climbing claws—while taboo to use in combat—make you a natural in vertical environments. You gain a climb speed of 15 feet. You are not off-guard while climbing.',	'{"speed": [{"climb": 15}]}',	'Your retractable climbing claws—while taboo to use in combat—make you a natural in vertical environments.',	'0',	1,	'Wookiee',	NULL),
('aftSquadCommander',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Squad Commander',	'You coordinate fire to exploit enemy weaknesses.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Designate Target</h3>
