  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You roll a Critical Failure on a Saving Throw or skill check.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You treat the result as a Critical Success instead.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actOneInAMillion", "name": "One in a Million", "traits": "Human, Fortune", "trigger": "You roll a Critical Failure on a Saving Throw or skill check.", "frequency": "Once per day.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You treat the result as a Critical Success instead."}]}}',	'The probability of surviving this scenario is approximately 3,720 to 1. You like those odds.',	'0',	17,	'Human, Fortune',	NULL),
('aftSpiritOfTheMother',	'ancIthorian',	'Spirit of the Mother',	'You carry the spirit of Ithor with you. You can ask questions of and receive answers from plants and fungi, but the spell doesn''t make them more friendly or intelligent than normal. Most normal plants and fungi have a distinctive view of the world around them, so they don''t recognize details about creatures or know anything about the world beyond their immediate vicinity. Cunning plant or fungus monsters are likely to be terse and evasive, while less intelligent ones often make inane comments.

Plant creatures will never treat you as hostile unless you attack them first.',	NULL,	'You carry the spirit of Ithor with you.',	'0',	9,	'Ithorian',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftMotherJunglesDisciple", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftDeepPressureAdaptation',	'ancGungan',	'Deep Pressure Adaptation',	'Your body is hardened against the crushing depths. You gain resistance to Cold damage equal to half your level (minimum 1). You act normally in high-gravity environments and cannot be Sickened by pressure changes or motion sickness.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Cold", "amount": "max(1, level // 2)", "source": "Deep Pressure Adaptation (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your body is hardened against the crushing depths.',	'0',	9,	'Gungan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftHydroDynamic", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftVolcanicSkin',	'ancSullustan',	'Volcanic Skin',	'Your skin hardens into a heat-dispersing hide. You gain resistance 10 to Fire damage. If you take Fire damage from an adjacent enemy (or an enemy touches you), you can use your Reaction to deal 2d6 Fire damage back to them as your skin flares with absorbed heat.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Fire", "amount": "10", "source": "Volcanic Skin (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your skin hardens into a heat-dispersing hide.',	'0',	13,	'Sullustan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftVolcanicAdaptation", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftThickSkull',	'ancGamorrean',	'Thick Skull',	'Your cranial plating is incredibly dense.

You gain resistance to Piercing and Slashing damage from critical hits equal to your level.  

You gain immunity from critical hits that deal Bludgeoning damage -- the attacker rolls normal damage rather than double and does not add extra effects like Deadly or Fatal. The attacker still triggers any other Critical Specialization effects (like being knocked prone), but the damage spike is negated.',	'{"defense": {"immunity": [{"type": "Critical Hits (Bludgeoning)", "source": "Thick Skull (Ancestry Feat)"}], "resistance": [{"type": "Piercing", "amount": "{level}", "source": "Thick Skull (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Slashing", "amount": "{level}", "source": "Thick Skull (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your cranial plating is incredibly dense.',	'0',	13,	'Gamorrean',	NULL),
('aftHeatHazeSurvivor',	'ancJawa',	'Heat Haze Survivor',	'Your heavy robes are actually a sophisticated moisture-recapture system. You gain resistance to Fire damage equal to half your level (minimum 1). You are immune to environmental heat effects and can go without water for 3 days before making Fortitude checks.',	'{"defense": {"immunity": [{"type": "Environmental Heat", "source": "Heat Haze Survivor (Ancestry Feat)"}], "resistance": [{"type": "Fire", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Heat Haze Survivor (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your heavy robes are actually a sophisticated moisture-recapture system.',	'0',	1,	'Jawa',	NULL),
('aftDorinsResilience',	'ancKelDor',	'Dorin’s Resilience',	'Your body is evolved to withstand the crushing pressure and violent storms of Dorin. You gain resistance to Electricity damage equal to half your level (minimum 1). You treat winds (natural or magical) as one step less severe.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Electricity", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Dorin’s Resilience (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your body is evolved to withstand the crushing pressure and violent storms of Dorin.',	'0',	1,	'Kel Dor',	NULL),
('aftVolcanicAdaptation',	'ancSullustan',	'Volcanic Adaptation',	'Your species evolved on a world of magma and ash. You gain resistance to Fire damage equal to half your level (minimum 1). Additionally, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Saving Throws against Inhaled Poisons or volcanic gases.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Fire", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Volcanic Adaptation (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your species evolved on a world of magma and ash.',	'0',	1,	'Sullustan',	NULL),
('aftBrightLandsEndurance',	'ancTwilek',	'Bright Lands Endurance',	'Your ancestors evolved on the scorching day-side of tidally locked Ryloth, granting you exceptional thermal regulation. You gain resistance to Fire damage equal to half your level (minimum 1). You treat environmental heat effects as one step less severe.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Fire", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Bright Lands Endurance (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your ancestors evolved on the scorching day-side of tidally locked Ryloth, granting you exceptional thermal regulation.',	'0',	1,	'Twi''lek',	NULL),
('aftHyperSensoryAlertness',	'ancChubbit',	'Hyper-Sensory Alertness',	'Your highly complex nervous system processes environmental stimuli faster than most species can comprehend. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Perception checks for initiative.',	'{"perception": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Hyper-Sensory Alertness", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus for initiative.", "target": "perception"}]}}',	'Your highly complex nervous system processes environmental stimuli faster than most species can comprehend.',	'0',	1,	'Chubbit',	NULL),
('aftCombatCalculation',	'ancCerean',	'Combat Calculation',	'Your analysis reveals the structural weak points of your enemy. When you succeed at your Analytical Defense check, in addition to the AC bonus, your attacks against that creature ignore the first 5 points of resistance (to physical or energy damage) for 1 minute.',	NULL,	'Your analysis reveals the structural weak points of your enemy.',	'0',	13,	'Cerean',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftAnalyticalDefense", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftThickSkinned',	'ancOrtolan',	'Thick-Skinned',	'Your skin is like leather armor. You gain resistance 5 to all physical damage (Bludgeoning, Piercing, Slashing).',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Bludgeoning", "amount": "5", "source": "Thick-Skinned (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Piercing", "amount": "5", "source": "Thick-Skinned (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Slashing", "amount": "5", "source": "Thick-Skinned (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your skin is like leather armor.',	'0',	13,	'Ortolan',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftInsulatedBlubber", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftInsulatedBlubber',	'ancOrtolan',	'Insulated Blubber',	'Your body is covered in a thick layer of fat and fuzz designed for cold climates. You gain resistance to Cold damage equal to half your level (minimum 1). You treat environmental cold effects as one step less severe.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Cold", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Insulated Blubber (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your body is covered in a thick layer of fat and fuzz designed for cold climates.',	'0',	1,	'Ortolan',	NULL),
('aftMasterOfStorms',	'ancIktotchi',	'Master of Storms',	'You are immune to the Deafened condition (often caused by thunder/explosions) and gain resistance 5 to Sonic damage.',	'{"defense": {"immunity": [{"type": "Deafened", "source": "Master of Storms (Ancestry Feat)"}], "resistance": [{"type": "Sonic", "amount": "5", "source": "Master of Storms (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'You are immune to the Deafened condition (often caused by thunder/explosions) and gain Resistance 5 to Sonic damage.',	'0',	13,	'Iktotchi',	NULL),
('aftPredatorsResilience',	'ancTrandoshan',	'Predator''s Resilience',	'You gain resistance 3 to all physical damage (bludgeoning, piercing, slashing) thanks to your thickened hide and pain tolerance.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Bludgeoning", "amount": "3", "source": "Predator''s Resilience (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Piercing", "amount": "3", "source": "Predator''s Resilience (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Slashing", "amount": "3", "source": "Predator''s Resilience (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'You gain resistance 3 to all physical damage (bludgeoning, piercing, slashing) thanks to your thickened hide and pain tolerance.',	'0',	13,	'Trandoshan',	NULL),
('aftSandcrawlerSovereign',	'ancJawa',	'Sandcrawler Sovereign',	'You fight with the durability of a fortress. You gain resistance 5 to all Energy damage (Acid, Cold, Electricity, Fire, Plasma, and Sonic), and your Bulk limit is doubled. You can repair a Broken item you are holding as a 1-Action activity restoring 10 HP.',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Acid", "amount": "5", "source": "Sandcrawler Sovereign (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Cold", "amount": "5", "source": "Sandcrawler Sovereign (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Electricity", "amount": "5", "source": "Sandcrawler Sovereign (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Fire", "amount": "5", "source": "Sandcrawler Sovereign (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Plasma", "amount": "5", "source": "Sandcrawler Sovereign (Ancestry Feat)"}, {"type": "Sonic", "amount": "5", "source": "Sandcrawler Sovereign (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'You fight with the durability of a fortress.',	'0',	17,	'Jawa',	NULL),
('aftIndependentEyes',	'ancMonCalamari',	'Independent Eyes',	'Your large eyes can move independently, allowing you to scan two different fields of view simultaneously. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Perception checks. Additionally, you can perform the Search activity in a 10-foot burst (instead of a 5-foot square) with a single action.',	'{"perception": {"bonus": [{"type": "circumstance", "amount": "1", "source": "Independent Eyes (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your large eyes can move independently, allowing you to scan two different fields of view simultaneously.',	'0',	1,	'Mon Calamari',	NULL),
('aftSonarSensitiveEars',	'ancSullustan',	'Sonar-Sensitive Ears',	'Your large ears pick up echoes others miss. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Perception checks. If a creature is Hidden or Undetected within 30 feet, and they make a sound (move, speak, attack), you reduce the flat check DC to target them from 11 to 9.',	'{"perception": {"bonus": [{"type": "circumstance", "amount": "1", "source": "Sonar-Sensitive Ears (Ancestry Feat)"}]}}',	'Your large ears pick up echoes others miss.',	'0',	1,	'Sullustan',	NULL),
('aftDebrisHurler',	'ancSavrip',	'Debris Hurler',	'You don''t always need a blaster when you can just throw the environment at your enemies. You can use the Interact action to pick up a piece of heavy debris (a crate, a chunk of masonry, a broken droid) and throw it as a ranged Strike. This improvised weapon deals 1d6 bludgeoning damage and has a range increment of 20 feet.',	NULL,	'You don''t always need a blaster when you can just throw the environment at your enemies.',	'0',	5,	'Mantellian Savrip',	NULL),
('aftHeavyOrdnanceHauler',	'ancSavrip',	'Heavy Ordnance Hauler',	'Because of your massive frame and low center of gravity, you excel at stabilizing heavy weaponry that would knock smaller species off their feet. You reduce the Bulk of any heavy weapon you carry by 1. Additionally, when using weapons with the Auto-Fire or Area Fire traits, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to the DC of the saving throws forced by those actions.',	'{"need": "fix"}',	'Because of your massive frame and low center of gravity, you excel at stabilizing heavy weaponry that would knock smaller species off their feet.',	'0',	9,	'Mantellian Savrip',	NULL),
('aftDeepDesertSurvivalist',	'ancTusken',	'Deep Desert Survivalist',	'You are adept at surviving in environments that would easily kill an unprepared off-worlder. You become trained in Survival. If you would automatically become trained in Survival, you instead become trained in a skill of your choice. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Survival checks to Sense Direction or Subsist in desert or badland environments, and you treat environmental heat effects as one step less severe.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklSurvival", "rank": "Trained"}], "conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Deep Desert Survivalist", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Sense Direction or Subsist in desert or badland environments.", "target": "sklSurvival"}]}}',	'You are adept at surviving in environments that would easily kill an unprepared off-worlder.',	'0',	1,	'Tusken Raider',	NULL),
('aftScurry',	'ancChubbit',	'Scurry',	'You are incredibly adept at darting between the legs of larger adversaries. You can move through the space of any creature that is Medium or larger, treating that space as difficult terrain. (You still cannot end your turn in a creature''s space).',	NULL,	'You are incredibly adept at darting between the legs of larger adversaries.',	'0',	1,	'Chubbit, Move',	NULL),
('aftTargetingComputer',	'ancDroid',	'Targeting Computer',	'You can lock onto a target for enhanced accuracy.  You gain the Lock On action.

