('aftUniversalTranslator',	'ancDroid',	'Universal Translator',	'Your core design allows you to engage with any sentient entity.  You are trained in Society and gain the Translate action. 

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
