('aftMachineWhisperer',	'ancAnzellan',	'Machine Whisperer',	'You speak the universal language of root-access override codes and logic paradoxes. You can force even hostile machines to accept you as their administrator.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Admin Override</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 17</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Anzellan</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Auditory</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Linguistic</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per 10 minutes</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You shout a string of binary or a hard-coded "Backdoor" command at a Droid or Construct creature. The target must attempt a Will saving throw against your Class DC (or your Crafting DC, whichever is higher).This ability functions even if the target is Mindless or normally immune to Mental effects.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target identifies the override attempt and blocks it. It is immune to your Admin Override for 24 hours.<br><strong>Success</strong> The target''s processor lags as it filters your code. It is Stunned 1.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You successfully rewrite the target''s Friend/Foe designation. The target is Confused for 1 minute. (It treats all creatures as enemies and attacks wildly).<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You achieve total root access. The target is Controlled by you for 1 minute. It follows your verbal orders to the best of its ability. If you issue a clearly suicidal command (like "self-destruct"), the condition ends immediately, and the target is instead Stunned 3.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actAdminOverride", "name": "Admin Override", "traits": "Anzellan, Auditory, Linguistic", "frequency": "Once per 10 minutes", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You shout a string of binary or a hard-coded \"Backdoor\" command at a Droid or Construct creature. The target must attempt a Will saving throw against your Class DC (or your Crafting DC, whichever is higher).This ability functions even if the target is Mindless or normally immune to Mental effects.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target identifies the override attempt and blocks it. It is immune to your Admin Override for 24 hours.<br><strong>Success</strong> The target''s processor lags as it filters your code. It is Stunned 1.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You successfully rewrite the target''s Friend/Foe designation. The target is Confused for 1 minute. (It treats all creatures as enemies and attacks wildly).<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You achieve total root access. The target is Controlled by you for 1 minute. It follows your verbal orders to the best of its ability. If you issue a clearly suicidal command (like \"self-destruct\"), the condition ends immediately, and the target is instead Stunned 3."}]}}',	'You speak the universal language of root-access override codes and logic paradoxes.',	'0',	17,	'Anzellan, Auditory, Linguistic',	'[{"skill": [{"id": ["sklComputers", "sklCrafting"], "rank": "Legendary"}]}]'),
