('aftAnatomicalDatabase',	'ancDroid',	'Anatomical Database',	'Your memory banks contain the physiological schematics of millions of species, allowing you to predict movement and identify blind spots. You can use the Medicine skill to Recall Knowledge about any biological creature.

In addition, you gain the Exploit Biology action:

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Exploit Biology</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
