  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You observe a biological creature within 30 feet and analyze its physiology. You attempt to Recall Knowledge against the creature, gaining the listed additional effects.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> You predict the creature''s movement. The target is Off-Guard (Flat-Footed) against your attacks until the end of your next turn.<br><strong>Critical Success</strong> You voice the creature''s vulnerability aloud. The target is Off-Guard (Flat-Footed) against attacks from you and all your allies until the start of your next turn.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You find no exploitable weakness. The target is unaffected.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actExploitBiology", "name": "Exploit Biology", "traits": "Droid", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You observe a biological creature within 30 feet and analyze its physiology. You attempt to Recall Knowledge against the creature, gaining the listed additional effects.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> You predict the creature''s movement. The target is Off-Guard (Flat-Footed) against your attacks until the end of your next turn.<br><strong>Critical Success</strong> You voice the creature''s vulnerability aloud. The target is Off-Guard (Flat-Footed) against attacks from you and all your allies until the start of your next turn.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You find no exploitable weakness. The target is unaffected."}]}}',	'Your memory banks contain the physiological schematics of millions of species, allowing you to predict movement and identify blind spots.',	'0',	5,	'Droid',	'[{"heritage": "herDroidClass1"}]'),
('aftMantellianWrangler',	'ancSavrip',	'Mantellian Wrangler',	'Your immense size and raw strength make you an absolute terror in close quarters. Whether wrestling a feral akk dog, wrangling an oversized womp rat, or manhandling a heavily armed bounty hunter, you excel at physical control. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks to Grapple or Reposition. If you roll a success on an Athletics check to Reposition a creature, you get a critical success instead.',	'{"skill": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Mantellian Wrangler", "value": "You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Grapple or Reposition.", "target": "sklAthletics"}]}}',	'Your immense size and raw strength make you an absolute terror in close quarters.',	'0',	9,	'Mantellian Savrip',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklAthletics", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftFearsomeBellow',	'ancTusken',	'Fearsome Bellow',	'Your culture communicates over long distances through terrifying, echoing roars. You become trained in Intimidation. When you attempt to Demoralize a creature, you do not take a penalty if the target doesn''t understand your language, and you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to the check if you are wielding a two-handed weapon.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklIntimidation", "rank": "Trained"}], "conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Fearsome Bellow", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Demoralize if wielding a two-handed weapon", "target": "sklIntimidation"}]}}',	'Your culture communicates over long distances through terrifying, echoing roars.',	'0',	1,	'Tusken Raider',	NULL),
('aftVenomousSpit',	'ancSavrip',	'Venomous Spit',	'You have learned to aggressively expel the venom from your glands. You make a ranged unarmed Strike against a target within 20 feet. On a hit, the target takes 1d4 poison damage and must make a Fortitude save against your Class DC or become clumsy 1 for 1 round.',	'{"weapon": [{"id": "natVenomousSpit", "bulk": null, "name": "Venomous Spit", "type": "Ranged", "group": "Brawling", "hands": "1", "range": 20, "traits": null, "category": "Unarmed", "damagedie": "d4", "damagetype": "Poison", "description": "You have learned to aggressively expel the venom from your glands. You make a ranged unarmed Strike against a target within 20 feet. On a hit, the target takes 1d4 poison damage and must make a Fortitude save against your Class DC or become clumsy 1 for 1 round."}]}',	'You have learned to aggressively expel the venom from your glands.',	'0',	9,	'Mantellian Savrip, Poison',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftParalyticVenom", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftDefensiveFlurry',	'ancCodruJi',	'Defensive Flurry',	'You create a wall of steel with your weapons. When you Parry or Raise a Shield, you gain an additional +1 circumstance bonus to AC against melee attacks until the start of your next turn, as your other limbs deflect incoming blows.

