('aftAridusScrambler',	'ancChubbit',	'Aridus Scrambler',	'You are used to navigating the jagged canyons and shifting dunes of your homeworld to avoid Imperial patrols. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Acrobatics checks to Balance and Athletics checks to Climb on rocky, sandy, or uneven terrain.',	'{"skill": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Aridus Scrambler", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Balance on rocky, sandy, or uneven terrain.", "target": "sklAcrobatics"}, {"name": "Aridus Scrambler", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Climb on rocky, sandy, or uneven terrain.", "target": "sklAthletics"}]}}',	'You are used to navigating the jagged canyons and shifting dunes of your homeworld to avoid Imperial patrols.',	'0',	1,	'Chubbit',	NULL),
('aftOverchargeTech',	'ancSquib',	'Overcharge Tech',	'You know how to bypass safety limiters to unleash a devastating—albeit destructive—blast of energy.

