('aftAridusSurvivor',	'ancChubbit',	'Aridus Survivor',	'You grew up enduring the punishing heat and scarce resources of your desert homeworld. You become trained in Survival. If you would automatically become trained in Survival, you instead become trained in a skill of your choice. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Survival checks to Subsist or Sense Direction in desert environments.',	'{"skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklSurvival", "rank": "Trained"}], "conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Aridus Survivor", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to Subsist or Sense Direction in desert environments.", "target": "sklSurvival"}]}}',	'You grew up enduring the punishing heat and scarce resources of your desert homeworld.',	'0',	1,	'Chubbit',	NULL),
('aftIthorianBellow',	'ancIthorian',	'Ithorian Bellow',	'You blast sonic energy in a 15-foot Cone. All creatures in the area take 3d6 Sonic damage (Basic Fortitude save against your Class DC). Leveling: At Level 7, the damage increases to 4d6, and increases by 1d6 every 2 levels thereafter (to a maximum of 10d6 at Level 19).

