</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actGaffiWhirlwind", "name": "Gaffi Whirlwind", "traits": "Tusken Raider, Flourish", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You spin your weapon in a blurring, deadly arc. You make a melee Strike against every enemy adjacent to you. Roll the damage once and apply it to all creatures you hit. This counts as a single attack for your multiple attack penalty, and your penalty doesn''t increase until after all the attacks are resolved.", "requirements": "You are wielding a gaffi stick or other two-handed melee weapon."}]}}',	'You spin your weapon in a blurring, deadly arc.',	'0',	9,	'Tusken Raider, Flourish',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftTuskenWeaponFamiliarity", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftBlindingSand',	'ancTusken',	'Blinding Sand',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Blinding Sand</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tusken Raider</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Manipulate</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You are standing on loose dirt, sand, or rubble.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You kick a spray of blinding grit into your attacker''s eyes. The triggering creature must succeed at a Reflex save against your Class DC. On a failure, the creature is blinded until the end of its current turn. As per the standard rules for blindness, if the creature fails this save, they must succeed at a DC 11 flat check to target you, or the triggering attack fails.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actBlindingSand", "name": "Blinding Sand", "traits": "Tusken Raider, Manipulate", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You kick a spray of blinding grit into your attacker''s eyes. The triggering creature must succeed at a Reflex save against your Class DC. On a failure, the creature is blinded until the end of its current turn. As per the standard rules for blindness, if the creature fails this save, they must succeed at a DC 11 flat check to target you, or the triggering attack fails.", "requirements": "You are standing on loose dirt, sand, or rubble."}]}}',	'You kick a spray of blinding grit into your attacker''s eyes.',	'0',	13,	'Tusken Raider, Manipulate',	NULL),
('aftKraytsFury',	'ancTusken',	'Krayt''s Fury',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Krayt''s Fury</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[free-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tusken Raider</span>
