  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Your perception of time slows down as combat begins. Before the first round of combat starts, you can immediately take a single Stride action, Step action, or Interact action to draw a weapon. This does not alter your place in the initiative order.
