</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actHyperReactiveSynapses", "name": "Hyper-Reactive Synapses", "traits": "Chubbit", "trigger": "You roll initiative.", "action_cost": "[free-action]", "description": "Your perception of time slows down as combat begins. Before the first round of combat starts, you can immediately take a single Stride action, Step action, or Interact action to draw a weapon. This does not alter your place in the initiative order."}]}}',	'',	'0',	17,	'Chubbit',	NULL),
('aftSavripsStride',	'ancSavrip',	'Savrip''s Stride',	'<div class="power-card-display">
