  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Attempt a Perception check against the Deception or Stealth DC of one creature that you can see.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> You learn one of the target&#39;s Resistances, Weaknesses, or Immunities (GM choice).<br><strong>Critical Success</strong> You learn all of the above, and you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your next Attack Roll against them.<br><br>Regardless of outcome, the target is immune to Scan Weakness for 24 hours.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actScanWeakness", "name": "Scan Weakness", "traits": "Mon Calamari, Mental", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "Attempt a Perception check against the Deception or Stealth DC of one creature that you can see.\n\n**Success** You learn one of the target''s Resistances, Weaknesses, or Immunities (GM choice).\n**Critical Success** You learn all of the above, and you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your next Attack Roll against them.\n\nRegardless of outcome, the target is immune to Scan Weakness for 24 hours."}]}}',	'You analyze threats instantly.',	'0',	13,	'Mon Calamari, Mental',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "aftIndependentEyes", "type": "ancestry"}]}]'),
('aftBoardSweeper',	'ancSavrip',	'Board Sweeper',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
