  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Because your own nervous system is so complex, you instinctively understand the pain centers of other species. You make a melee Strike. On a hit, the target must succeed at a Fortitude save against your Class DC or become enfeebled 1 for 1 minute (or enfeebled 2 on a critical failure).
  </div>
