  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You are at least 10 feet above your target.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You turn gravity into a weapon. You can jump down onto a creature as an attack. Make a melee Strike.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> You deal the weapon&#39;s damage plus 1d6 falling damage to the target. You take no falling damage yourself.<br><strong>Miss</strong> You take half the normal falling damage and land adjacent to the target.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDropBearTactics", "name": "Drop Bear Tactics", "traits": "Ewok", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You turn gravity into a weapon. You can jump down onto a creature as an attack. Make a melee Strike.\n\n**Success** You deal the weapon''s damage plus 1d6 falling damage to the target. You take no falling damage yourself.\n**Miss** You take half the normal falling damage and land adjacent to the target.", "requirements": "You are at least 10 feet above your target."}]}}',	'You turn gravity into a weapon.',	'0',	5,	'Ewok',	NULL),
('aftIktotchiPrescience',	'ancIktotchi',	'Iktotchi Prescience',	'You can focus your precognitive senses to locate a creature you have previously encountered. You gain the Glimpse the Target activity.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Glimpse the Target</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">None</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 5</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Iktotchi</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentration</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Exploration</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Mental</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You focus your mind on a specific creature you have seen, touched, or studied for at least 1 minute within the last week. After 1 minute of concentration, the target must attempt a Will saving throw against your Class DC or Spell DC (whichever is higher).<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected and realizes something attempted to view it. You cannot use this ability on this specific creature again for 24 hours.<br><strong>Success</strong> The connection is vague. You learn the target’s general direction (North, South, etc.) if they are within 10 miles of you, but not their specific location or distance.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You forge a clear mental link. For the next 10 minutes, you sense the direction and approximate distance to the target as long as they are on the same planet. Additionally, if the target is within 120 feet of you, you ignore the Concealed condition when targeting them, and they cannot be Undetected by you (though they can still be Hidden).<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the mental image is so clear that for the duration, the target is Observed by you as long as they are within 120 feet, regardless of invisibility or cover (though solid barriers still block line of effect
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actGlimpseTheTarget", "name": "Glimpse the Target", "traits": "Iktotchi, Concentration, Exploration, Mental", "frequency": "Once per day", "action_cost": null, "description": "You focus your mind on a specific creature you have seen, touched, or studied for at least 1 minute within the last week. After 1 minute of concentration, the target must attempt a Will saving throw against your Class DC or Spell DC (whichever is higher).<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected and realizes something attempted to view it. You cannot use this ability on this specific creature again for 24 hours.<br><strong>Success</strong> The connection is vague. You learn the target’s general direction (North, South, etc.) if they are within 10 miles of you, but not their specific location or distance.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You forge a clear mental link. For the next 10 minutes, you sense the direction and approximate distance to the target as long as they are on the same planet. Additionally, if the target is within 120 feet of you, you ignore the Concealed condition when targeting them, and they cannot be Undetected by you (though they can still be Hidden).<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the mental image is so clear that for the duration, the target is Observed by you as long as they are within 120 feet, regardless of invisibility or cover (though solid barriers still block line of effect"}]}}',	'You can focus your precognitive senses to locate a creature you have previously encountered.',	'0',	5,	'Iktotchi',	NULL),
('aftHypnoticLekkuWeave',	'ancTwilek',	'Hypnotic Lekku-Weave',	'<p>You perform a complex, rhythmic motion with your head-tails that overloads the visual processing of onlookers.</p>
