  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You deal 12d6 Sonic damage in a 60-foot Cone. All creatures and objects in the area must attempt a basic Fortitude save against your Class DC with the following additional effects.<br><br><strong>Failure</strong> Target is deafened for 1 minute.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Target is Stunned 1, and Deafened permanently.<br><strong>Special</strong> This attack ignores all Hardness of structures and objects in the area.
  </div>
