  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You know the perfect lie to turn allies against one another. You can spend 2 Actions to whisper a rumor or shout an accusation at an enemy within 30 feet. The target must make a Will save against your Deception DC.<br><br><strong>Failure</strong> The target refuses to be aided by its allies for 1 round (it cannot benefit from flanking, buff spells cast by allies, or the Aid action).<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target becomes Confused for 1 round, viewing its nearest ally as a traitorous threat.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSowDiscord", "name": "Sow Discord", "traits": "Bothan", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You know the perfect lie to turn allies against one another. You can spend 2 Actions to whisper a rumor or shout an accusation at an enemy within 30 feet. The target must make a Will save against your Deception DC.\n\n**Failure** The target refuses to be aided by its allies for 1 round (it cannot benefit from flanking, buff spells cast by allies, or the Aid action).\n**Critical Failure** The target becomes Confused for 1 round, viewing its nearest ally as a traitorous threat."}]}}',	'You know the perfect lie to turn allies against one another.',	'0',	5,	'Bothan',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklDeception", "rank": "Trained"}]}]'),
('aftTheGrandFinale',	'ancOrtolan',	'The Grand Finale',	'<p>You hit the &quot;High Note&quot;—a frequency that resonates with the cerebral cortex of most species.</p>
<div class="power-card-display">
