('aftPropheticDestiny',	'ancIktotchi',	'Prophetic Destiny',	'<p>Your connection to the future deepens, allowing you to foresee the consequences of your choices.  You gain the Deep Trance exploration activity.</p>
<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Deep Trance</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">None</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Iktotchi</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentration</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Exploration</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Mental</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Secret</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You enter a meditative state to glimpse the likely outcome of a specific course of action you plan to take within the next 7 days. You must state the specific goal and timeframe to the GM (e.g., &quot;What will happen if we infiltrate the Hutt&#39;s palace tonight?&quot;). After 10 minutes of medidation, the GM makes a Secret DC 6 Flat Check to determine if the vision is clear.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> You receive a truthful, albeit symbolic, mental image regarding the outcome. The GM chooses from the following results:<br>- <strong>Harmony</strong>: The action will likely yield good results (e.g., a vision of an open door or a clear sky).<br>- <strong>Calamity</strong>: The action will likely yield bad results (e.g., a vision of a broken weapon or a storm).<br>- <strong>Discord</strong>: The action will likely yield both good and bad results (e.g., a vision of a victory feast with poisoned food).<br>- <strong>Void</strong>: The outcome is not significant, or the future is too clouded to read.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You receive no vision (treat as Void).<br><strong>Special</strong> This vision reflects the current state of the galaxy. Taking this action, or subsequent actions by others, may alter the future and invalidate the vision.
  </div>
</div>
  ',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDeepTrance", "name": "Deep Trance", "traits": "Iktotchi, Concentration, Exploration, Mental, Secret", "frequency": "Once per day.", "action_cost": null, "description": "You enter a meditative state to glimpse the likely outcome of a specific course of action you plan to take within the next 7 days. You must state the specific goal and timeframe to the GM (e.g., \"What will happen if we infiltrate the Hutt''s palace tonight?\"). After 10 minutes of medidation, the GM makes a Secret DC 6 Flat Check to determine if the vision is clear.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> You receive a truthful, albeit symbolic, mental image regarding the outcome. The GM chooses from the following results:<br>- **Harmony**: The action will likely yield good results (e.g., a vision of an open door or a clear sky).<br>- **Calamity**: The action will likely yield bad results (e.g., a vision of a broken weapon or a storm).<br>- **Discord**: The action will likely yield both good and bad results (e.g., a vision of a victory feast with poisoned food).<br>- **Void**: The outcome is not significant, or the future is too clouded to read.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You receive no vision (treat as Void).<br><strong>Special</strong> This vision reflects the current state of the galaxy. Taking this action, or subsequent actions by others, may alter the future and invalidate the vision."}]}}',	'Your connection to the future deepens, allowing you to foresee the consequences of your choices.',	'0',	17,	'Iktotchi',	NULL),
('aftDroidDominator',	'ancJawa',	'Droid Dominator',	'<p>You don&#39;t just stop droids; you own them.</p>
<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
