('Deadfall Ambush',	'ancEwok',	'Deadfall Ambush',	'<p>You possess an uncanny knack for finding the &quot;loose thread&quot; in the environment—a support strut, a vine holding rocks, or a precariously stacked pile of crates—and bringing it down on your enemies.</p>
<div class="power-card-display">
