      <td>Attribute boosts, critical aim, general feat, greater weapon specialization, skill increase, specialized skill set</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>16</td>
      <td>On the move +10 feet, operative feat, skill feat</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>17</td>
      <td>Aim 4d4, ancestry feat, resolve, skill increase, tactical barrage</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>18</td>
