<h3 id="ancestry-and-background">Ancestry and Background</h3>
<p>In addition to what you get from your class at 1st level, you have the benefits of your selected ancestry and background, as described in Chapter 2.</p>
<h3 id="attribute-boosts">Attribute Boosts</h3>
<p>In addition to what you get from your class at 1st level, you have four free boosts to different attribute modifiers.</p>
<p>At 5th level and every 5 levels thereafter, you get four free boosts to different attribute modifiers. If an attribute modifier is already +4 or higher, it takes two boosts to increase it; you get a partial boost and must boost that attribute again at a later level to increase it by 1.</p>
<h3 id="initial-proficiencies">Initial Proficiencies</h3>
<p>At 1st level, you gain a number of proficiencies that represent your basic training. These proficiencies are noted at the start of this class.</p>
<h3 id="force-connection">Force Connection</h3>
<p>You have learned to open your mind to the flow of the Force, becoming a conduit for its power. You gain the Open Connection action.</p>
<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Open Connection</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 1</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentrate</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per round</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You center yourself, allowing the Force to flow through you freely. You enter the Connected state.

While Connected, you can use abilities with the Connected trait. While Connected, you can use the Telekinetic Impact action.
If you fall unconscious, the connection ends. You cannot use Open Connection if you are fatigued.
  </div>
</div>

<h3 id="telekinetic-impact">Telekinetic Impact</h3>
<p>While you are Connected, you can project raw waves of kinetic energy or hurl small debris without tiring. You gain the Telekinetic Impact ranged attack.</p>
<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Telekinetic Impact</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action] or [two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 1</span>
