    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You move out of the way as you elude your attackers. You Step.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You move out of the way as you elude your attackers.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actElusiveTarget", "name": "Elusive Target", "traits": "Operative", "trigger": "A Strike targeting you fails.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You move out of the way as you elude your attackers. You Step."}]}}',	'Operative',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftKeepThemInYourSights',	'Keep Them In Your Sights',	'You always keep a target marked and in your sights, even if they move. When you Aim, the benefits apply if your mark is within your weapon’s first or second range increment, rather than only within the first.',	NULL,	'You always keep a target marked and in your sights, even if they move.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftScopeSight',	'Scope Sight',	'Viewing your marks through a scope is as instinctive as opening your eyes. Whenever you Aim, you can Interact to Activate a sight weapon upgrade.',	NULL,	'Viewing your marks through a scope is as instinctive as opening your eyes.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDefensiveGunner',	'Defensive Gunner',	'You’ve learned to defend yourself with only a gun, shielding your body and deflecting blows with stock and barrel. Guns you wield gain the parry trait. If an appropriate weapon already has the parry trait, increase the circumstance bonus to AC it grants when used to parry from +1 to +2.',	NULL,	'You’ve learned to defend yourself with only a gun, shielding your body and deflecting blows with stock and barrel.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDevastatingAim',	'Devastating Aim',	'Your well-placed shots inflict devastating wounds on your targets. When you Aim, increase the precision damage dice from d4s to d6s.',	NULL,	'Your well-placed shots inflict devastating wounds on your targets.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBloodyWounds',	'Bloody Wounds',	'You know how to target your mark’s vital spots, leaving bloody wounds. When you critically hit your mark, you deal persistent bleed damage to your mark equal to your number of Aim damage dice.',	NULL,	'You know how to target your mark’s vital spots, leaving bloody wounds.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBioMetricScan',	'Bio-Metric Scan',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Bio-Metric Scan</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Secret</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You can see the target, and it is a living creature.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You use your rig to run a rapid, deep-tissue diagnostic on a creature''s biology. You attempt a Recall Knowledge check about the target using Medicine. You can use Medicine for this check regardless of the creature''s standard associated skill. You cannot target the same creature with Bio-Metric Scan again for 24 hours.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> In addition to the standard benefits of a successful Recall Knowledge check, you learn the creature''s current Hit Point value, any active poison or disease effects currently afflicting it, and its highest physical saving throw.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> As success, and you also learn all of the creature''s resistances and weaknesses.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subBioTech"}]}]',	'You use your rig to run a rapid, deep-tissue diagnostic on a creature''s biology.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actBioMetricScan", "name": "Bio-Metric Scan", "traits": "Tech Specialist, Secret", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You use your rig to run a rapid, deep-tissue diagnostic on a creature''s biology. You attempt a Recall Knowledge check about the target using Medicine. You can use Medicine for this check regardless of the creature''s standard associated skill. You cannot target the same creature with Bio-Metric Scan again for 24 hours.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> In addition to the standard benefits of a successful Recall Knowledge check, you learn the creature''s current Hit Point value, any active poison or disease effects currently afflicting it, and its highest physical saving throw.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> As success, and you also learn all of the creature''s resistances and weaknesses.", "requirements": "You can see the target, and it is a living creature."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist, Secret',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftUnhinderedAdvance',	'Unhindered Advance',	'When you use Tactical Advance, you ignore difficult terrain and greater difficult terrain.',	'[{"feat": {"id": "cftTacticalAdvance", "type": "class"}}]',	'When you use Tactical Advance, you ignore difficult terrain and greater difficult terrain.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftOpeningVolley',	'Opening Volley',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Opening Volley</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a gun.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You shoot your target, then you follow up with a melee attack to keep the pressure on your foe. Make a ranged Strike with your held gun. If the Strike is successful, your next melee attack this round against the same target gains a +2 circumstance bonus to the attack roll.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You shoot your target, then you follow up with a melee attack to keep the pressure on your foe.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actOpeningVolley", "name": "Opening Volley", "traits": "Operative", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You shoot your target, then you follow up with a melee attack to keep the pressure on your foe. Make a ranged Strike with your held gun. If the Strike is successful, your next melee attack this round against the same target gains a +2 circumstance bonus to the attack roll.", "requirements": "You’re wielding a gun."}]}}',	'Operative',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftChallengingShout',	'Challenging Shout',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Challenging Shout</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Auditory</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Mental</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You roar a challenge that demands attention. Attempt an Intimidation check against the Will DC of a target within 30 feet.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> The target takes a –1 circumstance penalty to Attack Rolls against anyone other than you until the start of your next turn.<br><strong>Critical Success</strong> As Success, but the penalty is –2.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklIntimidation", "rank": "Trained"}]}]',	'You roar a challenge that demands attention.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actChallengingShout", "name": "Challenging Shout", "traits": "Guardian, Auditory, Mental", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You roar a challenge that demands attention. Attempt an Intimidation check against the Will DC of a target within 30 feet.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> The target takes a –1 circumstance penalty to Attack Rolls against anyone other than you until the start of your next turn.<br><strong>Critical Success</strong> As Success, but the penalty is –2."}]}}',	'Guardian, Auditory, Mental',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSoldiersToughness',	'Soldier''s Toughness',	'Your proficiency rank in Fortitude saves increases to master.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftSoldierDedication", "type": "class"}], "saving_throw": [{"fortitude": {"rank": "Expert"}}]}]',	'Your proficiency rank in Fortitude saves increases to master.',	NULL,	'{"saving_throw": [{"fortitude": {"rank": "Expert"}}]}',	'Archetype',	12,	'0',	'arcSoldier'),
('cftClusteredShots',	'Clustered Shots',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Clustered Shots</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
