  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a gun with at least 3 expend worth of ammunition.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You shoot a spray of bullets at a target. You Aim, make a ranged Strike against your mark, and subtract three times your weapon’s expend from its magazine. Roll the attack twice, and use the better result. The attack ignores circumstance penalties to the attack roll and any flat check required due to the target being concealed or hidden.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You shoot a spray of bullets at a target.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actClusteredShots", "name": "Clustered Shots", "traits": "Operative, Fortune", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You shoot a spray of bullets at a target. You Aim, make a ranged Strike against your mark, and subtract three times your weapon’s expend from its magazine. Roll the attack twice, and use the better result. The attack ignores circumstance penalties to the attack roll and any flat check required due to the target being concealed or hidden.", "requirements": "You’re wielding a gun with at least 3 expend worth of ammunition."}]}}',	'Operative, Fortune',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBurstFire',	'Burst Fire',	'You squeeze the trigger and release a calculated burst of fire. If you make your second Strike from Double Tap with the same gun, Double Tap counts as one attack when calculating your multiple attack penalty, and you apply your precision damage bonus from Aim to both Strikes.',	'[{"feat": {"id": "cftDoubleTap", "type": "class"}}]',	'You squeeze the trigger and release a calculated burst of fire.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	16,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDroidCompanionDedication',	'Droid Companion Dedication',	'You have acquired, built, or rescued a loyal droid companion that accompanies you on your journeys. You gain the service of a Droid Companion.

Your droid companion gains the construct and tech traits instead of the animal trait. It is immune to bleed, death effects, disease, healing, necromancy, nonlethal attacks, poison, and the doomed, drained, fatigued, paralyzed, sickened, and unconscious conditions. Because it is a construct, it can only be healed by the Crafting skill (such as the Repair action) or specific technological healing effects, not by biological medicine or Force healing.

If your companion is Tiny, it can occupy your space and ride on your person.<br><br><strong>Special</strong> You cannot select another dedication feat until you have gained at least two other feats from the Droid Companion archetype.',	'[{"skill": [{"id": ["sklComputers", "sklCrafting"], "rank": "Trained"}]}]',	'You have acquired, built, or rescued a loyal droid companion that accompanies you on your journeys.',	NULL,	'{"minion": {"companion_slot": [{"count": 1, "label": "Droid Companion", "trait_filter": "Construct"}]}}',	'Archetype, Dedication',	2,	'0',	'arcDroidCompanion'),
('cftDualAim',	'Dual Aim',	'Your sharpshooter skills improve. You can have two marks at a time instead of one. When you Aim, you can select two marks, rather than one.',	NULL,	'Your sharpshooter skills improve.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftRunningShot',	'Running Shot',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Running Shot</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Flourish</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Traversal</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a gun.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You rush forward, firing a precisely aimed shot at your enemy while you’re on the move. Aim and then Stride up to your Speed. At any point during this movement, you can make a ranged Strike with the gun you’re wielding.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You rush forward, firing a precisely aimed shot at your enemy while you’re on the move.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actRunningShot", "name": "Running Shot", "traits": "Operative, Flourish, Traversal", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You rush forward, firing a precisely aimed shot at your enemy while you’re on the move. Aim and then Stride up to your Speed. At any point during this movement, you can make a ranged Strike with the gun you’re wielding.", "requirements": "You’re wielding a gun."}]}}',	'Operative, Flourish, Traversal',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSprint',	'Sprint',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Sprint</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions] or [three-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Traversal</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">

  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You sprint at top speed to chase down a foe or flee a dangerous situation. Stride up to four times. You can increase the number of actions this activity takes to 3 to Stride up to six times.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You sprint at top speed to chase down a foe or flee a dangerous situation.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSprint", "name": "Sprint", "traits": "Operative, Traversal", "action_cost": "[two-actions] or [three-actions]", "description": "You sprint at top speed to chase down a foe or flee a dangerous situation. Stride up to four times. You can increase the number of actions this activity takes to 3 to Stride up to six times."}]}}',	'Operative, Traversal',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSoldiersResiliency',	'Soldier''s Resiliency',	'You gain 3 additional Hit Points for each soldier archetype class feat you have. As you continue selecting soldier archetype class feats, you continue to gain additional Hit Points in this way.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftSoldierDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You gain 3 additional Hit Points for each soldier archetype class feat you have.',	NULL,	'{"defense": {"hp_per_archetype_feat": {"hp": 3, "archetype_id": "arcSoldier"}}}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcSoldier'),
('cftCircleOfShelter',	'Circle of Shelter',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Circle of Shelter</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Form</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Aura</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You are in Soresu Stance.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You expand your defensive perimeter. You create a 15-foot Emanation. Allies within this area gain the AC bonus from your Soresu Stance (+2 vs Ranged).<br><br><strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> Allies in the area also gain Resistance to Physical damage equal to your Constitution modifier.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftDeflectingShield", "type": "form"}]}]',	'You expand your defensive perimeter.',	NULL,	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actCircleOfShelter", "name": "Circle of Shelter", "traits": "Form, Aura", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You expand your defensive perimeter. You create a 15-foot Emanation. Allies within this area gain the AC bonus from your Soresu Stance (+2 vs Ranged).<br><br><strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> Allies in the area also gain Resistance to Physical damage equal to your Constitution modifier.", "requirements": "You are in Soresu Stance."}]}}',	'Form, Aura',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftExtremeAccuracy',	'Extreme Accuracy',	'When you Aim, the benefits apply if your mark is within range up to your weapon’s fourth range increment. Additionally, you ignore the penalty for attacking your mark at up to four range increments away.',	'[{"feat": {"id": "cftKeepThemInYourSights", "type": "class"}}]',	'When you Aim, the benefits apply if your mark is within range up to your weapon’s fourth range increment.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	16,	'0',	NULL),
('cftGoToGround',	'Go to Ground!',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Go to Ground!</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action] or [two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Envoy</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Directive</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">

  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You succinctly direct your allies to find cover by any means necessary. You and all allies within 60 feet count any form of lesser cover as standard cover until the start of your next turn.<br><br><strong>Lead by Example</strong> If you used two actions, Take Cover. Any allies within 60 feet can Take Cover as a reaction.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You succinctly direct your allies to find cover by any means necessary.',	'clsEnvoy',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actGoToGround", "name": "Go to Ground!", "traits": "Envoy, Directive", "action_cost": "[one-action] or [two-actions]", "description": "You succinctly direct your allies to find cover by any means necessary. You and all allies within 60 feet count any form of lesser cover as standard cover until the start of your next turn.<br><br><strong>Lead by Example</strong> If you used two actions, Take Cover. Any allies within 60 feet can Take Cover as a reaction."}]}}',	'Directive, Envoy',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftRelentlessAim',	'Relentless Aim',	'You take careful aim with your shots so that your bullets ricochet off solid surfaces. When determining if you have line of effect to a target you’ve aimed at, you can choose one solid surface within your weapon’s first range increment to ricochet your shot to hit your target; determine line of effect from the chosen ricochet surface, rather than your location. If the creature is undetected, the GM still rolls a flat check in secret to see if you missed, but the flat check becomes DC 5.',	NULL,	'You take careful aim with your shots so that your bullets ricochet off solid surfaces.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftCombatReflexes',	'Combat Reflexes',	'Your extensive training has transformed you into a living weapon, ready to pull the trigger at a moment’s notice. At the start of each enemy’s turn, you gain an additional reaction during that turn that you can use only for an operative reaction.',	NULL,	'Your extensive training has transformed you into a living weapon, ready to pull the trigger at a moment’s notice.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	20,	'0',	NULL),
('cftInfiniteAim',	'Infinite Aim',	'You’re a sharpshooter who doesn’t need a scope or stance to shoot your best shot. You can Aim as a free action.',	NULL,	'You’re a sharpshooter who doesn’t need a scope or stance to shoot your best shot.',	'clsOperative',	NULL,	'Operative',	20,	'0',	NULL),
('cftPardonMe',	'Pardon Me',	'You distract your foes with a clever comment as you maneuver around them. You can use Deception instead of Acrobatics to Tumble Through using the target''s Will DC instead of Reflex DC. When you successfully Tumble Through using Deception, the foe whose space you passed through is suppressed until the end of its next turn.',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklDeception", "rank": "Trained"}]}]',	'You distract your foes with a clever comment as you maneuver around them.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy, Mental',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftIntimidatingTaunt',	'Intimidating Taunt',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Intimidating Taunt</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentrate</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Mental</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">

  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You taunt your enemy mercilessly, forcing them to acknowledge you as an immediate threat. Attempt an Intimidation check and compare it to the Will DC of one enemy creature within 60 feet. This action has the auditory trait or visual trait, depending on how you taunt your enemy.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your taunts sting hard. Until the start of your next turn, any hostile actions that the creature takes must include you as a target or include you in the area; otherwise, the creature takes a –2 circumstance penalty to attack rolls and to its save DC for those hostile actions.<br><strong>Success</strong> As critical success, but only the first hostile action that the creature takes is affected.<br><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is unaffected.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"skill": {"id": "sklIntimidation", "rank": "Trained"}}]',	'You taunt your enemy mercilessly, forcing them to acknowledge you as an immediate threat.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actIntimidatingTaunt", "name": "Intimidating Taunt", "traits": "Soldier, Concentrate, Mental", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You taunt your enemy mercilessly, forcing them to acknowledge you as an immediate threat. Attempt an Intimidation check and compare it to the Will DC of one enemy creature within 60 feet. This action has the auditory trait or visual trait, depending on how you taunt your enemy.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your taunts sting hard. Until the start of your next turn, any hostile actions that the creature takes must include you as a target or include you in the area; otherwise, the creature takes a –2 circumstance penalty to attack rolls and to its save DC for those hostile actions.<br><strong>Success</strong> As critical success, but only the first hostile action that the creature takes is affected.<br><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is unaffected."}]}}',	'Concentrate, Mental, Soldier',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftWatchOut',	'Watch Out',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Watch Out</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Envoy</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentrate</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>A creature targets an ally within 60 feet with an attack, and you can see both the attacker and your ally.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You signal a warning to your ally, granting them a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You signal a warning to your ally, granting them a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack.',	'clsEnvoy',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actWatchOut", "name": "Watch Out", "traits": "Envoy, Concentrate", "trigger": "A creature targets an ally within 60 feet with an attack, and you can see both the attacker and your ally.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You signal a warning to your ally, granting them a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack."}]}}',	'Concentrate, Envoy',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftComeGetSome',	'Come Get Some!',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Come Get Some!</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You are reduced to 0 Hit Points and would fall unconscious.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You fight on to the absolute last, pushing yourself to make one final attack at a foe. Make a Strike with a –2 circumstance penalty, or make an Area Fire or Auto-Fire attack ignoring the unwieldy trait and with the save DC decreased by 2. After the attack is concluded, you immediately fall unconscious and gain the dying condition.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You fight on to the absolute last, pushing yourself to make one final attack at a foe.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actComeGetSome", "name": "Come Get Some!", "traits": "Soldier", "trigger": "You are reduced to 0 Hit Points and would fall unconscious.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You fight on to the absolute last, pushing yourself to make one final attack at a foe. Make a Strike with a –2 circumstance penalty, or make an Area Fire or Auto-Fire attack ignoring the unwieldy trait and with the save DC decreased by 2. After the attack is concluded, you immediately fall unconscious and gain the dying condition."}]}}',	'Soldier',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDisarmingShot',	'Disarming Shot',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Disarming Shot</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a gun.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You attempt to disarm your foe with a well-aimed shot. You Aim and then make a ranged Strike against your mark. If the Strike hits, attempt to Disarm the target using the same ranged attack roll against the target''s Reflex DC, instead of attempting an Athletics check. A Disarming Shot counts as two attacks for your multiple attack penalty, but the penalty doesn''t increase until after you''ve used Disarming Shot.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You attempt to disarm your foe with a well-aimed shot.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDisarmingShot", "name": "Disarming Shot", "traits": "Operative", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You attempt to disarm your foe with a well-aimed shot. You Aim and then make a ranged Strike against your mark. If the Strike hits, attempt to Disarm the target using the same ranged attack roll against the target''s Reflex DC, instead of attempting an Athletics check. A Disarming Shot counts as two attacks for your multiple attack penalty, but the penalty doesn''t increase until after you''ve used Disarming Shot.", "requirements": "You’re wielding a gun."}]}}',	'Operative',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSpreadTheLove',	'Spread the Love',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Spread the Love</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding an area or automatic weapon.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You skillfully line up your attack to harry two targets within your blast zone with equal lethality. You Area Fire or Auto-Fire, selecting two different primary targets, rather than one.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You skillfully line up your attack to harry two targets within your blast zone with equal lethality.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSpreadTheLove", "name": "Spread the Love", "traits": "Soldier", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You skillfully line up your attack to harry two targets within your blast zone with equal lethality. You Area Fire or Auto-Fire, selecting two different primary targets, rather than one.", "requirements": "You’re wielding an area or automatic weapon."}]}}',	'Soldier',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDiverseSchemes',	'Diverse Schemes',	'You’re an efficient multitasker, and you always have more than one goal in mind or scheme on the go. You can maintain twice your Charisma modifier of assets.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftSizeUp", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You’re an efficient multitasker, and you always have more than one goal in mind or scheme on the go.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftConcentratedShot',	'Concentrated Shot',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Concentrated Shot</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Flourish</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding an automatic weapon.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Focusing your fire enables you to target an enemy for immediate destruction. Make a ranged Strike with an automatic weapon, expending three times the ammo and gaining a +4 circumstance bonus to damage. This bonus increases to +6 at 11th level and +8 at 15th level.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'Focusing your fire enables you to target an enemy for immediate destruction.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actConcentratedShot", "name": "Concentrated Shot", "traits": "Soldier, Flourish", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "Focusing your fire enables you to target an enemy for immediate destruction. Make a ranged Strike with an automatic weapon, expending three times the ammo and gaining a +4 circumstance bonus to damage. This bonus increases to +6 at 11th level and +8 at 15th level.", "requirements": "You’re wielding an automatic weapon."}]}}',	'Flourish, Soldier',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDistantFeint',	'Distant Feint',	'You’re an incredible actor, and you can use your over-the top bits and dramatic gestures to throw a foe off its game. If you’re wielding a ranged weapon, you can Feint against an opponent at a range of 100 feet, rather than just within melee reach. If you succeed, the opponent is off-guard against your melee and ranged attacks, rather than only your melee attacks.',	NULL,	'You’re an incredible actor, and you can use your over-the top bits and dramatic gestures to throw a foe off its game.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSwiftReposition',	'Swift Reposition',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Swift Reposition</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You’re about to roll a Reflex saving throw, but you haven’t rolled yet.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Sensing danger, you can leap and twist your body away from the threat. You Step or Leap and gain a +2 circumstance bonus on your Reflex save. You must still roll the Reflex save even if this ability moves you out of range of the triggering effect.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'Sensing danger, you can leap and twist your body away from the threat.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSwiftReposition", "name": "Swift Reposition", "traits": "Operative", "trigger": "You’re about to roll a Reflex saving throw, but you haven’t rolled yet.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "Sensing danger, you can leap and twist your body away from the threat. You Step or Leap and gain a +2 circumstance bonus on your Reflex save. You must still roll the Reflex save even if this ability moves you out of range of the triggering effect."}]}}',	'Operative',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftPinDown',	'Pin Down',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Pin Down</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>A creature you''re observing succeeds at their saving throw against your Area Fire or Auto-Fire attack.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>once per hour</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You focus your weapons fire on a resilient target in order to suppress them with the sheer ferocity of your assault. The required target must succeed at a Will save against your class DC or become suppressed until the start of your next turn.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You focus your weapons fire on a resilient target in order to suppress them with the sheer ferocity of your assault.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actPinDown", "name": "Pin Down", "traits": "Soldier", "trigger": "A creature you''re observing succeeds at their saving throw against your Area Fire or Auto-Fire attack.", "frequency": "once per hour", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You focus your weapons fire on a resilient target in order to suppress them with the sheer ferocity of your assault. The required target must succeed at a Will save against your class DC or become suppressed until the start of your next turn."}]}}',	'Soldier',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftFlowOfBattle',	'Flow of Battle',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Flow of Battle</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Consular</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Connected</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Movement</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>An enemy ends a move action adjacent to you.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You Step (move 5 feet without provoking reactions).<br><br><strong>Mandate of the Ascendant:</strong> You can Step up to 10 feet.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You sense the threat and drift away.',	'clsConsular',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actFlowOfBattle", "name": "Flow of Battle", "traits": "Consular, Connected, Movement", "trigger": "An enemy ends a move action adjacent to you.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You sense the threat and drift away. You Step (move 5 feet without provoking reactions).\n\n**Mandate of the Ascendant:** You can Step up to 10 feet."}]}}',	'Consular, Connected, Movement',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftLookAlive',	'Look Alive',	'You warn your ally to move away from danger. You can use Watch Out before an ally in range attempts a Reflex save in addition to its original trigger. If you do, the circumstance bonus applies to their Reflex save against the triggering effect.

When you use Watch Out and the triggering attack fails or critically fails, or your ally succeeds or critically succeeds at the saving throw, your ally can also Stride up to 10 feet as a free action.',	NULL,	'You warn your ally to move away from danger.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy, Traversal',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftUnstoppableDirectives',	'Unstoppable Directives',	'Your confidence is a battery that keeps your allies going. When you use a directive that grants temporary Hit Points, increase the temporary Hit Points by your level. When you use a directive that doesn’t grant temporary Hit Points, you can grant one ally affected by that directive temporary Hit Points equal to half your level. These temporary Hit Points last for 1 minute.',	NULL,	'Your confidence is a battery that keeps your allies going.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftThatllShowEm',	'That''ll Show ‘Em',	'When you warn an ally of an attack, you follow up with a shot at your enemy. The first time each round you use your Watch Out reaction, you can make a melee or ranged Strike against the triggering creature. This Strike doesn''t count toward your multiple attack penalty, and your multiple attack penalty doesn''t apply to this Strike. If you hit, your target is suppressed until the start of its next turn.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftWatchOut", "type": "class"}]}]',	'When you warn an ally of an attack, you follow up with a shot at your enemy.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForceReplenishment',	'Force Replenishment',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Force Replenishment</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Consular</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Connected</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You deepen your connection to prepare for a massive release of energy. You deepen your connection to prepare for a massive release of energy. If the next action you use has the Overexertion trait, your Connected state does not end immediately. Instead, it ends at the end of your next turn.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You deepen your connection to prepare for a massive release of energy.',	'clsConsular',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actForceReplenishment", "name": "Force Replenishment", "traits": "Consular, Connected", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You deepen your connection to prepare for a massive release of energy. You deepen your connection to prepare for a massive release of energy. If the next action you use has the Overexertion trait, your Connected state does not end immediately. Instead, it ends at the end of your next turn."}]}}',	'Consular, Connected',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftEffortlessInfluencer',	'Effortless Influencer',	'You''ve become such a master manipulator that spotting an opening to ply your influence has become second nature. You gain the Assurance skill feat three times for Deception, Diplomacy, and Intimidation. Furthermore, when you succeed at a check with Deception, Diplomacy, or Intimidation, allies within 60 feet who witnessed your success gain a +1 status bonus to the next check they attempt with that skill within 1 minute (or a +2 bonus if your check was a critical success).',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftInfluence", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You''ve become such a master manipulator that spotting an opening to ply your influence has become second nature.',	'clsEnvoy',	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaAssurance", "type": "skill", "context_override": {"target_skill": "sklDeception"}}, {"id": "feaAssurance", "type": "skill", "context_override": {"target_skill": "sklDiplomacy"}}, {"id": "feaAssurance", "type": "skill", "context_override": {"target_skill": "sklIntimidation"}}]}}',	'Envoy',	16,	'0',	NULL),
('cftGetThem',	'Get Them!',	'When you use Get ''Em!, you can choose any number of enemies within range instead of a single target (you still only Strike one target if you spent 2 actions).',	NULL,	'When you use Get ''Em!, you can choose any number of enemies within range.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	16,	'0',	NULL),
('cftFastSynergy',	'Fast Synergy',	'People follow your lead because you help push them to their ultimate potential. Each of your allies gain a second reaction if they start their turn within 100 feet of you and can perceive you. This second reaction can only be used for directives you issue.',	NULL,	'People follow your lead because you help push them to their ultimate potential.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftEndlesslyAdaptive',	'Endlessly Adaptive',	'Your varied life experiences let you adapt to nearly any situation. When you gain skill feats using adaptive talent, you gain two additional skill feats. In addition, you can adapt to the day’s challenges by spending 10 minutes to plan. If you do, you can reselect the feats chosen with adaptive talent as if you’d made your daily preparations. You can’t trade out feats with limited-use abilities that you’ve already used that day.',	NULL,	'Your varied life experiences let you adapt to nearly any situation.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	20,	'0',	NULL),
('cftTrueLeader',	'True Leader',	'You’ve worked with a team for so long that you’ve learned to convey orders with a glance, a single word, or the tiniest flick of your hand (or suitable appendage, depending on ancestry). Once per turn, you can issue a 1-action envoy directive as a free action. This directive doesn’t count toward your total number of directives issued this turn.',	NULL,	'You’ve worked with a team for so long that you’ve learned to convey orders with a glance.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	20,	'0',	NULL),
('cftImprovisedLegend',	'Improvised Legend',	'You can use Improvised Mastery once per hour, rather than twice per day.',	NULL,	'You can use Improvised Mastery once per hour, rather than twice per day.',	'clsEnvoy',	NULL,	'Envoy',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSustainedForce',	'Sustained Force',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Sustained Force</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[free-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Consular</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentrate</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Connected</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">

  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You effortlessly maintain a lingering effect. If you have an active Force Power with a duration of "Sustained," you can Sustain it as a free action.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You effortlessly maintain a lingering effect.',	'clsConsular',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSustainedForce", "name": "Sustained Force", "traits": "Consular, Concentrate, Connected", "action_cost": "[free-action]", "description": "You effortlessly maintain a lingering effect. If you have an active Force Power with a duration of \"Sustained,\" you can Sustain it as a free action."}]}}',	'Consular, Concentrate, Connected',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForewarnedDefense',	'Forewarned Defense',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Forewarned Defense</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
