      <span>You are targeted by an attack from an attacker you can see.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You foresee the angle of the attack and shift slightly before it happens. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You foresee the angle of the attack and shift slightly before it happens.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powForewarnedDefense", "name": "Forewarned Defense", "traits": "Sentinel, Force Power", "trigger": "You are targeted by an attack from an attacker you can see.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You foresee the angle of the attack and shift slightly before it happens. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack."}]}}',	'Sentinel, Force Power',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDefensiveStance',	'Defensive Stance',	'While you are Connected and not wearing medium or heavy armor, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC against ranged attacks.',	NULL,	'While you are Connected and not wearing medium or heavy armor, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC against ranged attacks.',	'clsConsular',	'{"ac": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Defensive Stance", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus against ranged attacks when Connected and not wearing medium or heavy armor.", "target": "ac"}]}}',	'Consular',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftTacticalAdvance',	'Tactical Advance',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Tactical Advance</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You aren’t encumbered.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You dodge, roll, and weave out of danger, leaving no openings for attack as you move across the battlefield. Stride up to your Speed. This movement doesn’t trigger reactions.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You dodge, roll, and weave out of danger, leaving no openings for attack as you move across the battlefield.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actTacticalAdvance", "name": "Tactical Advance", "traits": "Operative", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You dodge, roll, and weave out of danger, leaving no openings for attack as you move across the battlefield. Stride up to your Speed. This movement doesn’t trigger reactions.", "requirements": "You aren’t encumbered."}]}}',	'Flourish, Move, Operative, Traversal',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDestructiveDash',	'Destructive Dash',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Destructive Dash</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re in an environment with suitable material to tear up, such as an urban environment.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You dash across the battlefield, tearing up your surroundings and toppling nearby objects as you go to make it harder for your foes to maneuver or to give chase. Stride up to your Speed. The squares you move through become difficult terrain.<br><br>A creature within reach of one of the affected squares can clear the area with an Interact action, removing any difficult terrain you created in the square.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You dash across the battlefield, tearing up your surroundings and toppling nearby objects as you go to make it harder for your foes to maneuver or to give chase.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDestructiveDash", "name": "Destructive Dash", "traits": "Operative", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You dash across the battlefield, tearing up your surroundings and toppling nearby objects as you go to make it harder for your foes to maneuver or to give chase. Stride up to your Speed. The squares you move through become difficult terrain.\n\nA creature within reach of one of the affected squares can clear the area with an Interact action, removing any difficult terrain you created in the square.", "requirements": "You’re in an environment with suitable material to tear up, such as an urban environment."}]}}',	'Operative',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftLorekeeperOfTheOrder',	'Lorekeeper of the Order',	'You have internalized the vast archives of your Order. You can use your The Force skill to Recall Knowledge on any topic (not just those relevant to the Force). However, when Recalling Knowledge on topics unrelated to the Force, the Jedi/Sith, or galactic history, you take a –2 circumstance penalty to the check.',	NULL,	'You have internalized the vast archives of your Order.',	'clsConsular',	NULL,	'Consular',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForceSense',	'Force Sense',	'You have a passive, low-level awareness of the Living Force. You gain a vague sense of the presence of living creatures within 30 feet, even if they are Hidden or Invisible. This counts as an imprecise sense. You do not need to be Connected to use this, but if you are Connected, the range increases to 60 feet.',	NULL,	'You have a passive, low-level awareness of the Living Force.',	'clsConsular',	'{"sense": {"Force Sense": "Imprecise"}}',	'Consular, Detection',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBasicGunner',	'Basic Gunner',	'You gain a 1st- or 2nd-level operative feat.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftOperativeDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You gain a 1st- or 2nd-level operative feat.',	NULL,	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "choice(''target_feat'')", "type": "class_feat"}]}, "inputs": [{"name": "target_feat", "type": "class_feat", "label": "Operative Feat", "filter": {"trait": ["Operative"], "max_level": 2}}]}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcOperative'),
('cftTacticalSwap',	'Tactical Swap',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Tactical Swap</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Flourish</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>Your last ranged Strike this turn missed or hit and failed to damage the target.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You swap weapons with a practiced motion. You Switch Hands or Interact to swap your current weapon for another. Make a Strike against the required target with your newly drawn weapon.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You swap weapons with a practiced motion.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actTacticalSwap", "name": "Tactical Swap", "traits": "Operative, Flourish", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You swap weapons with a practiced motion. You Switch Hands or Interact to swap your current weapon for another. Make a Strike against the required target with your newly drawn weapon.", "requirements": "Your last ranged Strike this turn missed or hit and failed to damage the target."}]}}',	'Operative, Flourish',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDominatorsGrasp',	'Dominator''s Grasp',	'While Connected, whenever you have a creature Restrained or Grabbed via a Force Power, that creature takes damage equal to your Wisdom modifier at the end of its turn.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subMandateOfDominance"}]}]',	'While Connected, whenever you have a creature Restrained or Grabbed via a Force Power, that creature takes damage equal to your Wisdom modifier at the end of its turn.',	'clsConsular',	NULL,	'Consular, Connected',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftMentalRebound',	'Mental Rebound',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Mental Rebound</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
