  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You propel yourself through the air with a burst of telekinesis. You Leap. If you are Focused, the distance of your vertical and horizontal Leap increases by 15 feet. If you end this movement adjacent to an enemy, you can make a Strike as part of the action (but with a –2 penalty).
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You propel yourself through the air with a burst of telekinesis.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actForceJump", "name": "Force Jump", "traits": "Guardian, Move", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You propel yourself through the air with a burst of telekinesis. You Leap. If you are Focused, the distance of your vertical and horizontal Leap increases by 15 feet. If you end this movement adjacent to an enemy, you can make a Strike as part of the action (but with a –2 penalty)."}]}}',	'Guardian, Move',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSoldierDedication',	'Soldier Dedication',	'You''re a stalwart shield who never stops blasting while protecting your allies from danger, including from your own terrifying destruction. You become trained in Intimidation. If you were already trained in Intimidation, you instead become trained in a skill of your choice. Increase your maximum and encumbered Bulk limits by 2. You become trained in soldier class DC.

You become trained in light armor and medium armor. If you already were trained in light armor and medium armor, you gain training in heavy armor as well. If you''re 13th level or higher, you also become an expert in the armor types granted to you by this feat.',	'[{"attribute": [{"con": 2}]}]',	'You''re a stalwart shield who never stops blasting while protecting your allies from danger, including from your own terrifying destruction.',	NULL,	'{"dc": [{"name": "Soldier Class DC", "rank": "Trained", "attribute": "CON"}], "skill": {"fixed": [{"id": "sklIntimidation", "rank": "Trained"}]}, "armor_progression": {"sequence": ["light", "medium", "heavy"], "base_rank": "Trained", "level_upgrades": [{"rank": "Expert", "min_level": 13}]}}',	'Archetype, Dedication, Multiclass',	2,	'0',	'arcSoldier'),
('cftArrestingManeuver',	'Arresting Maneuver',	'<div class="power-card-display">
