  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You lay down a punishing, inescapable barrage of heavy fire. Make an Auto-Fire or Area Fire attack. Any creature that takes damage from this attack is also suppressed until the start of your next turn.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subArmstech"}]}]',	'You lay down a punishing, inescapable barrage of heavy fire.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSuppressingFirepower", "name": "Suppressing Firepower", "traits": "Tech Specialist", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You lay down a punishing, inescapable barrage of heavy fire. Make an Auto-Fire or Area Fire attack. Any creature that takes damage from this attack is also suppressed until the start of your next turn.", "requirements": "You are wielding a ranged weapon with the area or automatic trait."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftMatureBeastmasterCompanion',	'Mature Beastmaster Companion',	'All of your animal companions grow up, becoming mature animal companions and gaining additional capabilities.

Your animal companion has greater independence. During an encounter, even if you don’t use the Command an Animal action, your active animal companion can still use 1 action that round on your turn to Stride or Strike. It can do this at any point during your turn, as long as you aren’t currently taking an action. If it does, that’s all the actions it gets that round— you can’t Command it later.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBeastmasterDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'All of your animal companions grow up, becoming mature animal companions and gaining additional capabilities.',	NULL,	'{"minion": {"apply_template": "mature"}}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcBeastmaster'),
('cftCullTheWeak',	'Cull The Weak',	'You end suffering quickly. Your melee Strikes against creatures that are Frightened or Dying deal an additional 1d8 damage.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheDestroyer"}]}]',	'You end suffering quickly.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForceAthleticism',	'Force Athleticism',	'You use the Force to enhance your physical prowess. You gain the Hefty Hauler skill feat. Additionally, when you High Jump or Long Jump, you use your Strength modifier instead of your Dexterity modifier for the check, and you do not need a running start.',	NULL,	'You use the Force to enhance your physical prowess.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftCombatReflexesG',	'Combat Reflexes',	'Your reaction time is supernatural. You gain an additional Reaction at the start of each of your turns. This extra reaction can only be used for Reactive Strike or Intercede.',	NULL,	'Your reaction time is supernatural.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftImprovedIntercede',	'Improved Intercede',	'Your protective instincts are honed. When you use the Intercede reaction, you reduce the damage by 4 + (2 × Level) instead of 2 + Level.',	NULL,	'Your protective instincts are honed.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftReflectBlasters',	'Reflect Blasters',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Reflect Blasters</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
