  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You catch the bolt on your blade and send it back.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actReflectBlasters", "name": "Reflect Blasters", "traits": "Guardian", "trigger": "A ranged attack that deals energy damage misses you.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You catch the bolt on your blade and send it back. Make a ranged Strike against the attacker (or another target within 60 feet) using your Lightsaber proficiency. If you hit, deal the damage of the original attack.", "requirements": "You are wielding a lightsaber."}]}}',	'Guardian',	16,	'0',	NULL),
('cftOneWithTheForce',	'One with the Force',	'The Force flows through your every muscle. You gain a permanent +1 status bonus to AC and Saving Throws. Your movement speed increases by 10 feet.',	NULL,	'The Force flows through your every muscle.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"speed": [{"amount": 10, "target": "base"}], "defense": {"ac_bonus": [{"type": "status", "amount": 1, "source": "One with the Force (Class Feat)"}]}, "saving_throw": [{"fortitude": {"bonus": [{"type": "status", "amount": 1, "source": "One with the Force (Class Feat)"}]}}, {"reflex": {"bonus": [{"type": "status", "amount": 1, "source": "One with the Force (Class Feat)"}]}}, {"will": {"bonus": [{"type": "status", "amount": 1, "source": "One with the Force (Class Feat)"}]}}]}',	'Guardian',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftFieldForgedGadget',	'Field-Forged Gadget',	'You maintain a small stockpile of volatile chemical mixtures, spare wiring, and universal micro-chips. During your daily preparations (or as a 10-minute activity), you can rapidly assemble a temporary, single-use technological item. You can create one consumable technological item of 1st level or lower (such as a commercial-grade grenade or a specialized piece of ammunition). This item is highly unstable and clearly jury-rigged, giving it no resale value. It loses its charge and ceases to function the next time you make your daily preparations.',	NULL,	'You maintain a small stockpile of volatile chemical mixtures, spare wiring, and universal micro-chips.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	NULL,	'Tech Specialist',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDevastatingCritical',	'Devastating Critical',	'Your blows shatter armor and bone. When you critically hit with a melee weapon, the target is Slowed 1 until the end of their next turn.',	NULL,	'Your blows shatter armor and bone.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftChampionOfTheForce',	'Champion of the Force',	'You are the ultimate warrior. Your Strength modifier increases by 1. You are permanently Quickened; you can use the extra action to Strike, Stride, or Step.',	NULL,	'You are the ultimate warrior.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian',	20,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDangerSense',	'Danger Sense',	'You constantly scan the future for threats. You gain a +2 status bonus to Perception checks for Initiative. Additionally, you are not Off-Guard to creatures of your level or lower that are Hidden or Undetected by you (though you still cannot see them).',	NULL,	'You constantly scan the future for threats',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftFinalStand',	'Final Stand',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Final Stand</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You would be reduced to 0 HP.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>once per day</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You refuse to fall. You are reduced to 1 HP instead. You immediately gain Temporary HP equal to your full Hit Point maximum. These Temporary HP last for 1 minute.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You refuse to fall.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actFinalStand", "name": "Final Stand", "traits": "Guardian", "trigger": "You would be reduced to 0 HP.", "frequency": "once per day", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You refuse to fall. You are reduced to 1 HP instead. You immediately gain Temporary HP equal to your full Hit Point maximum. These Temporary HP last for 1 minute."}]}}',	'Guardian',	20,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBillowingWings',	'Billowing Wings',	'<strong>Prerequisites</strong> animal companion with wings

You''ve trained your winged companions to gather air in their wings, whipping up a concentrated gust of wind at opponents, potentially staggering them. Your companions with wings gain a gust ranged unarmed attack, which deals 1d4 bludgeoning damage with a range of 30 feet and has the air and propulsive traits. On a critical hit, the target is pushed back 5 feet. This is forced movement.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBeastmasterDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You''ve trained your winged companions to gather air in their wings, whipping up a concentrated gust of wind at opponents, potentially staggering them.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Archetype',	12,	'0',	'arcBeastmaster'),
('cftOperativeExploit',	'Operative Exploit',	'You gain the exploit of your chosen specialization.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftSpecializedOperative", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You gain the exploit of your chosen specialization.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Archetype',	8,	'0',	'arcOperative'),
('cftAuraOfDespair',	'Aura of Despair',	'Hope dies in your presence. Enemies within a 30-foot emanation cannot reduce their Frightened value below 1.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheDestroyer"}]}]',	'Hope dies in your presence.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian, Aura, Emotion, Fear',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBlurOfMotion',	'Blur of Motion',	'You move faster than the eye can track. While you are moving (during a Stride, Step, or Jump), you are Concealed.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheSwift"}]}]',	'You move faster than the eye can track.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftRecalibrateOptics',	'Recalibrate Optics',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Recalibrate Optics</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentrate</span>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You briefly sync your rig''s predictive ballistics to burn through visual interference. The next ranged Strike you make this turn ignores the concealed condition. If you are targeting a creature that is hidden from you, the DC of the flat check to target that creature is reduced from 11 to 5.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subArmstech"}]}]',	'You briefly sync your rig''s predictive ballistics to burn through visual interference.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actRecalibrateOptics", "name": "Recalibrate Optics", "traits": "Tech Specialist, Concentrate", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You briefly sync your rig''s predictive ballistics to burn through visual interference. The next ranged Strike you make this turn ignores the concealed condition. If you are targeting a creature that is hidden from you, the DC of the flat check to target that creature is reduced from 11 to 5."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist, Concentrate',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftTrapfinder',	'Trapfinder',	'You have an intuitive sense for mechanical danger. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Perception checks to find traps, to AC against attacks by traps, and to saves against traps. You can disable traps that require Master proficiency even if you are only Expert.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subPathOfTheArtisan"}]}]',	'You have an intuitive sense for mechanical danger.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"ac": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Trapfinder", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus against traps.", "target": "all"}]}, "perception": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Trapfinder", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus to find traps.", "target": "all"}]}, "saving_throw": {"conditional_bonus": [{"name": "Trapfinder", "value": "+1 circumstance bonus against traps.", "target": "all"}]}}',	'Sentinel',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftProjectedIntercession',	'Projected Intercession',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Projected Intercession</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>An ally within 15 feet is targeted by an attack or is forced to attempt a Reflex save.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You project a momentary deflector shield or hard-light barrier over an ally''s position. The ally gains a +2 circumstance bonus to their Armor Class against the triggering attack, or a +2 circumstance bonus to the triggering Reflex save.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You project a momentary deflector shield or hard-light barrier over an ally''s position.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actProjectedIntercession", "name": "Projected Intercession", "traits": "Tech Specialist", "trigger": "An ally within 15 feet is targeted by an attack or is forced to attempt a Reflex save.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You project a momentary deflector shield or hard-light barrier over an ally''s position. The ally gains a +2 circumstance bonus to their Armor Class against the triggering attack, or a +2 circumstance bonus to the triggering Reflex save."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSilentStep',	'Silent Step',	'You move like a ghost. You can move at your full Speed when you Sneak, and you gain the Quiet Allies skill feat.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subPathOfTheShadow"}]}]',	'You move like a ghost.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDirtyFighting',	'Dirty Fighting',	'You exploit every advantage. If you critically hit a creature that is Off-Guard, the creature is also Blinded or Deafened (your choice) until the start of your next turn.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subPathOfTheCorsair"}]}]',	'You exploit every advantage.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftGunExpert',	'Gun Expert',	'Your proficiency ranks for simple and martial guns increase to expert.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftOperativeDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'Your proficiency ranks for simple and martial guns increase to expert.',	NULL,	'{"attack": [{"simple": [{"ranged": {"rank": "Expert"}}]}, {"martial": [{"ranged": {"rank": "Expert"}}]}]}',	'Archetype',	12,	'0',	'arcOperative'),
('cftShockAndAwe',	'Shock and Awe',	'The sheer kinetic impact or thermal payload of your customized weaponry permanently overwhelms enemy nervous systems and structural integrity. Whenever you score a critical hit with a ranged technological weapon, the target is stunned 1. If you are using the Auto-Fire or Area Fire action, any creature that critically fails its Reflex save against your attack is also stunned 1.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subArmstech"}]}]',	'The sheer kinetic impact or thermal payload of your customized weaponry permanently overwhelms enemy nervous systems and structural integrity.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	NULL,	'Tech Specialist',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftPhalanxBreaker',	'Phalanx Breaker',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Phalanx Breaker</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 12</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid"></div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You slam into a formation. You Stride. At the end of your movement, all adjacent enemies take 4d6 Bludgeoning damage (Basic Reflex save). On a failure, they are also pushed 10 feet.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheVanguard"}]}]',	'You slam into a formation.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powPhalanxBreaker", "name": "Phalanx Breaker", "level": 12, "traits": "Guardian, Force Power", "action_cost": ["two-actions"], "description": "You slam into a formation. You Stride. At the end of your movement, all adjacent enemies take 4d6 Bludgeoning damage (Basic Reflex save). On a failure, they are also pushed 10 feet."}]}}',	'Guardian, Force Power',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftInvincibleBastion',	'Invincible Bastion',	'Your defense is absolute. While in Soresu Stance, critical hits against you are normal hits instead.

<strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> You can use your Intercede reaction an additional time per round (gaining an extra Reaction specifically for Intercede).',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftCircleOfShelter", "type": "form"}]}]',	'Your defense is absolute.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Form',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftMasterOfAggression',	'Master of Aggression',	'You are a whirlwind of destruction. While in Ataru Stance, you are permanently Quickened 1. You can use the extra action only to Stride or Leap.

<strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> You can also use the extra action to Strike.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftSaberSwarm", "type": "form"}]}]',	'You are a whirlwind of destruction.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Form',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDoubleTap',	'Double Tap',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Double Tap</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a gun.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You fire two shots at the same target in quick succession. You Aim and then make two Strikes against your mark. Apply the multiple attack penalty normally. If both attacks hit, combine their damage. You add any precision damage only once, to the attack of your choice. Apply the target’s resistances and weaknesses only once.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You fire two shots at the same target in quick succession.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDoubleTap", "name": "Double Tap", "traits": "Operative", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You fire two shots at the same target in quick succession. You Aim and then make two Strikes against your mark. Apply the multiple attack penalty normally. If both attacks hit, combine their damage. You add any precision damage only once, to the attack of your choice. Apply the target’s resistances and weaknesses only once.", "requirements": "You’re wielding a gun."}]}}',	'Operative',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftRicochetStratagem',	'Ricochet Stratagem',	'You bounce shots off walls to hit foes behind cover. Your Ranged Strikes ignore the Concealed condition and ignore cover (but not Greater Cover).',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subPathOfTheCorsair"}]}]',	'You bounce shots off walls to hit foes behind cover.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSunderingStrike',	'Sundering Strike',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Sundering Strike</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">

  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You smash through armor. Make a melee Strike. This attack ignores all Resistance and Hardness. If the target has a Shield raised, the Shield automatically takes the full damage as well (bypassing its Hardness).
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheCrusader"}]}]',	'You smash through armor.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSunderingStrike", "name": "Sundering Strike", "traits": "Guardian", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You smash through armor. Make a melee Strike. This attack ignores all Resistance and Hardness. If the target has a Shield raised, the Shield automatically takes the full damage as well (bypassing its Hardness)."}]}}',	'Guardian',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftFluidRiposte',	'Fluid Riposte',	'Your counter-attacks are devastating. While in Shien / Djem So Stance, whenever you use a Reaction to Strike an enemy (such as via Barrier of Blades), you treat the result of your attack roll as one degree of success better (a Failure becomes a Hit; a Hit becomes a Crit).

<strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> You gain an extra Reaction at the start of each of your turns that can only be used for Barrier of Blades.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBarrierOfBlades", "type": "form"}]}]',	'Your counter-attacks are devastating.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Form',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftToolsOfTheTrade',	'Tools of the Trade',	'You’re well-versed in weapons that allow you to bring bounties back in one piece, or at least alive. You have familiarity with weapons with the Nonlethal trait; for the purposes of proficiency, you treat martial weapons as simple weapons and advanced weapons as martial weapons. You deal an additional 1d4 precision damage with these weapons when using them to make Strikes against your prey. In addition, you take no penalty when making a nonlethal attack with a weapon without the Nonlethal trait.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBountyHunterDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You’re well-versed in weapons that allow you to bring bounties back in one piece, or at least alive.',	NULL,	'{"attack": {"weapon_familiarity": ["nonlethal"]}}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcBountyHunter'),
('cftFlowingConnection',	'Flowing Connection',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Flowing Connection</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Consular</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>once per minute</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You enter the Connected state. As part of this action, you can also Stride or Step.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You enter the Connected state.',	'clsConsular',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actFlowingConnection", "name": "Flowing Connection", "traits": "Consular", "frequency": "once per minute", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You enter the Connected state. As part of this action, you can also Stride or Step."}]}}',	'Consular',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBlindFight',	'Blind-Fight',	'Your reliance on eyes is a weakness you have overcome. You do not need to succeed at a flat check to target Hidden creatures. You''re not off-guard to creatures that are Hidden or Undetected.',	NULL,	'Your reliance on eyes is a weakness you have overcome.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftStrategicBypass',	'Strategic Bypass',	'You foresee the weak point in the armor. When you hit a creature using your Force Premonition roll, you ignore resistance equal to your level. If the target has Hardness (like a droid or door), you ignore half its Hardness.',	NULL,	'You foresee the weak point in the armor.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftPrecognitiveAmbush',	'Precognitive Ambush',	'You act before the enemy thinks to move. During the first round of combat, if you roll a higher Initiative than a target, that target is Off-Guard to your attacks.',	NULL,	'You act before the enemy thinks to move.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftOperativeDedication',	'Operative Dedication',	'You become trained in simple and martial guns. You become trained in operative class DC.

You gain the Aim action, it doesn''t deal additional damage, but still reduces the bonus to AC your mark gains from cover (which does not increase as you gain levels).',	'[{"attribute": [{"dex": 2}]}]',	'You become trained in simple and martial guns.',	NULL,	'{"dc": [{"name": "Operative Class DC", "rank": "Trained", "attribute": "DEX"}], "attack": [{"simple": [{"ranged": {"rank": "Trained"}}]}, {"martial": [{"ranged": {"rank": "Trained"}}]}]}',	'Archetype, Dedication, Multiclass',	2,	'0',	'arcOperative'),
('cftChampionOfVaapad',	'Champion of Vaapad',	'You walk the razor''s edge between light and dark. While in Juyo Stance, your lightsaber attacks are treated as one degree of success higher on a natural 19 or 20 (instead of only on the normal natural 20), but you cannot make nonlethal attacks.

<strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> If you roll a natural 20, you deal maximum weapon damage (do not roll damage dice).',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftAssaultOfTheVornskr", "type": "form"}]}]',	' You walk the razor''s edge between light and dark.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Form',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDisarmingTwist',	'Disarming Twist',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Disarming Twist</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You critically succeed on a Strike against your Dueling Target.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You twist your blade to wrench theirs free. You immediately attempt to Disarm the target.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheDuelist"}]}]',	'You twist your blade to wrench theirs free.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDisarmingTwist", "name": "Disarming Twist", "traits": "Guardian", "trigger": "You critically succeed on a Strike against your Dueling Target.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You twist your blade to wrench theirs free. You immediately attempt to Disarm the target."}]}}',	'Guardian',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftMindBlank',	'Mind Blank',	'Your mind is a fortress. You are immune to divination effects that would detect your presence, thoughts, or alignment. You are immune to the Controlled condition.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": ["subPathOfTheJusticar", "subPathOfTheShadow"]}]}]',	'Your mind is a fortress.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"defense": {"immunity": [{"type": "Controlled", "source": "Mind Blank (Sentinel Feat)"}]}}',	'Sentinel',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftMasterSaboteur',	'Master Saboteur',	'When you use the Sabotage action, if the target is a Construct or Droid, it takes damage equal to your Level × 2 on a Success (or double that on a Critical Success). If you Sabotage a vehicle, you can disable a specific system (Engines, Weapons, Shields).',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftSabotage", "type": "class"}]}]',	'When you use the Sabotage action, if the target is a Construct or Droid, it takes damage equal to your Level × 2 on a Success (or double that on a Critical Success). If you Sabotage a vehicle, you can disable a specific system (Engines, Weapons, Shields).',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftCoordinatedFire',	'Coordinated Fire',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Coordinated Fire</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[three-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Auditory</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding an area or automatic weapon.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    With a mighty bellow, you unload your weapon to give your allies the cover they need to rally. You Area Fire or Auto-Fire without selecting a primary target. Give a verbal order as part of your firing, selecting either Reload, Strike, or Take Cover. Every ally within 30 feet who hears and understands your order can perform the action you selected as a reaction.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'With a mighty bellow, you unload your weapon to give your allies the cover they need to rally.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actCoordinatedFire", "name": "Coordinated Fire", "traits": "Soldier, Auditory", "action_cost": "[three-actions]", "description": "With a mighty bellow, you unload your weapon to give your allies the cover they need to rally. You Area Fire or Auto-Fire without selecting a primary target. Give a verbal order as part of your firing, selecting either Reload, Strike, or Take Cover. Every ally within 30 feet who hears and understands your order can perform the action you selected as a reaction.", "requirements": "You’re wielding an area or automatic weapon."}]}}',	'Auditory, Soldier',	18,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForseenCritical',	'Forseen Critical',	'You know exactly when to strike for maximum lethality. When you use Force Premonition and attack the target, your attack gains the Fatal d10 trait (or Fatal d12 if wielding a lightsaber). If your weapon already has Fatal, the die size increases by one step.',	NULL,	'You know exactly when to strike for maximum lethality.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftTruthSeeker',	'Truth Seeker',	'Your connection to the Force allows you to see reality as it truly is. You are constantly under the effects of True Seeing. You automatically succeed at disbelieving Illusions, and you can see Invisible creatures, perceive the true form of Polymorphed creatures, and see through magical Darkness within 60 feet.',	NULL,	'Your connection to the Force allows you to see reality as it truly is.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftFogOfWar',	'Fog of War',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Fog of War</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding an area or automatic weapon</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    The flash and smoke from your frenzied gunfire conceals you from any enemies who might be left standing in the aftermath. You Area Fire or Auto-Fire. You leave behind a cloud of smoke and dust within the area that lasts until the end of your next turn or until dissipated by a strong wind (whichever happens first). Creatures in the area have the concealed condition, and all other creatures are concealed to them.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'The flash and smoke from your frenzied gunfire conceals you from any enemies who might be left standing in the aftermath.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actFogOfWar", "name": "Fog of War", "traits": "Soldier", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "The flash and smoke from your frenzied gunfire conceals you from any enemies who might be left standing in the aftermath. You Area Fire or Auto-Fire. You leave behind a cloud of smoke and dust within the area that lasts until the end of your next turn or until dissipated by a strong wind (whichever happens first). Creatures in the area have the concealed condition, and all other creatures are concealed to them.", "requirements": "You’re wielding an area or automatic weapon"}]}}',	'Soldier',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftOmniscientSentinel',	'Omniscient Sentinel',	'You exist a split second in the future. You are permanently Quickened; you can use the extra action to Stride, Step, Recall Knowledge, or use Force Premonition. Additionally, your Sentinel''s Strike damage dice become d8s instead of d6s.',	NULL,	'You exist a split second in the future.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel',	20,	'0',	NULL),
('cftPerfectParry',	'Perfect Parry',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Perfect Parry</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
