    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You take your time to line up a shot that''s sure to hit. Make a ranged Strike with your gun against your mark. It gains the following failure effect.<br><br><strong>Failure</strong> Your attack deals minimum damage to the target. (Calculate this damage as if every die you would roll has a result of 1.)
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You take your time to line up a shot that''s sure to hit.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actGrazingShot", "name": "Grazing Shot", "traits": "Operative, Flourish", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You take your time to line up a shot that''s sure to hit. Make a ranged Strike with your gun against your mark. It gains the following failure effect.<br><br><strong>Failure</strong> Your attack deals minimum damage to the target. (Calculate this damage as if every die you would roll has a result of 1.)", "requirements": "You have a mark."}]}}',	'Flourish, Operative',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftMartialAdept',	'Martial Adept',	'<p>You have mastered a new way to weave the Force into your physical combat. You gain one additional Force Power.</p>
<p><strong>Special</strong> You can select this feat more than once. You can take it again at 10th, 14th, and 18th levels. Each time you select it, you gain a different Force Power.</p>
',	NULL,	'You have mastered a new way to weave the Force into your physical combat.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"power": {"power_slot": [{"count": "1"}]}}',	'Guardian',	6,	'1',	NULL),
('cftForceVersatility',	'Force Versatility',	'<p>You have learned a new trick to aid in your investigations or survival. You gain one additional Force Power.</p>
<p><strong>Special</strong> You can select this feat more than once. You can take it again at 8th, 12th, 16th, and 20th levels. Each time you select it, you gain a different Force Power.</p>
',	NULL,	'You have learned a new trick to aid in your investigations or survival.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"power": {"power_slot": [{"count": "1"}]}}',	'Sentinel',	4,	'1',	NULL),
('cftAdvancedGunner',	'Advanced Gunner',	'You gain one operative feat. For the purpose of meeting its prerequisites, your operative level is half your character level.<br><br><strong>Special</strong> You can select this feat more than once. Each time you do, you gain another operative feat.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBasicGunner", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You gain one operative feat.',	NULL,	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "choice(''target_feat'')", "type": "class_feat"}]}, "inputs": [{"name": "target_feat", "type": "class_feat", "label": "Operative Feat", "filter": {"trait": ["Operative"], "max_level": "{slot_level // 2}"}}]}',	'Archetype',	6,	'1',	'arcOperative'),
('cftForceLevitation',	'Force Levitation',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Force Levitation</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
