    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Consular</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Connected</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You lift yourself from the ground. You gain a Fly Speed equal to half your land speed. You must use this action again each round to maintain the flight, or you float gently to the ground at the end of your turn.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You lift yourself from the ground.',	'clsConsular',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powForceLevitation", "name": "Force Levitation", "level": 8, "traits": "Consular, Force Power, Connected", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You lift yourself from the ground. You gain a Fly Speed equal to half your land speed. You must use this action again each round to maintain the flight, or you float gently to the ground at the end of your turn."}]}}',	'Consular, Force Power, Connected',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftTerrifyingPresence',	'Terrifying Presence',	'Your battle prowess is terrifying to behold. Enemies within 15-feet of you take a –1 circumstance penalty to Will saves against Fear effects.

<strong>Focused Benefit</strong> If you critically hit an enemy within the aura, they become Frightened 1.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftChallengingShout", "type": "class"}]}]',	'Your battle prowess is terrifying to behold.',	'clsGuardian',	NULL,	'Guardian, Emotion, Fear, Aura',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftCompelledDuel',	'Compelled Duel',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Compelled Duel</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
