  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You whip up debris and air currents around you.',	'clsConsular',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powTelekineticWhirlwind", "name": "Telekinetic Whirlwind", "level": 12, "traits": "Consular, Force Power, Connected, Aura", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You whip up debris and air currents around you. For 1 minute, you are surrounded by a 15-foot aura of swirling force. The area is Difficult Terrain for enemies. Enemies who start their turn in the aura take Bludgeoning damage equal to your Wisdom modifier."}]}}',	'Consular, Force Power, Connected, Aura',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftAscendantAgility',	'Ascendant Agility',	'While Connected, you can run across liquid surfaces and vertical surfaces, provided you end your movement on solid ground. If you do not end on solid ground, you fall.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subMandateOfTheAscendant"}]}]',	'While Connected, you can run across liquid surfaces and vertical surfaces, provided you end your movement on solid ground. If you do not end on solid ground, you fall.',	'clsConsular',	NULL,	'Consular, Movement',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftMasterSpy',	'Master Spy',	'Your proficiency rank for Perception increases to master.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftOperativeDedication", "type": "class"}], "perception": {"rank": "Expert"}}]',	'Your proficiency rank for Perception increases to master.',	NULL,	'{"perception": {"rank": "Master"}}',	'Archetype',	12,	'0',	'arcOperative'),
('cftSwitchTarget',	'Switch Target',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
