  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
     </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You can manipulate heavy objects with ease. You cast Telekinetic Grasp, but the Bulk limit increases to 10. You can use this to create temporary cover for allies.
    <br><br>
    <strong>Connected Benefit:</strong> The Bulk limit increases to 20.
