</div>',	'[{"power": [{"id": "powTelekineticGrasp"}]}]',	'You can manipulate heavy objects with ease.',	'clsConsular',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powTelekineticHaul", "name": "Telekinetic Haul", "level": 6, "traits": "Consular, Force Power, Alter", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You can manipulate heavy objects with ease. You cast Telekinetic Grasp, but the Bulk limit increases to 10. You can use this to create temporary cover for allies.\n\n**Connected Benefit:** The Bulk limit increases to 20."}]}}',	'Consular, Force Power, Alter',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftWallRun',	'Wall Run',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Wall Run</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Move</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You use your momentum to run along vertical surfaces. You Stride up to your Speed. During this movement, you can move across vertical surfaces (like walls) as if they were ground. You must end your movement on a horizontal surface or you fall.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheSwift"}]}]',	'You use your momentum to run along vertical surfaces.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actWallRun", "name": "Wall Run", "traits": "Guardian, Move", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You use your momentum to run along vertical surfaces. You Stride up to your Speed. During this movement, you can move across vertical surfaces (like walls) as if they were ground. You must end your movement on a horizontal surface or you fall."}]}}',	'Guardian, Move',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftCrushingWill',	'Crushing Will',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Crushing Will</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
