  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subMandateOfConflict"}, {"id": "subMandateOfDominance"}]}]',	'You attempt to crush the target''s mind or body with overwhelming pressure.',	'clsConsular',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powCrushingWill", "name": "Crushing Will", "level": 4, "range": "30 feet", "target": "1 creature", "traits": "Consular, Force Power, Connected, Overexertion, Mental", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You attempt to crush the target''s mind or body with overwhelming pressure. The target makes a Will save.\n\n**Critical Success:** Target is unaffected.\n**Success:** Target is Stunned 1.\n**Failure:** Target is Stunned 2 and takes 2d6 Mental damage.\n**Critical Failure:** Target is Stunned 3 and takes 4d6 Mental damage."}]}}',	'Consular, Force Power, Connected, Overexertion, Mental',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftWideSwing',	'Wide Swing',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Wide Swing</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
