  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">

  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You cleave through the line. Make a melee Strike. Compare the attack roll to the AC of every enemy in a 10-foot Cone in front of you. Roll damage once and apply it to all creatures hit.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheVanguard"}]}]',	'You cleave through the line.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actWideSwing", "name": "Wide Swing", "traits": "Guardian, Area", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You cleave through the line. Make a melee Strike. Compare the attack roll to the AC of every enemy in a 10-foot Cone in front of you. Roll damage once and apply it to all creatures hit."}]}}',	'Guardian, Area',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForceRecovery',	'Force Recovery',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Force Recovery</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 2</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Consular</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Connected</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentrate</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Healing</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
     </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You draw upon the Living Force to revitalize your own body. You regain Hit Points equal to 1d8 + your Constitution modifier. You cannot use this ability again for 10 minutes.
    <br><br>
    <strong>Mandate of Life:</strong> You heal 2d8 + CON instead.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You draw upon the Living Force to revitalize your own body.',	'clsConsular',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powForceRecovery", "name": "Force Recovery", "level": 2, "traits": "Consular, Force Power, Connected, Concentrate, Healing", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You draw upon the Living Force to revitalize your own body. You regain Hit Points equal to 1d8 + your Constitution modifier. You cannot use this ability again for 10 minutes.\n\n**Mandate of Life:** You heal 2d8 + CON instead."}]}}',	'Consular, Force Power, Connected, Concentrate, Healing',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSpecializedOperative',	'Specialized Operative',	'Choose a specialization. You become trained in one skill determined by your specialization; if you were already trained in that skill, you instead become trained in another skill of your choice. You gain a skill feat associated with that skill. You don’t gain any other benefits from your specialization.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftOperativeDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'Choose a specialization.',	NULL,	'{"inputs": [{"name": "operative_subclass", "type": "subclass", "label": "Operative Specialization", "filter": {"class_id": "clsOperative"}, "apply_keys": ["feature", "flags", "inputs", "skill"]}]}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcOperative'),
('cftTopplingShot',	'Toppling Shot',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Toppling Shot</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a gun.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You aim your shots to unbalance your foe, pushing them back or knocking them over. You Aim and then make a ranged Strike against your mark. If the Strike hits, the target is knocked back 5 feet. If this forced movement would cause them to collide with a creature or object, both the target and the creature (if any) take bludgeoning damage equal to your Aim damage. On a critical hit, the target is also knocked prone.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You aim your shots to unbalance your foe, pushing them back or knocking them over.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actTopplingShot", "name": "Toppling Shot", "traits": "Operative", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You aim your shots to unbalance your foe, pushing them back or knocking them over. You Aim and then make a ranged Strike against your mark. If the Strike hits, the target is knocked back 5 feet. If this forced movement would cause them to collide with a creature or object, both the target and the creature (if any) take bludgeoning damage equal to your Aim damage. On a critical hit, the target is also knocked prone.", "requirements": "You’re wielding a gun."}]}}',	'Operative',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftTelekineticDefense',	'Telekinetic Defense',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Telekinetic Defense</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 4</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Consular</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Connected</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>A physical ranged attack targets you.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You instinctively bat away a blaster bolt or debris. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack. If the attack misses, you can redirect it. Make a spell attack roll against a target within 30 feet. On a hit, the target takes the damage the original attack would have dealt.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You instinctively bat away a blaster bolt or debris.',	'clsConsular',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powTelekineticDefense", "name": "Telekinetic Defense", "level": 4, "traits": "Consular, Force Power, Connected", "trigger": "A physical ranged attack targets you.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You instinctively bat away a blaster bolt or debris. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack. If the attack misses, you can redirect it. Make a spell attack roll against a target within 30 feet. On a hit, the target takes the damage the original attack would have dealt."}]}}',	'Consular, Connected, Force Power',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForceInfusion',	'Force Infusion',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Force Infusion</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[free-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
