    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid"></div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You yank a weapon from a foe''s grip. Attempt an Athletics check to Disarm a target within 30 feet.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You yank a weapon from a foe''s grip.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powTelekineticDisarm", "name": "Telekinetic Disarm", "level": 4, "traits": "Guardian, Force Power", "action_cost": ["one-action"], "description": "You yank a weapon from a foe''s grip. Attempt an Athletics check to Disarm a target within 30 feet."}]}}',	'Guardian, Force Power',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForceSight',	'Force Sight',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Force Sight</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top"><span class="power-level">Level 2</span></div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Sentinel</span><span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid"></div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You tune your vision to the Force spectrum. For 1 minute, you gain Darkvision. Additionally, you can see the aura of Force-sensitive creatures and active Force effects within 30 feet, even if they are hidden (though they remain concealed to you).
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You tune your vision to the Force spectrum.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powForceSight", "name": "Force Sight", "traits": "Sentinel, Force Power", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You tune your vision to the Force spectrum. For 1 minute, you gain Darkvision. Additionally, you can see the aura of Force-sensitive creatures and active Force effects within 30 feet, even if they are hidden (though they remain concealed to you)."}]}}',	'Sentinel, Force Power',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftInfluence',	'Influence',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Influence</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Envoy</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Emotion</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Fortune</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Mental</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You''re about to roll a Deception, Diplomacy, or Intimidation check, but you haven''t rolled yet.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    With masterful timing and a careful choice of words, you can manipulate the emotions and thoughts of others. You roll the triggering Deception, Diplomacy, or Intimidation check twice, and use the higher result.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'With masterful timing and a careful choice of words, you can manipulate the emotions and thoughts of others.',	'clsEnvoy',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actInfluence", "name": "Influence", "traits": "Envoy, Emotion, Fortune, Mental", "trigger": "You''re about to roll a Deception, Diplomacy, or Intimidation check, but you haven''t rolled yet.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "With masterful timing and a careful choice of words, you can manipulate the emotions and thoughts of others. You roll the triggering Deception, Diplomacy, or Intimidation check twice, and use the higher result."}]}}',	'Emotion, Envoy, Fortune, Mental',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSurgicalPrecision',	'Surgical Precision',	'Your blade finds vital spots—joints, weapon hilt, and exposed armor gaps—with pinpoint accuracy. While in Makashi Stance, your lightsaber attacks against your Dueling Target gain the Fatal d12 trait.

<strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> Your critical hits destroy functionality. On a Critical Hit against your Dueling Target, the target becomes Enfeebled 1 for 1 minute. This represents a severed muscle, damaged servo, or cauterized nerve cluster.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftContentiousRiposte", "type": "form"}]}]',	'Your blade finds vital spots—joints, weapon hilt, and exposed armor gaps—with pinpoint accuracy.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Form',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBasicGuardianTraining',	'Basic Guardian Training',	'You gain a 1st- or 2nd-level Guardian class feat of your choice.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftGuardianDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You gain a 1st- or 2nd-level Guardian class feat of your choice.',	NULL,	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "choice(''target_feat'')", "type": "class_feat"}]}, "inputs": [{"name": "target_feat", "type": "class_feat", "label": "Guardian Feat", "filter": {"trait": ["Guardian"], "max_level": 2}}]}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcGuardian'),
('cftImmovableObject',	'Immovable Object',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Immovable Object</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
