  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You gain Resistance 15 against that energy type for the triggering attack. If you are Focused, you regain HP equal to half the damage prevented.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subCauseOfTheStalwart"}]}]',	'You gain Resistance 15 against that energy type for the triggering attack.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powAbsorbEnergy", "name": "Absorb Energy", "level": 12, "traits": "Guardian, Force Power", "trigger": "You take Energy damage.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You gain Resistance 15 against that energy type for the triggering attack. If you are Focused, you regain HP equal to half the damage prevented."}]}}',	'Guardian, Force Power',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftEnergyShunt',	'Energy Shunt',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Energy Shunt</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You would take cold, electricity, fire, or sonic damage.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You rapidly cycle your rig''s thermal and conductive regulators to absorb the blow. You gain Resistance to the triggering damage type equal to half your level for the duration of the attack or effect.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You rapidly cycle your rig''s thermal and conductive regulators to absorb the blow.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actEnergyShunt", "name": "Energy Shunt", "traits": "Tech Specialist", "trigger": "You would take cold, electricity, fire, or sonic damage.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You rapidly cycle your rig''s thermal and conductive regulators to absorb the blow. You gain Resistance to the triggering damage type equal to half your level for the duration of the attack or effect."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBenevolentAura',	'Benevolent Aura',	'While Connected, your healing powers are more potent. Whenever you cast a Force Power that restores Hit Points to a target other than yourself, roll d10s instead of d8s.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subMandateOfLife"}]}]',	'While Connected, your healing powers are more potent.',	'clsConsular',	NULL,	'Consular, Connected, Healing',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftIronMind',	'Iron Mind',	'The strict discipline of the Resol''nare and your intense martial focus fortify your mind against mystical manipulation. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Will saving throws against mental effects and effects with the Force power trait.

Additionally, your mental training allows you to shake off mental dominance. When you roll a success on a Will save against a mental effect, you get a critical success instead.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftMandalorianDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'The strict discipline of the Resol''nare and your intense martial focus fortify your mind against mystical manipulation.',	NULL,	'{"saving_throw": [{"will": {"bonus": [{"type": "circumstance", "amount": 1, "source": "Iron Mind (Class Feat)"}]}}]}',	'Archetype',	8,	'0',	'arcMandalorian'),
('cftGuardiansFocus',	'Guardian''s Focus',	'You learn to center your mind on the immediate physical conflict, entering a state of hyper-awareness. You gain the Center for Battle action, allowing you to enter the Focused state. While Focused, if you are in a Stance gained from a Lightsaber Form feat, you gain the Guardian Mastery benefit listed in that feat.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftGuardianDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You learn to center your mind on the immediate physical conflict, entering a state of hyper-awareness.',	NULL,	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actCenterForBattle", "name": "Center for Battle", "traits": "Concentrate, Force Power", "frequency": "Once per round", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You clear your mind of distractions. You enter the Focused state. While Focused, if you are in a Stance gained from a Lightsaber Form feat, you gain the Guardian Mastery benefit listed in that feat. If you fall Unconscious, the Focused state ends."}]}}',	'Archetype',	6,	'0',	'arcGuardian'),
('cftSharedVision',	'Shared Vision',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Shared Vision</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
