  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Focused</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Range</strong>
      <span>20-foot emanation</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You slam your fist or weapon into the ground, sending a shockwave through the floor. All creatures in the area (except you) take 6d6 Bludgeoning damage (Basic Reflex save).
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You slam your fist or weapon into the ground, sending a shockwave through the floor.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powQuake", "name": "Quake", "level": 14, "range": "20-foot emanation", "traits": "Guardian, Focused, Force Power", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You slam your fist or weapon into the ground, sending a shockwave through the floor. You slam your fist or weapon into the ground, sending a shockwave through the floor. All creatures in the area (except you) take 6d6 Bludgeoning damage (Basic Reflex save)."}]}}',	'Guardian, Focused, Force Power',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftAdvancedGuardianTraining',	'Advanced Guardian Training',	'You gain one Guardian class feat. For the purpose of meeting its prerequisites, your Guardian level is equal to half your character''s level.<br><br><strong>Special</strong> You can select this feat more than once. Each time you select it, you gain another Guardian class feat.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBasicGuardianTraining", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You gain one Guardian class feat.',	NULL,	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "choice(''target_feat'')", "type": "class_feat"}]}, "inputs": [{"name": "target_feat", "type": "class_feat", "label": "Guardian Feat", "filter": {"trait": ["Guardian"], "max_level": "{slot_level // 2}"}}]}',	'Archetype',	6,	'1',	'arcGuardian'),
('cftBeskarResilience',	'Beskar Resilience',	'Your beskar''gam has been expertly forged and tempered to withstand the searing, plasma-edged cuts of a Jedi''s signature weapon. While wearing medium or heavy armor made of beskar, you gain resistance equal to half your level against damage dealt by weapons of the lightsaber weapon group.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBeskarDeflection", "type": "class"}]}]',	'Your beskar''gam has been expertly forged and tempered to withstand the searing, plasma-edged cuts of a Jedi''s signature weapon.',	NULL,	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "Lightsabers", "amount": "{max(1, level // 2)}", "source": "Beskar Resilience (Class Feat)"}]}}',	'Archetype',	10,	'0',	'arcMandalorian'),
('cftMandalorianWeaponFamiliarity',	'Mandalorian Weapon Familiarity',	'The traditional weapons of Mandalore carry the weight of thousands of years of galactic warfare. You wield these specialized armaments with the practiced ease and ruthless efficiency of your ancestors. You have familiarity with weapons with the Mandalorian trait.  For the purposes of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons.

If you are at least expert in any of these weapons, whenever you get a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftMandalorianDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'The traditional weapons of Mandalore carry the weight of thousands of years of galactic warfare.',	NULL,	'{"attack": {"weapon_familiarity": ["mandalorian"]}}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcMandalorian'),
('cftDeflectingShield',	'Deflecting Shield',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Deflecting Shield</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Form</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You are hit by a ranged energy attack.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You are in Soresu Stance.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack (stacking with your Stance bonus). If this causes the attack to miss, you deflect the bolt harmlessly away.<br><br><strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> If the attack misses, you deflect the bolt back at the attacker. Make a ranged Strike using your lightsaber proficiency. If you hit, you deal the attack''s original damage to the attacker.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftSoresuStance", "type": "form"}]}]',	'You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack (stacking with your Stance bonus). If this causes the attack to miss, you deflect the bolt harmlessly away.',	NULL,	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDeflectingShield", "name": "Deflecting Shield", "traits": "Form", "trigger": "You are hit by a ranged energy attack.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack (stacking with your Stance bonus). If this causes the attack to miss, you deflect the bolt harmlessly away.<br><br><strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> If the attack misses, you deflect the bolt back at the attacker. Make a ranged Strike using your lightsaber proficiency. If you hit, you deal the attack''s original damage to the attacker.", "requirements": "You are in Soresu Stance."}]}}',	'Form',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSweepingTail',	'Sweeping Tail',	'<strong>Prerequisites</strong> animal companion with a tail unarmed attack

Your companion swings its tail powerfully. Your companions with a qualifying unarmed attack learn the Sweeping Tail activity.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Sweeping Tail</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Archetypes</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    This companion makes two tail Strikes against different creatures within its reach, increasing its multiple attack penalty as normal. On a hit, it pushes a target back 5 feet or 10 feet on a critical hit. This is forced movement.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBeastmasterDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'Your companion swings its tail powerfully.',	NULL,	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSweepingTail", "name": "Sweeping Tail", "traits": "Archetype", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "This companion makes two tail Strikes against different creatures within its reach, increasing its multiple attack penalty as normal. On a hit, it pushes a target back 5 feet or 10 feet on a critical hit. This is forced movement."}]}}',	'Archetype',	10,	'0',	'arcBeastmaster'),
('cftForceGhost',	'Force Ghost',	'Death is a lie; there is only the Force. If you die, your consciousness remains. You can manifest as a Force Ghost at will. While a ghost, you are incorporeal, invisible (unless you choose to be seen), and have a fly speed equal to your base movement speed. You cannot attack or affect the physical world, but you can speak and use [Sense] and [Mind] powers that do not deal damage.',	NULL,	'Death is a lie; there is only the Force.',	'clsConsular',	NULL,	'Consular',	20,	'0',	NULL),
('cftForceKick',	'Force Kick',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Force Kick</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You are wielding a lightsaber.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You weave a physical blow into your swordplay. Make an unarmed Strike. If this attack hits, the target becomes Off-Guard to your next Lightsaber attack before the end of your next turn.<br><br><b>Focused Benefit</b> On a hit, you can push the target 5 feet.  This gives this action the [Focused] trait.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You weave a physical blow into your swordplay.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actForceKick", "name": "Force Kick", "traits": "Guardian", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You weave a physical blow into your swordplay. Make an unarmed Strike. If this attack hits, the target becomes Off-Guard to your next Lightsaber attack before the end of your next turn.<br><br><b>Focused Benefit</b> On a hit, you can push the target 5 feet.  This gives this action the [Focused] trait.", "requirements": "You are wielding a lightsaber."}]}}',	'Guardian',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftRemoteHack',	'Remote Slice',	'Your connection to machines is absolute. You can use Computers and Thievery (Disable Device) at a range of 30 feet. If you have a datajack, this range increases to 60 feet.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subPathOfTheArtisan"}]}]',	'Your connection to machines is absolute.',	'clsSentinel',	NULL,	'Sentinel, Force Power',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftQuickSwap',	'Quick Swap',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Quick Swap</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>An enemy creature moves adjacent to you.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>once per hour</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a two-handed weapon.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You can switch weapons in stressful situations so that you quickly set yourself up to punish incoming foes. You stow your current weapon and draw another two-handed weapon. If you have multiple sets of arms, you can instead Switch Hands.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You can switch weapons in stressful situations so that you quickly set yourself up to punish incoming foes.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actQuickSwap", "name": "Quick Swap", "traits": "Soldier", "trigger": "An enemy creature moves adjacent to you.", "frequency": "once per hour", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You can switch weapons in stressful situations so that you quickly set yourself up to punish incoming foes. You stow your current weapon and draw another two-handed weapon. If you have multiple sets of arms, you can instead Switch Hands.", "requirements": "You’re wielding a two-handed weapon."}]}}',	'Soldier',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftInstantInvestigation',	'Instant Investigation',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Instant Investigation</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[free-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Sentinel</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You roll initiative.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You scan the battlefield instantly. You can Recall Knowledge about every enemy you can see. For each success, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC against that specific enemy for the first round of combat.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You scan the battlefield instantly.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actInstantInvestigation", "name": "Instant Investigation", "traits": "Sentinel", "trigger": "You roll initiative.", "action_cost": "[free-action]", "description": "You scan the battlefield instantly. You can Recall Knowledge about every enemy you can see. For each success, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC against that specific enemy for the first round of combat."}]}}',	'Sentinel',	16,	'0',	NULL),
('cftTerrainScout',	'Terrain Scout',	'You have mastered movement in many different environments. You gain the Terrain Stalker skill feat twice, choosing a different terrain each time. If you Avoid Notice while exploring and any allies use Follow the Expert to follow you as you do so, you can choose one of those allies to gain the benefit of any one Terrain Stalker feat you have.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftScoutDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You have mastered movement in many different environments.',	NULL,	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "feaTerrainStalker", "type": "skill"}, {"id": "feaTerrainStalker", "type": "skill"}]}}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcScout'),
('cftForceBreach',	'Force Breach',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Force Breach</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Focused</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You channel kinetic energy into a single object-shattering blow. Make a melee Strike against an unattended object, structure, or door. You ignore up to 10 Hardness on this Strike. If you destroy the object, you can immediately make an Intimidation check to Demoralize creatures within 30 feet.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You channel kinetic energy into a single object-shattering blow.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actForceBreach", "name": "Force Breach", "traits": "Guardian, Focused", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You channel kinetic energy into a single object-shattering blow. Make a melee Strike against an unattended object, structure, or door. You ignore up to 10 Hardness on this Strike. If you destroy the object, you can immediately make an Intimidation check to Demoralize creatures within 30 feet."}]}}',	'Guardian',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSilencingStrike',	'Silencing Strike',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Silencing Strike</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top"><span class="power-level">Level 4</span></div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Sentinel</span><span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid"></div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You attack the throat or the mind. Make a melee Strike. If it hits, the target takes normal damage and must make a Fortitude save against your Class DC. On a failure, the target is Silenced (cannot speak or use any effects with the Linguistic trait) until the end of your next turn.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subPathOfTheJusticar"}]}]',	'You attack the throat or the mind.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powSilencingStrike", "name": "Silencing Strike", "traits": "Sentinel, Force Power", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You attack the throat or the mind. Make a melee Strike. If it hits, the target takes normal damage and must make a Fortitude save against your Class DC. On a failure, the target is Silenced (cannot speak or use any effects with the Linguistic trait) until the end of your next turn."}]}}',	'Sentinel, Force Power',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSideBySide',	'Side by Side',	'You and your animal companion fight in tandem, distracting your foes and keeping them off balance. Whenever you and your animal companion are adjacent to the same foe, you are both flanking that foe with each other, regardless of your actual positions.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBeastmasterDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You and your animal companion fight in tandem, distracting your foes and keeping them off balance.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Archetype',	14,	'0',	'arcBeastmaster'),
('cftPunishingSalvo',	'Punishing Salvo',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Punishing Salvo</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>Your last action this turn was an Area Fire attack.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You know unleashing a barrage of gunfire can bring most enemies low. You make a follow-up Strike against your primary target using the same weapon. Ignore the unwieldy trait on your weapon when using this action. This doesn’t make a new area attack and is treated as a Strike made using primary target.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You know unleashing a barrage of gunfire can bring most enemies low.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actPunishingSalvo", "name": "Punishing Salvo", "traits": "Soldier", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You know unleashing a barrage of gunfire can bring most enemies low. You make a follow-up Strike against your primary target using the same weapon. Ignore the unwieldy trait on your weapon when using this action. This doesn’t make a new area attack and is treated as a Strike made using primary target.", "requirements": "Your last action this turn was an Area Fire attack."}]}}',	'Soldier',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftRelentlessEndurance',	'Relentless Endurance',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Relentless Endurance</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You take damage.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You bounce back stronger after a hit, ready to continue the f ight. You gain 1d8+4 temporary Hit Points that last for 1 minute. Increase this amount by 1d8+4 at 6th level and every 4 levels thereafter.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You bounce back stronger after a hit, ready to continue the f ight.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actRelentlessEndurance", "name": "Relentless Endurance", "traits": "Soldier", "trigger": "You take damage.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You bounce back stronger after a hit, ready to continue the f ight. You gain 1d8+4 temporary Hit Points that last for 1 minute. Increase this amount by 1d8+4 at 6th level and every 4 levels thereafter."}]}}',	'Soldier',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDeathBlossom',	'Death Blossom',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Death Blossom</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[three-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding an area or automatic weapon with a full magazine.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Spinning in place, you fire indiscriminately to completely clear out the room. You Area Fire (even if using an automatic weapon), affecting each creature in an emanation around you with a radius equal to the range of the weapon, expending the weapon’s entire magazine. Creatures in the area take a –1 circumstance penalty to Reflex saves against this attack due to the cataclysmic nature of the raining fire. You don’t designate a primary target with this attack.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"feat": {"id": "cftRunHot", "type": "class"}}]',	'Spinning in place, you fire indiscriminately to completely clear out the room.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actDeathBlossom", "name": "Death Blossom", "traits": "Soldier", "action_cost": "[three-actions]", "description": "Spinning in place, you fire indiscriminately to completely clear out the room. You Area Fire (even if using an automatic weapon), affecting each creature in an emanation around you with a radius equal to the range of the weapon, expending the weapon’s entire magazine. Creatures in the area take a –1 circumstance penalty to Reflex saves against this attack due to the cataclysmic nature of the raining fire. You don’t designate a primary target with this attack.", "requirements": "You’re wielding an area or automatic weapon with a full magazine."}]}}',	'Soldier',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftPhaseStep',	'Phase Step',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Phase Step</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top"><span class="power-level">Level 10</span></div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Sentinel</span><span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span><span class="trait-tag">Teleportation</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid"></div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You dissolve into shadows and reappear elsewhere. You teleport up to 60 feet to a space you can see that is in dim light or darkness.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subPathOfTheShadow"}]}]',	'You dissolve into shadows and reappear elsewhere.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powPhaseStep", "name": "Phase Step", "traits": "Sentinel, Force Power, Teleportation", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You dissolve into shadows and reappear elsewhere. You teleport up to 60 feet to a space you can see that is in dim light or darkness."}]}}',	'Sentinel, Force Power, Teleportation',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftIllBeBack',	'I''ll Be Back',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">I''ll Be Back</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[free-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
