    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You draw on your inner reserves and rally yourself to try again. Reroll the triggering check, but you must use the new result, even if it’s worse.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You draw on your inner reserves and rally yourself to try again.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actBurstOfStrength", "name": "Burst of Strength", "traits": "Soldier, Fortune", "trigger": "You fail an Athletics check to Disarm, Grapple, Reposition, Shove, or Trip.", "frequency": "once per hour", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You draw on your inner reserves and rally yourself to try again. Reroll the triggering check, but you must use the new result, even if it’s worse."}]}}',	'Fortune, Soldier',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftWeakeningShot',	'Weakening Shot',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Weakening Shot</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a gun.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You target a creature’s limbs or load-bearing appendages to weaken them. You Aim and then make a ranged Strike against your mark. If the Strike hits, the creature becomes your choice of clumsy 1 or enfeebled 1 until the end of your next turn (clumsy 2 or enfeebled 2 on a critical hit).
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You target a creature’s limbs or load-bearing appendages to weaken them.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actWeakeningShot", "name": "Weakening Shot", "traits": "Operative", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You target a creature’s limbs or load-bearing appendages to weaken them. You Aim and then make a ranged Strike against your mark. If the Strike hits, the creature becomes your choice of clumsy 1 or enfeebled 1 until the end of your next turn (clumsy 2 or enfeebled 2 on a critical hit).", "requirements": "You’re wielding a gun."}]}}',	'Operative',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftModularExpansion',	'Modular Expansion',	'You have optimized your custom rig''s power draw, allowing it to sustain more active schematics simultaneously. You gain one additional modification slot. During your daily preparations, you can install one additional Modification from your Modification Library.',	NULL,	'You have optimized your custom rig''s power draw, allowing it to sustain more active schematics simultaneously.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	NULL,	'Tech Specialist',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftHamperingShot',	'Hampering Shot',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Hampering Shot</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
