    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You hinder your target with a shot. You Aim and then make a ranged Strike against your mark. If the Strike hits, the target is slowed 1 until the end of its next turn. If the target is flying, it also falls 10 feet.
