  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You assess a foe while in the thick of battle by observing their reactions to your attack. Make a melee or ranged Strike against a creature that isn''t your asset. On a hit, your target becomes your asset as if you''d used Size Up. On a critical hit, you can also immediately attempt a check to Recall Knowledge about the target.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftSizeUp", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You assess a foe while in the thick of battle by observing their reactions to your attack.',	'clsEnvoy',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actAcquireAsset", "name": "Acquire Asset", "traits": "Envoy, Flourish", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You assess a foe while in the thick of battle by observing their reactions to your attack. Make a melee or ranged Strike against a creature that isn''t your asset. On a hit, your target becomes your asset as if you''d used Size Up. On a critical hit, you can also immediately attempt a check to Recall Knowledge about the target."}]}}',	'Envoy, Flourish',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftGuardiansIntercession',	'Guardian''s Intercession',	'You have learned to use the Force to dampen impacts and intercept attacks meant for your allies. You gain the Intercede reaction.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftGuardianDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You have learned to use the Force to dampen impacts and intercept attacks meant for your allies.',	NULL,	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "actIntercede", "name": "Intercede", "level": 1, "traits": "Guardian, Focused, Force Power", "trigger": "An enemy damages an ally within 15 feet of you.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You project a telekinetic cushion or physically intercept the blow. The damage the ally takes is reduced by  2 + your Level. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your next Attack roll against the triggering enemy before the end of your next turn."}]}}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcGuardian'),
('cftOverrideCommand',	'Override Command',	'<div class="power-card-display">
