  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You brace yourself as you prepare to defend your allies behind you. You Area Fire or Auto-Fire. Until the start of your next turn or until you use a move action, whichever happens first, you gain the Living Shield reaction and, if you would be moved by a forced movement effect, you move 10 feet less.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You brace yourself as you prepare to defend your allies behind you.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actYoullHaveToGoThroughMe", "name": "You''ll Have to Go Through Me", "traits": "Soldier", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You brace yourself as you prepare to defend your allies behind you. You Area Fire or Auto-Fire. Until the start of your next turn or until you use a move action, whichever happens first, you gain the Living Shield reaction and, if you would be moved by a forced movement effect, you move 10 feet less."}, {"id": "actLivingShield", "name": "Living Shield", "traits": "Soldier", "trigger": "An ally you’re providing cover to or adjacent to is damaged by an enemy", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "Reduce the triggering damage by an amount equal to your level plus your Constitution modifier. You take an amount of damage equal to the damage negated."}]}}',	'Soldier',	2,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBattleAssessment',	'Battle Assessment',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Battle Assessment</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
