  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You observe a foe to gauge their capabilities. Choose a creature within 30 feet and attempt a Perception check against their Deception DC.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> You learn two of the following: The target''s highest Saving Throw, lowest Saving Throw, or current approximate HP quartile (full, wounded, bloodied, or near-death).<br><strong>Success</strong> You learn one of the above.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You learn nothing.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You misjudge the target, learning false information.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You observe a foe to gauge their capabilities.',	'clsSentinel',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actBattleAssessment", "name": "Battle Assessment", "traits": "Sentinel, Secret", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You observe a foe to gauge their capabilities. Choose a creature within 30 feet and attempt a Perception check against their Deception DC.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> You learn two of the following: The target''s highest Saving Throw, lowest Saving Throw, or current approximate HP quartile (full, wounded, bloodied, or near-death).<br><strong>Success</strong> You learn one of the above.<br><strong>Failure</strong> You learn nothing.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You misjudge the target, learning false information."}]}}',	'Sentinel, Secret',	1,	'0',	NULL),
('cftHeightenedInstincts',	'Heightened Instincts',	'You''ve worked to sharpen your companions'' instincts to near-supernatural levels. When one of your companions rolls a success on a saving throw, it gets a critical success instead.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBeastmasterDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You''ve worked to sharpen your companions'' instincts to near-supernatural levels.',	NULL,	NULL,	'Archetype',	18,	'0',	'arcBeastmaster'),
('cftBasicLeadership',	'Basic Leadership',	'You gain a 1st- or 2nd-level envoy feat of your choice.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftEnvoyDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You gain a 1st- or 2nd-level envoy feat of your choice.',	NULL,	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "choice(''target_feat'')", "type": "class_feat"}]}, "inputs": [{"name": "target_feat", "type": "class_feat", "label": "Envoy Feat", "filter": {"trait": ["Envoy"], "max_level": 2}}]}',	'Archetype',	4,	'0',	'arcEnvoy'),
('cftDigitalPhantom',	'Digital Phantom',	'Your custom rig runs constant, passive spoofing routines that render you practically invisible to technological targeting systems. You are permanently concealed against standard attacks made by creatures with the construct trait and hazards with the tech trait. Additionally, your localized jamming throws off the predictive algorithms of heavy weaponry, granting you a +2 circumstance bonus to Reflex saving throws against Auto-Fire and Area Fire actions. Furthermore, automated technological sensors (such as security cameras or thermal scanners) cannot detect you unless the sensor''s level is higher than your own.',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subSlicer"}]}]',	'Your custom rig runs constant, passive spoofing routines that render you practically invisible to technological targeting systems.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	NULL,	'Tech Specialist',	14,	'0',	NULL),
('cftCheerUp',	'Cheer Up',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Cheer Up</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
