    <span class="trait-tag">Healing</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">

  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You encourage an adjacent ally to overcome their minor ailments by patting them on the back, providing them useful advice, or offering some form of comfort or inspiration. The target reduces the value of one of the following conditions of their choice by 2: clumsy, enfeebled, frightened, sickened, stupefied. The target then becomes temporarily immune to Cheer Up for 1 day.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"skill": [{"id": "sklMedicine", "rank": "Trained"}]}]',	'You encourage an adjacent ally to overcome their minor ailments by patting them on the back, providing them useful advice, or offering some form of comfort or inspiration.',	'clsEnvoy',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actCheerUp", "name": "Cheer Up", "traits": "Envoy, Healing", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You encourage an adjacent ally to overcome their minor ailments by patting them on the back, providing them useful advice, or offering some form of comfort or inspiration. The target reduces the value of one of the following conditions of their choice by 2: clumsy, enfeebled, frightened, sickened, stupefied. The target then becomes temporarily immune to Cheer Up for 1 day."}]}}',	'Envoy, Healing',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftAdaptiveTalent',	'Adaptive Talent',	'You gain the adaptive talent class feature, but you do not gain additional skill feats at higher levels.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftEnvoyDedication", "type": "class"}]}]',	'You gain the adaptive talent class feature, but you do not gain additional skill feats at higher levels.',	NULL,	'{"feature": ["clfAdaptiveTalent"]}',	'Archetype',	6,	'0',	'arcEnvoy'),
('cftDownToTheWire',	'Down to the Wire',	'<div class="power-card-display">
