  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You’re about to roll initiative.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You read the demeanor, body language, and instinctive tics of your foes as easily as you read a comm unit, allowing you to react a moment before those around you and gain an edge in the coming battle. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your initiative roll, and you can immediately do one of the following: Interact to draw a weapon, Step, or Stride.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You read the demeanor, body language, and instinctive tics of your foes as easily as you read a comm unit, allowing you to react a moment before those around you and gain an edge in the coming battle.',	'clsEnvoy',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSawItComing", "name": "Saw it Coming", "traits": "Envoy, Traversal", "trigger": "You’re about to roll initiative.", "action_cost": "[free-action]", "description": "You read the demeanor, body language, and instinctive tics of your foes as easily as you read a comm unit, allowing you to react a moment before those around you and gain an edge in the coming battle. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your initiative roll, and you can immediately do one of the following: Interact to draw a weapon, Step, or Stride."}]}}',	'Envoy, Traversal',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftGotEm',	'Got ‘Em!',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
