  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You surge forward to take the blow. You Stride up to 20 feet to end your movement adjacent to the ally. You then use your Intercede reaction against the triggering attack.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You surge forward to take the blow.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actInterceptingCharge", "name": "Intercepting Charge", "traits": "Guardian, Focused, Move", "trigger": "An ally within 20 feet is targeted by a melee attack.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You surge forward to take the blow. You Stride up to 20 feet to end your movement adjacent to the ally. You then use your Intercede reaction against the triggering attack."}]}}',	'Guardian, Focused, Move',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftReactiveStrike',	'Reactive Strike',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Reactive Strike</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[reaction]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>A creature within your reach uses a manipulate action or a move action, makes a ranged attack, or leaves a square during a move action it’s using.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You lash out at a foe that leaves an opening. Make a melee Strike against the triggering creature. If your attack is a critical hit and the trigger was a manipulate action, you disrupt that action.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You lash out at a foe that leaves an opening.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actReactiveStrike", "name": "Reactive Strike", "traits": "Guardian", "trigger": "A creature within your reach uses a manipulate action or a move action, makes a ranged attack, or leaves a square during a move action it’s using.", "action_cost": "[reaction]", "description": "You lash out at a foe that leaves an opening. Make a melee Strike against the triggering creature. If your attack is a critical hit and the trigger was a manipulate action, you disrupt that action."}]}}',	'Guardian',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftDrawCloser',	'Draw Closer',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Draw Closer</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 4</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Form</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Range</strong>
      <span>30 feet</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Target</strong>
      <span>1 creature</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You are in Niman Stance.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You pull an enemy into your blade. The target must succeed at a Fortitude save or be pulled adjacent to you. If they are pulled adjacent to you, you can immediately make a melee Strike against them.<br><br><strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> The Strike gains a +2 circumstance bonus to the attack roll (stacking with the bonus from your Stance).
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftNimanStance", "type": "form"}]}]',	'You pull an enemy into your blade.',	NULL,	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powDrawCloser", "name": "Draw Closer", "range": "30 feet", "target": "1 creature", "traits": "Form, Force Power", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "You pull an enemy into your blade. The target must succeed at a Fortitude save or be pulled adjacent to you. If they are pulled adjacent to you, you can immediately make a melee Strike against them.<br><br><strong>Guardian Mastery</strong> The Strike gains a +2 circumstance bonus to the attack roll (stacking with the bonus from your Stance).", "requirements": "You are in Niman Stance."}]}}',	'Form, Force Power',	4,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSeveringStrike',	'Severing Strike',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Severing Strike</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top">
      <span class="power-level">Level 12</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Guardian</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Focused</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Force Power</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid"></div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You strike to disable. Make a melee Strike. If it hits and deals damage, the target must make a Fortitude save against your Class DC.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> The target is Enfeebled 1 until the end of its next turn.<br><strong>Failure</strong> The target is Enfeebled 2 for 1 minute.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is Enfeebled 3 for 1 minute.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You strike to disable.',	'clsGuardian',	'{"power": {"grant": [{"id": "powSeveringStrike", "name": "Severing Strike", "level": 12, "traits": "Guardian, Focused, Force Power", "action_cost": ["two-actions"], "description": "You strike to disable. Make a melee Strike. If it hits and deals damage, the target must make a Fortitude save against your Class DC.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> The target is Enfeebled 1 until the end of its next turn.<br><strong>Failure</strong> The target is Enfeebled 2 for 1 minute.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is Enfeebled 3 for 1 minute."}]}}',	'Guardian, Focused, Force Power',	12,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBringItOn',	'Bring It On!',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Bring It On!</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Soldier</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Requirements</strong>
      <span>You’re wielding a two-handed weapon.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    Your sheer bravado bolsters your defenses despite your recklessness. Until the start of your next turn, you take a –2 circumstance penalty to AC and gain resistance to all damage equal to half your level. If you have the armor storm fighting style, this resistance is doubled against attacks made by suppressed creatures.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'Your sheet bravado bolsters your defenses despite your recklessness.',	'clsSoldier',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actBringItOn", "name": "Bring It On!", "traits": "Soldier", "action_cost": "[one-action]", "description": "Your sheer bravado bolsters your defenses despite your recklessness. Until the start of your next turn, you take a –2 circumstance penalty to AC and gain resistance to all damage equal to half your level. If you have the armor storm fighting style, this resistance is doubled against attacks made by suppressed creatures.", "requirements": "You’re wielding a two-handed weapon."}]}}',	'Soldier',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftKickItIntoOverdrive',	'Kick it into Overdrive',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Kick it into Overdrive</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[free-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Operative</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Traversal</span>
  </div>

  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>Your turn begins.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>once per hour</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="power-card-divider" />

  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    With a steadying breath and a moment of intense focus, you push yourself beyond your limits, gaining incredible speed for a short period of time. You become quickened until the end of your turn, and you can use the extra action only to Stride.<br><br>When you use this ability, you can instead choose to become quickened until the end of your next turn, but at the end of this duration, you become fatigued for 2 rounds as your body recovers. You can still only use the extra action from quickened to Stride with this effect.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'With a steadying breath and a moment of intense focus, you push yourself beyond your limits, gaining incredible speed for a short period of time.',	'clsOperative',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actKickItIntoOverdrive", "name": "Kick it into Overdrive", "traits": "Operative, Traversal", "trigger": "Your turn begins.", "frequency": "once per hour", "action_cost": "[free-action]", "description": "With a steadying breath and a moment of intense focus, you push yourself beyond your limits, gaining incredible speed for a short period of time. You become quickened until the end of your turn, and you can use the extra action only to Stride.\n\nWhen you use this ability, you can instead choose to become quickened until the end of your next turn, but at the end of this duration, you become fatigued for 2 rounds as your body recovers. You can still only use the extra action from quickened to Stride with this effect."}]}}',	'Operative',	6,	'0',	NULL),
('cftAdvancedTechFeatures',	'Advanced Tech Features',	'Your continuous tinkering yields complex results. You gain one Tech Specialist class feat. For the purpose of meeting its prerequisites, your Tech Specialist level is equal to half your character level.<br><br><strong>Special</strong> You can select this feat more than once. Each time you select it, you gain another Tech Specialist class feat.',	'[{"feat": [{"id": "cftBasicTechFeatures", "type": "class"}]}]',	'Your continuous tinkering yields complex results.',	NULL,	'{"feat": {"fixed": [{"id": "choice(''target_feat'')", "type": "class_feat"}]}, "inputs": [{"name": "target_feat", "type": "class_feat", "label": "Tech Specialist Feat", "filter": {"trait": ["Tech Specialist"], "max_level": "{slot_level // 2}"}, "class_id": "clsTechSpecialist"}]}',	'Archetype',	6,	'1',	'arcTechSpecialist'),
('cftAdaptiveEnergyEmitter',	'Adaptive Energy Emitter',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Adaptive Energy Emitter</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[free-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Trigger</strong>
      <span>You make a ranged Strike with a weapon that deals energy damage, or you activate a Modification that deals energy damage.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per turn.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You instantly recalibrate your weapon''s focal lens or your rig''s output frequency. You change the damage type of the triggering Strike or Modification to your choice of cold, electricity, or fire damage.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You instantly recalibrate your weapon''s focal lens or your rig''s output frequency.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actAdaptiveEnergyEmitter", "name": "Adaptive Energy Emitter", "traits": "Tech Specialist", "trigger": "You make a ranged Strike with a weapon that deals energy damage, or you activate a Modification that deals energy damage.", "frequency": "Once per turn.", "action_cost": "[free-action]", "description": "You instantly recalibrate your weapon''s focal lens or your rig''s output frequency. You change the damage type of the triggering Strike or Modification to your choice of cold, electricity, or fire damage."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftBruteForceExecution',	'Brute-Force Execution',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Brute-Force Execution</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions] or [three-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Manipulate</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You force your custom rig to rapidly compile and execute a schematic from your deep storage drives that you didn''t actively install this morning. You can immediately activate a Modification with a one-action activation cost that is not currently installed. If you spend three actions, you can instead activate a Modification with a two-action cost.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You force your custom rig to rapidly compile and execute a schematic from your deep storage drives that you didn''t actively install this morning.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actBruteForceExecution", "name": "Brute-Force Execution", "traits": "Tech Specialist, Manipulate", "frequency": "Once per day.", "action_cost": "[two-actions] or [three-actions]", "description": "You force your custom rig to rapidly compile and execute a schematic from your deep storage drives that you didn''t actively install this morning. You can immediately activate a Modification with a one-action activation cost that is not currently installed. If you spend three actions, you can instead activate a Modification with a two-action cost."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist, Manipulate',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftScrapBarricade',	'Scrap Barricade',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Scrap Barricade</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Manipulate</span>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You rapidly magnetize and fuse surrounding loose material into a defensive bulwark. You create a 10-foot-long, 5-foot-high wall of junk in unoccupied squares within 30 feet. The wall provides standard cover. It has Hardness equal to your level and Hit Points equal to three times your level. The wall collapses into harmless debris after 1 minute or when reduced to 0 Hit Points. You cannot use Scrap Barricade again for 10 minutes.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subScrapper"}]}]',	'You rapidly magnetize and fuse surrounding loose material into a defensive bulwark.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actScrapBarricade", "name": "Scrap Barricade", "traits": "Tech Specialist, Manipulate", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You rapidly magnetize and fuse surrounding loose material into a defensive bulwark. You create a 10-foot-long, 5-foot-high wall of junk in unoccupied squares within 30 feet. The wall provides standard cover. It has Hardness equal to your level and Hit Points equal to three times your level. The wall collapses into harmless debris after 1 minute or when reduced to 0 Hit Points. You cannot use Scrap Barricade again for 10 minutes."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist, Manipulate',	8,	'0',	NULL),
('cftCombatTriage',	'Combat Triage',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Combat Triage</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You physically interpose yourself to keep your allies in the fight. You Stride up to your Speed, and then immediately perform the Administer First Aid or Treat Poison action on an adjacent ally. If your skill check is successful, the targeted ally can immediately Crawl or Step as a free action.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subBioTech"}]}]',	'You physically interpose yourself to keep your allies in the fight.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actCombatTriage", "name": "Combat Triage", "traits": "Tech Specialist", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You physically interpose yourself to keep your allies in the fight. You Stride up to your Speed, and then immediately perform the Administer First Aid or Treat Poison action on an adjacent ally. If your skill check is successful, the targeted ally can immediately Crawl or Step as a free action."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftSystemLockout',	'System Lockout',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">System Lockout</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[two-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You violently throttle an enemy''s hardware resources. Attempt a Computers check against the Fortitude DC or Will DC (whichever is higher) of a target within 30 feet that has the construct trait or is wearing technological armor.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> The target''s operating system lags. It is suppressed until the end of its next turn.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> As success, but the suppressed condition lasts until the end of your next turn.
  </div>
</div>',	'[{"subclass": [{"id": "subSlicer"}]}]',	'You violently throttle an enemy''s hardware resources.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actSystemLockout", "name": "System Lockout", "traits": "Tech Specialist", "action_cost": "[two-actions]", "description": "You violently throttle an enemy''s hardware resources. Attempt a Computers check against the Fortitude DC or Will DC (whichever is higher) of a target within 30 feet that has the construct trait or is wearing technological armor.<br><br><strong>Success</strong> The target''s operating system lags. It is suppressed until the end of its next turn.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> As success, but the suppressed condition lasts until the end of your next turn."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftHotSwappableMemory',	'Hot-Swappable Memory',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Hot-Swappable Memory</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[three-actions]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Concentrate</span>
    <span class="trait-tag">Manipulate</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
