    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You rapidly recompile your rig''s active drivers and physically slam a new data-drive into your terminal, completely bypassing standard boot sequences. You swap out one Modification you currently have installed for another Modification from your Modification Library. You then immediately activate the newly installed Modification, provided its normal activation cost is 1 or 2 actions.
  </div>
</div>',	NULL,	'You rapidly recompile your rig''s active drivers and physically slam a new data-drive into your terminal, completely bypassing standard boot sequences.',	'clsTechSpecialist',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actHotSwappableMemory", "name": "Hot-Swappable Memory", "traits": "Tech Specialist, Concentrate, Manipulate", "action_cost": "[three-actions]", "description": "You rapidly recompile your rig''s active drivers and physically slam a new data-drive into your terminal, completely bypassing standard boot sequences. You swap out one Modification you currently have installed for another Modification from your Modification Library. You then immediately activate the newly installed Modification, provided its normal activation cost is 1 or 2 actions.", "requirements": "Once per day."}]}}',	'Tech Specialist, Concentrate, Manipulate',	10,	'0',	NULL),
('cftWetwareOverclock',	'Wetware Overclock',	'<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Wetware Overclock</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action]</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Tech Specialist</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Frequency</strong>
      <span>Once per day.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">
    You temporarily bypass the core safety limiters on your custom rig and your own nervous system. For 1 minute, you gain the quickened condition. You can use this extra action only to Stride, Step, or activate a Modification.
  </div>
