('clfSilverTongue',	'Silver Tongue',	'Your savvy and skill are unparalleled. Your proficiency rank for your envoy class DC increases to master. You gain the Silver Tongue action:

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
