Resolve',	'{"perception": {"rank": "Master"}}'),
('clfIncredibleSenses',	'Incredible Senses',	'You notice things that are almost impossible for an ordinary person to detect. Your proficiency rank for Perception increases to legendary.',	'{"perception": {"rank": "Legendary"}}'),
('clfFortitudeExpertise',	'Fortitude Expertise',	'Your physique is incredibly hardy. Your proficiency rank for Fortitude saves increases to expert.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"fortitude": {"rank": "Expert"}}]}'),
('clfGreaterResolve',	'Greater Resolve',	'Your ambition and stubbornness grant you mental resiliency. Your proficiency rank for Will saves increases to legendary. When you roll a success on a Will save, you get a critical success instead. When you roll a critical failure on a Will save, you get a failure instead. When you fail a Will save against a damaging effect, you take half damage.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"will": {"rank": "Legendary"}}]}'),
('clfTechSpecialistExpertise',	'Tech Specialist Expertise',	'Your hands-on experience has improved your engineering skills. Your proficiency rank for your tech specialist class DC increases to expert.',	'{"dc": [{"name": "Tech Specialist Class DC", "rank": "Expert", "attribute": "INT"}]}'),
('clfSkillIncreaseLegendary',	'Skill Increase (Legendary)',	'At 3rd level and every 2 levels thereafter, you gain a skill increase. You can use this increase either to increase your proficiency rank to trained in one skill you''re untrained in, or to increase your proficiency rank in one skill in which you''re already trained to expert.

At 7th level, you can use skill increases to increase your proficiency rank to master in a skill in which you''re already an expert, and at 15th level, you can use them to increase your proficiency rank to legendary in a skill in which you''re already a master.',	'{"skill": {"skill_increase": [{"max": "Legendary", "count": 1}]}}'),
('clfOneWithTheForce',	'One with the Force',	'Your body is merely a vessel for the Force. You gain resistance to all damage equal to your Wisdom modifier. Additionally, once per day, if you would be reduced to 0 Hit Points, you can instead remain at 1 Hit Point and immediately enter the Connected state (even if it isn''t your turn).',	'{"defense": {"resistance": [{"type": "All", "amount": "{WIS}", "source": "One with the Force (Consular Feature)"}]}}'),
('clfEnvoyDirectives',	'Envoy Directives',	'Envoys encourage their allies with directives. A directive is an order that benefits allies who follow it. Envoy directives include a way for the envoy to lead by example by spending more actions for increased effects. Directives have the auditory or visual trait depending on how you inspire your allies.

You begin with one envoy directive. You can learn more directives through the envoy class, envoy class feats, and your leadership style. You can issue one directive a round. Unless otherwise stated, an envoy''s directive and the benefits it grants last until the beginning of your next turn.

You gain the Get ''Em! envoy directive.

<div class="power-card-display">
  <header class="power-card-header">
    <div class="power-title-line">
      <h3 class="power-name">Get ''Em</h3>
      <span class="power-action-cost">[one-action] or [two-actions]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="power-meta-top"><span class="power-level">Feature</span></div>
  </header>
  <div class="power-card-traits">
    <span class="trait-tag">Envoy</span><span class="trait-tag">Directive</span>
  </div>
  <div class="power-card-meta-grid">
  </div>
  <hr class="power-card-divider" />
  <div class="power-card-description markdown-body">You single out an enemy for you and your allies to focus your attacks on. Select an enemy within 60 feet that you can see. You and your allies gain a +1 status bonus to attacks against that target until the beginning of your next turn.<br><br><b>Lead by Example</b> If you used two actions, Strike the target. You gain a status bonus to the damage roll equal to your Charisma modifier. Regardless of whether the Strike hits, you and your allies gain a +1 status bonus to damage on subsequent Strikes made against the enemy until the start of your next turn. Increase the damage by 1 at 5th, 10th, 15th, and 20th levels.
  </div>
</div>',	'{"action": {"grant": [{"id": "actGetEm", "name": "Get ''Em", "traits": "Envoy, Directive", "action_cost": "[one-action] or [two-actions]", "description": "You single out an enemy for you and your allies to focus your attacks on. Select an enemy within 60 feet that you can see. You and your allies gain a +1 status bonus to attacks against that target until the beginning of your next turn.<br><br><b>Lead by Example</b> If you used two actions, Strike the target. You gain a status bonus to the damage roll equal to your Charisma modifier. Regardless of whether the Strike hits, you and your allies gain a +1 status bonus to damage on subsequent Strikes made against the enemy until the start of your next turn. Increase the damage by 1 at 5th, 10th, 15th, and 20th levels."}]}}'),
('clfIronWill',	'Iron Will',	'Your training allows you to shrug off mental influence. Your proficiency rank for Will saves increases to Legendary. When you roll a critical success on a Will save, you treat the result as one degree of success better.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"will": {"rank": "Legendary"}}]}'),
('clfConsularWeaponExpertise',	'Consular Weapon Expertise',	'You have dedicated yourself to the art of the lightsaber as a meditative practice. Your proficiency ranks for simple weapons, lightsabers, and unarmed attacks increase to expert. You gain access to the critical specialization effects of lightsabers.',	'{"attack": [{"simple": {"rank": "Expert"}}, {"unarmed": {"rank": "Expert"}}, {"group": [{"lightsaber": {"rank": "Expert"}}]}]}'),
('clfConsularExpertise',	'Consular Expertise',	'Your command of the Force deepens. Your proficiency rank for your consular class DC increases to expert.',	'{"dc": [{"name": "Consular Class DC", "rank": "Expert"}]}'),
('clfSerenity',	'Serenity',	'Your calm mind is a fortress. If you start your turn Confused, Controlled, or Frightened, you can reduce the value of the condition by 1 and can attempt a new save against the effect immediately as a free action.',	NULL),
('clfVigilance',	'Vigilance',	'Your reflexes are honed by precognition. Your proficiency rank for Reflex saves increases to Expert. When you roll a success on a Reflex save, you get a critical success instead.',	'{"saving_throw": [{"reflex": {"rank": "Expert"}}]}'),
('clfConsularWeaponMastery',	'Consular Weapon Mastery',	'Through skill and dedication, you have mastered the lightsaber. Your proficiency ranks for simple weapons, lightsabers, and unarmed attacks increase to master.',	'{"attack": [{"simple": {"rank": "Master"}}, {"unarmed": {"rank": "Master"}}, {"group": [{"lightsaber": {"rank": "Master"}}]}]}'),
