('idBooma',	'Booma',	0,	'1',	NULL,	'Ammunition, Area (Burst 5ft), Electricity, Grenade, Gungan',	'Mined from the porous, plasma-rich crust deep within Naboo''s oceans, boomas are spheres of highly pressurized, naturally occurring energy. They are contained within a fragile, translucent organic membrane that keeps the volatile blue plasma stable until it experiences a hard kinetic impact. Ranging in size from a small apple to a large grapefruit, they are carried in specialized, padded bandoliers or woven satchels to prevent accidental discharge. When the membrane shatters, it releases a sudden, violent burst of concussive force and electricity.',	NULL,	NULL,	'1',	NULL),
